(4, 7, 87, 'Zizonke iinkomo zedini elinyukayo zaba ziinkunzi ezintsha ezilishumi elinambini, neenkunzi zezimvu zabalishumi elinambini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye zaba lishumi elinambini, namadini azo anyukayo, zalishumi elinambini iinkunzi zezimvu, zedini lesono.', 'XHO22'),
