(4, 7, 89, 'Ke ekungeneni kukaMoses ententeni yokuhlangana, ukuba athethe naye, weva izwi lothetha kuye esisithekweni esiphezu kwetyeya yesingqino, phakathi kweekerubhi zombini; wathetha naye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 2, 'Thetha kuAron, uthi kuye, Ekuzimiseni kwakho izibane, mazikhanyise izibane zibe sixhenxe ecaleni kwesiphatho sezibane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 3, 'Wenjenjalo uAron; wazimisa izibane zaso zaphambi kwesiphatho sezibane, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 4, 'Ukusetyenzwa kwesiphatho eso yaba yigolide ekhandiweyo, kwasa esiqwini saso, kwasa ezintyantyambeni zaso, ingumkhando wona; ngokomfanekiso uYehova awawubonisayo uMoses, wenjenjalo ukwenza isiphatho sezibane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 5, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 6, 'Bakhuphe abaLevi phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, ubahlambulule;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 7, 'Nantsi into oya kuyenza kubo ukuba bahlanjululwe: Bafefa ngamanzi okuhlambulula, yaye bachebe umzimba wabo wonke, bahlambe iimpahla zabo, bahlambuluke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 8, 'Uze uthabathe inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nedini layo elinyukayo, nomgubo ocoliweyo, ogalelwe ioli, uyithabathe eyesibini inkunzi entsha, ibe lidini lesono;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 9, 'Uze ubasondeze abaLevi ententeni yokuhlangana, ulibizele ndawonye lonke ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 10, 'Ubasondeze abaLevi phambi koYehova, bacinezela oonyana bakaSirayeli ngezandla zabo phezu kwabaLevi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 11, 'Wobasondeza uAron abaLevi phambi koYehova, babe ngumbingelelo woonyana bakaSirayeli, bakhonze uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 12, 'AbaLevi bacinezela ngezandla zabo phezu kweentloko zezo nkunzi zeenkomo, uze wenze enye ibe lidini lesono, enye ibe lidini elinyukayo kuYehova lokucamagushela izono zabaLevi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 13, 'Ubabeke abaLevi phambi koAron naphambi koonyana bakhe, ubasondeze njengomnikelo kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 14, 'Khetha ke abaLevi phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, babe ngabam abaLevi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 15, 'Emveni koko bongena abaLevi, basebenze ententeni yokuhlangana; bazihlambulule, bazenze idini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 16, 'Ngokuba ndanikwa mna phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli; esikhundleni sabo bavula zonke izizalo zonina, esikhundleni samazibulo onke koonyana bakaSirayeli, ndabathabathela mna.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 17, 'Ngokuba ngawam onke amazibulo phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, ebantwini nasezinkomeni; xa ndawaxabelayo onke amazibulo ezweni laseYiputa, ndawangcwalisela mna.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 18, 'Ndabathabatha abaLevi esikhundleni samazibulo onke koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 19, 'AbaLevi ndabanikela ukuba babe sisipho kuAron noonyana bakhe phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, ukuba balungiselele oonyana bakaSirayeli ententeni yokuhlangana, bacamagushele izono zoonyana bakaSirayeli akukho sihlwayo phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, ekusondeleni koonyana bakaSirayeli engcweleni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 20, 'Benza ke ooMoses noAron nebandla lonke loonyana bakaSirayeli kubaLevi; njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses ngabaLevi, benjenjalo oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 21, 'Bazihlambulula abaLevi, bahlamba iingubo zabo; uAron wayisondeza yaba ngumsondezo phambi koYehova; yaye uAron wabenzela umnikelo wokuba bahlambuluke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 22, 'Emva koko bangena abaLevi ukuze basebenze umsebenzi wabo ententeni yokuhlangana phambi koAron naphambi koonyana bakhe; njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses ngenxa yabaLevi, benjenjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 23, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 24, '“Nguwo lo wabaLevi: othabathele kominyaka imashumi mabini anamihlanu ezelwe, kwenyusa, bongena enkonzweni ententeni yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 25, 'Ukususela kwiminyaka engamashumi amahlanu ubudala baya kuyeka ukuyilinda inkonzo yayo, yaye abayi kuphinda bayikhonze.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 8, 26, 'Kodwa bafanele basebenze kunye nabazalwana babo ententeni yokuhlangana ukuba bagcine inkonzo, bangenzi nawuphi na umsebenzi wakukhonza. Uze wenjenjalo kubaLevi ngokwesiko aya kuniwisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses entlango yaseSinayi, ngenyanga yokuqala, ngomnyaka wesibini wokuphuma kwabo ezweni laseYiputa, wathi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 2, 'Oonyana bakaSirayeli bafanele bayibhiyozele ipasika ngexesha layo elimisiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 3, 'Noyenza ngomhla weshumi elinesine kuloo nyanga, lakutshona ilanga, ngexesha elimisiweyo; niyigcine ngokwamasiko nezithethe zayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 4, 'Wathi uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli, mabenze ipasika.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 5, 'Bayenza ke ipasika ngenyanga yokuqala, ngomhla weshumi elinesine, ngokuhlwa, entlango yaseSinayi njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses, benjenjalo oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 6, 'Kwakukho amadoda athile awayedyobhekile sisidumbu somntu, kangangokuba ayengenakuyenza ipasika ngaloo mini; bakhokela phambi koMoses noAron ngaloo mini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 7, 'Athi loo madoda kuye, Siziinqambi ngomntu; sithintelwe yini na, ukuba singawusondezi umbingelelo kaYehova phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli ngexesha lakhe elimisiweyo?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 8, 'Wathi uMoses kubo, Sukani nime, ndive ukuba uYehova woniwisela ntoni na.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 9, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 10, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi, Umntu ngomntu ongowembewu yenu, xa athe wazenza inqambi ngofileyo, nokuba uthe wathabathe uhambo olude, woyenza ipasika, ukumzukisa uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 11, 'Boyenza ngenyanga yesibini, ngomhla weshumi elinesine, ngokuhlwa, kunye nezonka ezingenagwele kunye nemifuno ekrakra;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 12, 'Musa ukushiya nto kuyo kude kuse, ungaphuli thambo layo; wenze ngokwemithetho yonke yepasika.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 13, 'Ke yena umntu ohlambulukileyo, ongekho eluhambeni, othe akayibhiyozeli ipasika, loo mphefumlo wonqanyulwa, ungabikho ebandleni, ngokuba akawusondezanga umbingelelo kaYehova ngexesha elimisiweyo, wowuhlawula lowo isono sakhe sinxibe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 14, 'Njengokuphambukela kuni ophambukele phakathi kwenu, wenza ipasika ekumzukiseni uYehova; Ukwenjenjalo ke uya kwenza ngokommiselo wepasika nangokwesiko layo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 15, 'Ngomhla wokumiswa komnquba, ilifu lawusibekela umnquba oyintente yesingqino;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 16, 'Kwahlala kunjalo: Ilifu laliwusibekela emini, laba yimbonakalo yomlilo ebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 17, 'Kwathi, lakunyuka ilifu phezu komnquba, basuke balandele oonyana bakaSirayeli; yaye kwindawo elihlala kuyo ilifu oonyana bakaSirayeli bamisa iintente zabo khona kanye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 18, 'Ngokomyalelo kaYehova banduluka oonyana bakaSirayeli, bamisa iinkampu ngokomyalelo kaYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 19, 'Lahlala ilifu imihla emininzi phezu komnquba, bayigcina oonyana bakaSirayeli inkonzo kaYehova, abanduluka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 20, 'Lathi, lakubuya ilifu phezu komnquba nokuba yimihla embalwa, basigcina isigxina sikaYehova, abanduluka. Ngokomlomo kaYehova bahlala ezintenteni zabo, ngokomlomo kaYehova banduluka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 21, 'Lathi, lakubakho ilifu ngokuhlwa kude kuse, lakunyuka ilifu kwakusa, banduluke; nokuba kunyuke ilifu emini, nokuba kusebusuku, ahamba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 22, 'Nokuba ilifu lihleli phezu komnquba iintsuku ezimbini, nokuba yinyanga, nokuba ngumnyaka, ukuthi lihlale phezu kwawo, bamisa oonyana bakaSirayeli, abanduluka; lakuba ke lavuka, bahamba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 9, 23, 'Ngokomlomo kaYehova babehlala ezintenteni, bafuduka ngokomlomo kaYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 2, 'Zenzele amaxilongo esilivere abe mabini; wenze iqashiso, ukuze ube nokuwusebenzisa ekubizeni ibandla nasekutsaleni izitya.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 3, 'Xa kukhatshwa isandi, lohlanganisana nawe lonke ibandla emnyango wentente yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 4, 'Ukuba kuthe kwavuthelwa ixilongo, kwavuthela nje elinye, zohlanganisana kuwe izikhulu eziziintloko zamawaka akwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 5, 'Xa ubiza ukumkani, iibhere zasempumalanga ziya phambili.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 6, 'Xa nithe nambiza okwesibini ukumkani, maze ashukume amatyala asezantsi; kufuneka baziphakamisele i-alarm emva koko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 7, 'Kodwa xa ibandla lithe lahlangana, khwazani, kodwa ningahlabi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 8, 'Bavuthela ngezigodlo oonyana baka-Aron ababingeleli; ibe ngummiselo ongunaphakade kuni kwizizukulwana zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 9, 'Xa uthe walihlasela utshaba olunibandezelayo, vuthelani ngezigodlo; aye niya kukhunjulwa phambi koYehova uThixo wenu, nikhululwe ezintshabeni zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 10, 'Yaye, ngomhla wovuyo lwenu nangemihla yenu yomthendeleko nasekuthwaseni kweenyanga zenu novuthela amaxilongo phezu kweminikelo yenu etshiswayo naphezu kwemibingelelo yenu yombulelo; ukuze sibe sisikhumbuzo kuni phambi koThixo wenu: ndinguYehova, uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 11, 'Ngomhla wamashumi amabini wenyanga yesibini, ngomnyaka wesibini, kwabakho ilifu phezu kwentente yesingqino.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 12, 'Banduluka ke oonyana bakaSirayeli entlango yaseSinayi; lema ilifu entlango yaseParan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 13, 'Baqala banduluka ngokomyalelo kaYehova ngenkonzo kaMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 14, 'Yahamba ibhanile yeminquba yoonyana bakaYuda phambi kwabo, banduluka benemikhosi yabo; yaye iqabane lakhe lalinguNashon unyana ka-Aminadabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 15, 'Indlu yendlu yoonyana bakaIsakare yayiphethwe nguNataniyeli, unyana kaTsuhare.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 16, 'Indlu yoonyana bakaZebhulon yayiphethwe nguEliyabhi, unyana kaHelon;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 17, 'Wadilizwa umnquba; Baphuma ke oonyana bakaGershon noonyana bakaMerari, bethwele umnquba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 18, 'Yaye ibhanile yongqingo lukaRubhen yahlulwa ngokwezahlulo zabo, yaye isahlulo sakhe yayinguElitsure unyana kaTedure.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 19, 'Indlu yendlu yoonyana bakaSimon yayiphethwe nguSelumiyeli, unyana kaTsurishadayi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 20, 'Indlu yendlu yoonyana bakaGadi yayiphethwe nguEliyasafu, unyana kaDehuweli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 21, 'Bemka ke oonyana bakaKehati, bayithwala ingcwele; bamisa umnquba phezu kwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 22, 'Ibhanile yokhuselo loonyana bakaEfrayim yayikwizikolo zabo, yaye ibutho lakhe yayinguElishama unyana ka-Amihudi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 23, 'Indlu yoonyana bakaManase ibiphethwe nguGamaliyeli, unyana kaPedasure;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 24, 'Indlu yendlu yoonyana bakaBhenjamin yayiphethwe nguAbhidan, unyana kaGidiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 25, 'Yaye ibhanile yongqingo loonyana bakaDana yaba ngumvuzo wongqingo bonke ngamaqela abo; yaye iqabane lakhe yayinguAhieser unyana ka-Amishadayi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 26, 'Ibhunga lemizalwane yoonyana baka-Ashere laliphethwe nguPagiyeli unyana kaOkran.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 27, 'Ibhunga losapho loonyana bakaNafetali laliphethwe nguAhira, unyana kaEnana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 28, 'Iihambo zoonyana bakaSirayeli namabhunga abo zazinjalo ekunyukeni kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 29, 'Wathi uMoses kuHobhabhi, unyana kaReguweli, umMidiyan, uyise womkaMoses, Thina siyenyuka siye kuloo ndawo athe uYehova, Ndiya kuninika yona; Hamba nathi, sokwenzela okulungileyo; uYehova uthethe kakuhle ngoSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 30, 'Wathi yena kuye, Andiyi kuhamba; kodwa ke ndiza kuya kwilizwe lakowethu nakwindlu yam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 31, 'Wathi yena, Musa ukusishiya; ngokuba uyakwazi ukumisa iintente entlango, kwaye unokuba kwindawo yethu kumgama wamehlo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 32, 'Ukuba uthe wahamba nathi, ewe, konke okulungileyo aya kusenzela kona uYehova, sokwenzela nathi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 33, 'Banduluka entabeni kaYehova, umgama weentsuku ezintathu, yaye ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova yabakhokela kuhambo lweentsuku ezintathu ukuba ibafumanele indawo yokuphumla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 34, 'Ilifu likaYehova laba phezu kwabo emini ekuphumeni kwabo eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 35, 'Kwathi ekumkeni kwetyeya, wathi uMoses, Zivuse, Yehova, zichithachithe iintshaba zakho; mababaleke kuwe abakuthiyayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 10, 36, 'Uthe ke ekuphumleni kwawo, Nkosi, buyela kumawaka akwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 1, 'Ukuba bathe abantu bakrokra, bububi emehlweni kaYehova; weva uYehova; wavutha umsindo wakhe; watsha umlilo kaYehova phakathi kwabo, wabadla abo basemacaleni eminquba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 2, 'Abantu bambiza uMoses; wathandaza uMoses kuYehova, waphuma umlilo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 3, 'Wathi igama laloo ndawo yiTabhera, ngenxa yokuba umlilo kaYehova wawusitsha phakathi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 4, 'Yaza inkitha ephakathi kwabo yefa yindlala; babuya balila oonyana bakaSirayeli, besithi, Ngubani na oya kusinika ukudla, sidle?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 5, 'Sicinga ngeentlanzi ebesizidla eYiputa ngesisa; iikomkomere, iimelon, iiliki, itswele, ikonofile;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 6, 'Kungokunje umphefumlo wethu womile;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 7, 'Imana leyo ibinjengeenkozo zekoriyandire, ukubonakala kwayo bekunjengokubonakala kweBhedola;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 8, 'Bajikeleza abantu, bayichola, bayisile etyeni lokusila, mhlawumbi bayisile ngodaka, bayibhaka ngeepani, benza ngayo isonka;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 9, 'Kwakuhla umbethe esililini ebusuku, yawa imana phezu kwawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 10, 'Weva uMoses abantu bekhala emizalwaneni yabo, elowo emnyango wentente yakhe; Wavutha umsindo kaYehova kunene; NoMoses wayengonwabanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 11, 'Wathi uMoses kuYehova, Yini na ukuba umcinezele umkhonzi wakho? yaye kutheni na ndingaboni mfesane emehlweni akho, ekubeni undibize ngokuba ngumthwalo wolu hlanga luphela?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 12, 'Ndibamkele bonke na aba? Ndim na owabazalayo, naxa uthe kum, Bathwale esifubeni sakho, njengoko kuzala umntwana, ubase kwelo zwe wafunga kooyise ngalo?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 13, 'Ndoyizuza phi na inyama, ndibanike bonke aba bantu? ngokuba bekhala kum, besithi, Siphe ukudla, sidle.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 14, 'Andinako ukuluthwala ndedwa olu hlanga, ngokuba lunzima kakhulu kum.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 15, 'Ukuba uthe wenjenjalo kum, ndibulale, ukuba ndibabalwe nguwe; kwaye andizange ndiyibone intlungu yam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 16, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Ndihlanganisele amadoda amashumi asixhenxe kumadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli, owaziyo ukuba ngamadoda amakhulu abantu, neentloko zabo; uwazise ententeni yokuhlangana, eme khona nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 17, 'Ndiya kuhla, ndithethe nawe khona; ndithabathe ube mnye kuMoya ophezu kwakho, ndiwubeke phezu kwabo; yaye baya kuwuthwala umthwalo waba bantu kunye nawe, ukuze ungawuthwali wedwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 18, 'Uthi ebantwini, Zihlambululeni ngomso, nodla inyama; ngokuba nakhalayo phambi koYehova, nisithi, Ngubani na oya kusinika inyama sidle? ngokuba izinto bezisihambela kakuhle eYiputa; ke uYehova uya kuninika inyama, nidle.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 19, 'Nize ningadli usuku olunye, nokuba ziintsuku ezimbini, nokuba mihlanu, nokuba lishumi, nokuba ziintsuku ezimashumi mabini;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 20, 'yoba yinyanga iphela, ide iphume emathatheni enu, ibe lisikizi kuni; ngokuba nimcekisile uYehova ophakathi kwenu, namemeza phambi kwakhe, nisithi, Savela eYiputa?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 21, 'Wathi uMoses, Abantu endiphakathi kwabo bangamakhulu amathandathu amawaka amadoda ahamba ngeenyawo; Ubusithi, Ndiya kubanika inyama, bayidle inyanga iphela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 22, 'Umhlambi weebhokhwe neenkomo uya kuxhelelwa bona na? Okanye ngaba zonke iintlanzi zolwandle ziya kuhlanganiselwa ukuba zibalingane?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 23, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Isandla sikaYehova sifutshane na? wandule ukubona ukuba ilizwi lam liya kuza kuwe, aliyi kubuya.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 24, 'Waphuma uMoses, wawathetha ebantwini amazwi kaYehova, wahlanganisa amadoda amakhulu angamashumi asixhenxe abantu, ahlala ewujikelezile umnquba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 25, 'iNkosi yehla efini, yathetha kuye, yathabatha uMoya ophezu kwakhe, yawunika amadoda amakhulu angamashumi asixhenxe; Wahlala uMoya phezu kwabo, baprofeta, ababeka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 26, 'Ke kaloku kwasala amadoda amabini eminqubeni, igama lenye belinguElidade, igama leyesibini linguMedade; wahlala phezu kwawo umoya; yaye babengabaprofeti abathile, yaye babengaphumi emnqubeni; baprofeta eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 27, 'Wagidima umfana, waxelela uMoses, wathi, OoElidade noMedade bayaprofeta eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 28, 'Waphendula uYoshuwa unyana kaNun, umlungiseleli kaMoses, wakubakhonzi bakhe, wathi, Bathintele, Moses, nkosi yam;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 29, 'Wathi uMoses kuye, Unekhwele ngam na? Wanga uThixo angabenza abaprofeti bonke abantu bakaYehova, abeke uMoya wakhe phezu kwabo!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 30, 'uMoses wamrholela eminqubeni, yena namadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 31, 'Waphuma umoya kaYehova, wangenisa iinqanawa elwandle, zawela eminqubeni, zawela eminqubeni, zaba luhambo lwemini ukuya apha, zaba luhambo lwemini ukuya kwelinye, ngeenxa zonke iinkampu, nanjengohambo losuku ukuphakama kwawo bekuziikubhite ezimbini emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 32, 'Bema ke abantu yonke loo mini, ubusuku bonke, yonke imini yengomso, babutha izagwityi; owabutha kancinane wabutha iihomere ezilishumi, babela eminqubeni bonke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 33, 'Kwathi xa inyama leyo isesemazinyweni abo, ingekahlafunwa, wavutha umsindo kaYehova kubo abantu, wababulala abantu ngokufa kabuhlungu kunene.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 34, 'Wathi igama laloo ndawo yiKibrothafa, ngokuba kulapho bangcwabela khona iinkanuko zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 11, 35, 'Banduluka abantu eKibroti-hataweva, baya eHatseroti; wahlala eHatseroti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 1, 'Bathetha kakubi ooMiriyam noAron ngoMoses ngenxa yenkazana engumKushikazi abeyizekile, ngenxa yokuba wayezeke inkazana engumKushikazi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 2, 'Bathi ke, uYehova uthethile na ngoMoses? Akathethanga ngathi? Weva uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 3, '(uMoses wayengoyena mntu ulula kunabantu bonke behlabathi.)', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 4, 'Wathetha uYehova kwaoko kuMoses, nakuAron, nakuMiriyam, wathi, Phumani nina nobathathu ententeni yokuhlangana. Baphuma ke bobathathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 5, 'Wehla uYehova efini, wema emnyango wentente, wabiza ooAron noMiriyam, baphuma bobabini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 6, 'Wathi: Phulaphulani amazwi am: Ukuba kukho umprofeti phakathi kwenu, mna, Yehova, ndobonakala kuye ngombono, ndithethe kuye ephupheni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 7, 'Akanjalo ngomkhonzi wam uMoses, othembekileyo endlwini yam yonke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 8, 'Ndiya kuthetha naye umlomo kumlomo, ngokubonakalayo, kungabi ngamazwi adelekileyo; yaye uya kuwubona umfanekiselo kaYehova. Yini na ukuba ungoyiki ukuthetha kumkhonzi wam uMoses?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 9, 'Wavutha umsindo kaYehova kubo; wemka ke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 10, 'Lemka ilifu emnqubeni; nanko uMiriyam eneqhenqa, emhlophe njengekhephu; yaye uAron waya kuMiriyam, nanko eneqhenqa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 11, 'Wathi uAron kuMoses, Camagu, nkosi yam!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 12, 'Makangabi njengofileyo, ekuphumeni kwakhe esizalweni sonina, ekudliwe isiqingatha senyama.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 13, 'Wabiza uMoses kuYehova, wathi, Thixo, ndiyakukhunga, mphilise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 14, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Ukuba uyise wamtshicela ebusweni, ubengayi kuva ihlazo na iintsuku ezisixhenxe? wakhutshelwa ngaphandle kweminquba iintsuku ezisixhenxe, waphinda wamkelwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 15, 'uMiriyam wavalelwa ngaphandle kweminquba iintsuku zasixhenxe, àbaphuma ke abantu, wada wabuyiswa uMiriyam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 12, 16, 'Emva koko bemka abantu eHatseroti bamisa iinkampu entlango yaseParan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 2, 'Thumelani amadoda enu, aye kuhlola ilizwe lakwaKanan, endilinika oonyana bakaSirayeli kwisizwe sooyise, nithumele indoda ibe nye, iyileyo ibe ngukumkani kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 3, 'Wabathuma ke uMoses, esentlango yaseParan, ngokomlomo kaYehova; onke loo madoda eziintloko zoonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 4, 'Ngawo la amagama abo: kwisizwe sakwaRubhen ibinguSamuwa, unyana kaSakure;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 5, 'kwaSimon nguShafati, unyana kaHore;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 6, 'kwisizwe sakwaYuda, ibinguKalebhi, unyana kaYefune;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 7, 'kwisizwe sakwaIsakare, ibinguIgali, unyana kaYosefu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 8, 'kwisizwe sakwaEfrayim nguHoseya, unyana kaNun;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 9, 'kwisizwe sakwaBhenjamin, ibinguPalti, unyana kaRafu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 10, 'kwisizwe sakwaZebhulon, ibinguGadiyeli, unyana kaSodi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 11, 'kwisizwe sakwaYosefu, kwisizwe sakwaManase, ibinguGadi, unyana kaSusi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 12, 'kwisizwe sakwaDan, ibinguAmiyeli, unyana kaGemali;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 13, 'kwisizwe sakwa-Ashere nguSeture, unyana kaMikayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 14, 'kwisizwe sakwaNafetali, ibinguNagibhi, unyana kaWofi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 15, 'kwisizwe sakwaGadi ibinguGehuweli, unyana kaMagi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 16, 'Ngawo lawo amagama amadoda awawathumayo uMoses, ukuba aye kuhlola ilizwe. uMoses wabiza uHoseya, unyana kaNun, uYoshuwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 17, 'Wabathuma uMoses, ukuba baye kuhlola ilizwe lakwaKanan, wathi kubo, Hambani niye ngapha ezantsi, ninyuke entabeni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 18, 'Kwaye khangelani ihlabathi elikhoyo; nabantu abemi khona, nokuba bomelele, nokuba bathambile, bambalwa, nokuba baninzi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 19, 'Yaye liyintoni na ihlabathi abaphila kulo, enoba lilungile okanye libi kusini na; nokuba zeziphi na izixeko abahlala kuzo, enoba basezintenteni okanye basezinqabeni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 20, 'ukuba linjani na ilizwe elo, liyachuma, alichumi, kusini na; Yomelelani, nivelise iziqhamo zelizwe. Ngoku yayilixesha leziqhamo zokuqala ezivuthiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 21, 'Bandula ke benyuka baza balihlola ilizwe ukususela entlango yaseTsin ukusa eRehobhi ukuya kufikelela eHamati.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 22, 'Benyuka baya ezantsi, beza eHebron; apho kwakukho uAkiman, uSheshayi noTalemayi, oonyana baka-Anaki. Ke iHebron yayakhiwe iminyaka esixhenxe ngaphambi kweTsohan yaseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 23, 'Bafika entilini yomlambo waseEshkole, bagawula khona umdiliya onesihloko esinye seediliya, bawuthwala ngentonga phakathi kwawo; beza neerharnati namakhiwane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 24, 'Loo ndawo yathiywa igama lesihlambo sase-Eshkole, ngenxa yeediliya ababezivuna kuso oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 25, 'Abuya emva kweentsuku ezimashumi mane, eza kulihlola ilizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 26, 'Eza afika kuMoses, nakuAron, nakwibandla lonke loonyana bakaSirayeli, entlango yaseParan eKadeshe; wabaxelela, nakwibandla lonke, wabazisa eziqhameni zelizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 27, 'Bamxelela besithi, Sifikile kwelo zwe usithume kulo; inene, libaleka amasi nobusi; sisiqhamo sawo ke esi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 28, 'Ke bona abantu abemi kwelo zwe baqinisa amandla, imizi yakhiwe ngeendonga ezinkulu kunene; sabona nabantwana baka Enake apho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 29, 'Ama-Amaleki ahleli ezweni elingasezantsi, namaHeti, namaYebhusi, nama-Amori, ahleli ezintabeni, namaKanan ahleli ngaselunxwemeni lweYordan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 30, 'Wabakhwankqisa uKalebhi abantu phambi koMoses, wathi, Masinyuke ngokukhawuleza, siyithabathe; ngokuba somelele ngokwaneleyo ukuba sisoyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 31, 'Ke amadoda abenyuke naye athi, Asiyi kuya kwaba bantu; ngokuba bomelele kunathi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 32, 'Baza babazisa oonyana bakaSirayeli ilizwi elibi ngelizwe ababelihlola, besithi, Ilizwe esacanda kulo silihlola, lilizwe elidla abemi balo; yaye bonke abantu esababonayo kuyo bangabantu abade.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 13, 33, 'Sazibona khona iinkomo, oonyana baka-Enaki, bakubaFarisi; yaye emehlweni ethu saba njengeenkumbi, yaye sasinjalo emehlweni abo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 1, 'Laduma lonke ibandla; balila abantu ngobo busuku.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 2, 'Babakrokrela ooMoses noAron bonke oonyana bakaSirayeli, lathi kubo lonke ibandla, Akwaba besifele ezweni laseYiputa! okanye uThixo angasibulala kule ntlango!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 3, 'Kwakutheni ukuze uYehova asizise kweli hlabathi ukuze sibulawe ngekrele, baze abafazi nabantwana bethu babe ngabathinjwa? Akusilungele na kanye ukuba sibuyele eYiputa?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 4, 'Bathetha omnye komnye besithi, Masizinyulele ukumkani, sibuyele eYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 5, 'Bawa ngobuso uMoses noAron phambi kwebandla lonke lebandla loonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 6, 'uYoshuwa unyana kaNun, noKalebhi unyana kaYefune, ababephakathi kwabo babethimbe ilizwe, bazikrazula iingubo zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 7, 'Athetha kwisihlwele sonke soonyana bakaSirayeli, esithi, Ilizwe esacanda kulo silihlola, lilizwe elihle kunene.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 8, 'Ukuba uYehova uyakholiswa sithi, wosisa kweli lizwe, asinike; lilizwe elibaleka amasi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 9, 'Kodwa musani ukugwilika kuYehova, ningaboyiki abantu belo zwe nina; ngokuba kukudla kwethu; Umkile kubo ikhusi labo, ngokuba uYehova unathi; musani ukuboyika.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 10, 'Lathi lonke ibandla mabaxulutywe ngamatye. Babonakala ubuqaqawuli bukaYehova ententeni yokuhlangana, phambi koonyana bonke bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 11, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Kuya kuda kube nini na bengandithobeli aba bantu? kwaye kuyakuthatha ixesha elingakanani phambi kokuba bandikholelwe, ngenxa yayo yonke imimangaliso endiyenzileyo phakathi kwabo?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 12, 'Ndiya kuwohlwaya ngesibetho ndize ndiwuhluthe, ndikwenze ube luhlanga olukhulu nolomeleleyo kunalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 13, 'Wathi uMoses kuYehova, AmaYiputa avile, ukuba ulukhuphe ngesandla sakho olu hlanga phakathi kwawo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 14, 'Boxelela abantu beli lizwe, ngokuba bevile ukuba iNkosi yakho iphakathi kwaba bantu, nokuba iNkosi yakho ibonwa ubuso ngobuso, nokuba ilifu lakho liphezu kwabo, ubakhokela emini kubumnyama belifu nakubumnyama bomlilo ebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 15, 'Ukuba uthe walubulala lonke olu hlanga njengamntu mnye, zothi iintlanga eziluvileyo udumo lwakho, zithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 16, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova ebengenako ukubasa aba bantu ezweni abebafungele lona, ngenxa yoko wababulala entlango.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 17, 'Ke kaloku, ngamana amandla enkosi yam abe makhulu, njengoko uthethileyo ukuthi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 18, 'uYehova uzeka kade umsindo, unemfesane enkulu, uxolela ubugwenxa nezikreqo, angamenzi msulwa onetyala, ubuvelela ubugwenxa booyise koonyana, kwesesithathu nakwesesine isizukulwana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 19, 'Buxolele ubugwenxa baba bantu ngobuninzi benceba yakho, njengoko ubuxoleleyo ubugwenxa baba bantu, uthabathele eYiputa wezisa apha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 20, 'Wathi uYehova, Ndikuxolele ngelizwi lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 21, 'Noko ke, ndiphila nje, ihlabathi lonke liya kuzaliswa bubuqaqawuli bukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 22, 'Ekubeni bonke bebubonile ubuqaqawuli bam, nemisebenzi yam ebalulekileyo endayenzayo eYiputa nasentlango, bandilingile ngoku izihlandlo ezilishumi, abaliphulaphula izwi lam;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 23, 'Okunene abayi kulibona ilizwe endafunga kooyise ngalo, bengaliboni namnye kwabandingcikivayo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 24, 'Ke yena umkhonzi wam uKalebhi, ngenxa enokuba ebenamoya wumbi, wandilandela kwaphela, ndomzisa ezweni ebeye kulo; Ilidle ilifa imbewu yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 25, 'Abemi ke ama-Amaleki namaKanan entilini leyo. Jikani ngomso, niye entlango ngendlela eya eShelfeshe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 26, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses nakuAron, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 27, 'Kuya kuda kube nini na ndilithwele eli bandla lingendawo likrokrayo? Ndeva ke ukuduma koonyana bakaSirayeli, ekuthetheni kwabo ngam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 28, 'Yithi kubo, Ndihleli nje, utsho uYehova, njengoko nithethileyo ezindlebeni zam, ndiya kwenjenjalo kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 29, 'Izidumbu zenu ziya kuwa kule ntlango; nabo bonke ababhaliweyo ngani, bebonke ngokwenani lenu, bethabathela kominyaka imashumi mabini ezelwe, kwesa kwabakhulu, bona badunyiswa ndim.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 30, 'Aniyi kungena kulo ilizwe endafungayo ukuba ndonenza kulo, ngaphandle kukaKalebhi unyana kaYefune noYoshuwa unyana kaNun.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 31, 'Kodwa nina bantwana abancinane enithe niya kuthinjwa, ndiya kubazisa, yaye baya kulazi ilizwe enilicekisileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 32, 'Kodwa nina, imizimba yenu, niya kuwa kule ntlango.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 33, 'Oonyana bakho baya kubhadula entlango iminyaka emashumi mane, besenza ubuhenyu babo, zide izidumbu zabo ziphele entlango.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 34, 'Ngokwenani leentsuku enalihlola ngalo ilizwe, iintsuku ezimashumi mane, umhla ube ngumnyaka, uya kuzithwala izono zenu iminyaka emashumi mane, nilaphule ke ilizwi lam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 35, 'Mna, iNkosi, ndathi: Ndiya kuyenza le nto kulo lonke eli bandla likhohlakeleyo elindihlanganiseleyo; baya kutshabalala kule ntlango, bafele khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 36, 'Amadoda awawathumayo uMoses ukuba aye kuhlola ilizwe, abuya alikrokrisa lonke ibandla ngaye ngokuyihleka ilizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 37, 'Kwanaloo madoda azisa ingxelo embi elizweni abulawa sisibetho eso phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 38, 'Kodwa uYoshuwa unyana kaNun noKalebhi unyana kaYefune, ababephakathi kwamadoda awayeye kuhlola ilizwe, babesaphila.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 39, 'Wawathetha ke uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli bonke loo mazwi, bakhala abantu kakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 40, 'Bavuka kusasa, benyuka baya encotsheni yentaba, besithi, Yabona, sikho, siyanyuka siye kuloo ndawo wayithembisa uYehova, ngokuba soyisakele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 41, 'Wathi uMoses, Yini na ukuba niwaphule umthetho kaYehova? kodwa ayiyi kuphumelela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 42, 'Musani ukunyuka, kuba uYehova akakho phakathi kwenu; hleze nigxothwe ziintshaba zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 43, 'Ngokuba ama-Amaleki namaKanan aphambi kwenu, niya kuwa likrele; ngokuba umnikele umva uYehova, akayi kuba nawe uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 44, 'Basuka baba nobuganga, benyuka baya encotsheni yenduli; Ke yona ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova, noMoses ayiphumanga eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 14, 45, 'Ehla ke ama-Amaleki namaKanan awayehlala kuloo nduli, awoyisa aza adubaduba lawo ukuya kufikelela eHorem.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 2, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Xa nithe nafika ezweni lezakhiwo zenu endininika lona,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 3, 'nosondeza kuYehova idini elinyukayo, nokuba lidini elinyukayo, nokuba lidini elinyukayo, nokuba libe lidini elinyukayo, nokuba libe lidini lokuqhutywa yintliziyo, libe lidini elinyukayo kuYehova, libe lidini elinyukayo, nokuba libe livumba elithozamisayo kuYehova, nokuba yinkomo, nokuba yinkomo, nokuba lidini elinyukayo eyenkomo, neyeenkomo umhlambi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 4, 'Lowo uwuzisa umsondezo wakhe kuYehova, wosondeza isahlulo seshumi sehin yeoli, ukudla kwasemlilweni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 5, 'nomnikelo othululwayo nesahlulo sesine sehin yewayini, kunye nedini elinyukayo, nokuba ngumbingelelo, ube ngowamvana-nye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 6, 'Nokuba ngowenkunzi yegusha, wenze umnikelo wokudla ube zizahlulo ezibini zesishumi somgubo ocoliweyo, neoli ibe sisahlulo sesithathu sehin.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 7, 'Yaye uya kunikela isahlulo sesithathu sehin yewayini njengomnikelo othululwayo, ibe livumba elithozamisayo kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 8, 'Xa uthe wenza inkomo ibe lidini elinyukayo, nokuba yeyesibhambathiso, nokuba ngumbingelelo wokubulela kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 9, 'Yaye umele azise umnikelo wasemlilweni wezahlulo ezithathu zesishumi somgubo ocoliweyo nesiqingatha sehin yeoli ndawonye nenkunzi yenkomo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 10, 'Wosondeza isiqingatha sehin yewayini ibe ngumnikelo othululwayo, ibe livumba elithozamisayo kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 11, 'Kwenziwa oko ngenkunzi yenkomo enye, nokuba kukwinkunzi yegusha enye, nokuba kukwimvana enye, nokuba kukwitakane lebhokhwe elinye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 12, 'Ngokwenani eniya kulilungisa, yenzani ngokunjalo elowo ngokwenani lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 13, 'Wonk’ ubani ozalelwe kwelo lizwe uya kuzenza ezi zinto ngokunikela umnikelo wasemlilweni onevumba elithozamisayo kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 14, 'Kube ngathi kuphambukele kuni umphambukeli, ezizukulwaneni zenu, xa athe waphambukela kuni, wazisa ivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova, ivumba elithozamisayo; njengoko nisenza ngako, uya kwenza ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 15, 'Woba mnye umthetho kuni ebandleni nakumphambukeli ophambukele kuni, ube ngumthetho wexesha elingenammiselo kwizizukulwana zenu; njengoko unjalo wena, woba njalo umphambukeli phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 16, 'Wosebenza umthetho mnye, nendlela enye, kuni nakumphambukeli ophambukele phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 17, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 18, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Xa nithe nafika kulo ilizwe elo ndinisa kulo,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 19, 'Ngoku ke, ukuba nithe nasidla isonka selo lizwe, nosondeza umnikelo kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 20, 'Sondelani isonka eso sentlama sentlama yenu, sibe lidini elinyukayo; woyiphakamisa njengoko wenza ngako kwisabelo sesibetho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 21, 'Kowokuqala kwintlama yenu nomnika uYehova umnikelo kwizizukulwana zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 22, 'Ukuba nithe nalahleka, anayigcina yonke imithetho abethe uYehova wayiwisela uMoses;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 23, 'Zonke izinto uYehova waniwisela umthetho ngazo ngoMoses, kususela koko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses, nakwizizukulwana zenu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 24, 'Ukuba oku kuthe kwenziwa ningalazi ibandla lonke, ibandla lonke losondeza umnikelo otshiswayo, ivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova, nomnikelo wakhe wokudla, nomnikelo wakhe othululwayo ngokomthetho, nenkunzi yemvu ibe nye, ibe lidini lesono.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 25, 'Umbingeleli wozicamagushela izono zebandla lonke loonyana bakaSirayeli; ngokuba ikukungazi; yaye bawuzisa umbingelelo wabo wasemlilweni kuYehova nomnikelo wabo wesono phambi koYehova ngenxa yokungazi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 26, 'Loxolelwa ke lonke ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli, nomphambukeli ophambukele phakathi kwenu; kuba bonke abantu bebengazi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 27, 'Ukuba ubani uthe wona engazi, wosondeza ithokazi lenkomo elimnyaka mnye, libe lidini lesono.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 28, 'Umbingeleli wozicamagushela izono zomphefumlo owonayo ngongazi, xa uthe wona ngempazamo phambi koYehova, awucamagushele; kwaye uya kuxolelwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 29, 'Woba mnye umyalelo kuni ngowonileyo, engazi, nakozalelwe phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, nakowasemzini ophambukele phakathi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 30, 'Ke yena othe wakhukhumala, waba ngozalelwe ezweni nokuba ngumphambukeli, uyamdela uYehova; loo mphefumlo wonqanyulwa, ungabikho ebantwini bakowawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 31, 'Ngokuba ulidelile ilizwi likaYehova, uwaphule nomyalelo wakhe: loo mphefumlo wohlwaywa ngesiqalekiso; ubugwenxa bakhe buphezu kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 32, 'Kwathi, oonyana bakaSirayeli besentlango, bafumana umntu ethwele iinkuni ngomhla wesabatha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 33, 'Abo bamfumanayo ethwele iinkuni, bamsondeza kuMoses nakuAron nakwibandla lonke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 34, 'bamfaka elugcinweni, kuba bekungekathethwa nto eza kwenziwa ngaye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 35, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses: “Inene, loo mntu uya kubulawa; Lamngqinga lonke ibandla ngaphandle kweminquba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 36, 'Lonke ibandla lamkhuphela ngaphandle kweminquba, lamxuluba ngamatye, wafa; njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 37, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 38, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, mabenze imiqukumbelo yeempahla zabo ngokwemizalwane yabo, bafake umsonto omfusa emqukumbelweni waloo miqukumbelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 39, 'Woba ngumqondiso kuni, ukuba niwubone, niyikhumbule yonke imithetho kaYehova, niyenze; nokuze ungayigocagoci intliziyo yakho namehlo akho, obuye wahenyuza emva koko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 40, 'ukuze niyikhumbule niyenze yonke imiyalelo yam, nibe ngcwele kuThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 15, 41, 'NdinguYehova uThixo wenu, onikhuphileyo ezweni laseYiputa, ukuba ndibe nguThixo kuni; NdinguYehova, uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 1, 'uKore, unyana kaItsare, unyana kaKehati, unyana kaLevi, noDatan, noAbhiram, oonyana bakaEliyabhi, no-On unyana kaPelete, oonyana bakaRubhen.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 2, 'Bema phambi koMoses, ndawonye nabanye boonyana bakaSirayeli, iinkosana zebandla ezingamakhulu amabini anamashumi amahlanu, ezaziwayo ebandleni, nezazidumileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 3, 'Bababiza uMoses noAron, bathi kubo, Nisenanele nina, ngokuba lingcwele lonke ibandla, elowo kubo; uYehova uphakathi kwabo; niziphakamisile ngoko ebandleni likaYehova?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 4, 'Akuyiva uMoses loo nto, wawa ngobuso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 5, 'Wathetha kuKore nakwingxokolo yakhe yonke, esithi, Ngomso uYehova uya kumazisa ongcwele; wasondela kuye; lowo amnyulileyo uya kumsondeza kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 6, 'Yenzani; zithabatheni iingcedevu, wena Kora nebandla lakhe lonke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 7, 'Galela umlilo kuyo uze ugalele nesiqhumiso kuso phambi koYehova, yaye umntu athe uYehova wamnyula woba ngcwele; nidla kakhulu, nyana bakaLevi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 8, 'Wathi uMoses kuKora: “Phulaphulani, nina bonyana bakaLevi!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 9, 'Yinto encinane na kuni, ukuba uThixo kaSirayeli aninyule phakathi kwebandla lakwaSirayeli, ukuba anisondeze kuye, nisebenze umsebenzi womnquba kaYehova, nime phambi kwebandla, nilungiselele?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 10, 'wakuthabatha, wena nabazalwana bakho bonke, oonyana bakaLevi, ndawonye nawe; ningaba nifuna nobubingeleli na?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 11, 'Yini na ukuba nihlanganisene kuYehova wena nesihlwele sakho sonke, yaye uyintoni na uAron ukuba ummbombozelele?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 12, 'Wathumela uMoses, wabiza uDatan noAbhiram, oonyana bakaEliyabhi bathi, Asiyi kunyuka sinyuke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 13, 'Yinto encinane na le yokuba usikhuphe ezweni elivelisa amasi nobusi, uze kusibulala apha entlango, ukuba akuzenzanga ukumkani wethu kanye?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 14, 'Kananjalo akusingenisanga ezweni elibaleka amasi nobusi, akusinikanga lifa lamasimi nezidiliya; Uya kuwakrazula na amehlo aba bantu? asiyi kunyuka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 15, 'Wavutha kakhulu ngumsindo uMoses, wathi kuYehova: “Musa ukuyiphulaphula imibingelelo yabo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 16, 'Wathi uMoses kuKora, Wena nengxokolo yakho yonke, noba phambi koYehova, wena nabo, noAron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 17, 'Makathabathe elowo isitya sakhe somlilo, agalele kuso isiqhumiso, asondeze elowo isitya sakhe somlilo phambi koYehova, elowo abe neengcedevu zakhe ezimakhulu mabini anamanci mahlanu; wena noAron elowo epanini yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 18, 'Wathabatha elowo ugcedevu lwakhe, wabeka umlilo kuso, wagalela isiqhumiso phezu kwaso, wema noMoses noAron emnyango wentente yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 19, 'uKora walibizela ndawonye ngabo ibandla lonke emnyango wentente yokuhlangana, babonakala ubuqaqawuli bukaYehova kwibandla lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 20, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses nakuAron, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 21, 'Zahluleni kweli bandla, ukuze ndiliphelise kwaoko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 22, 'Bawa ngobuso, bathi, Camagu, Thixo, Thixo wemiphefumlo yenyama yonke, ùnokona na umntu omnye, unoburhalarhume kwibandla lonke na?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 23, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 24, 'Uze uthethe kwibandla, uthi, Sukani nize ngeenxa zonke emnqubeni kaKora noDatan noAbhiram.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 25, 'Wemka uMoses, waya kuDatan noAbhiram; amlandela amadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 26, 'Wathetha nebandla, wathi, Phumani ezintenteni zala madoda angendawo, ningachukumisi nto iyeyawo, hleze nitshabalale ezonweni zawo zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 27, 'Benyuka bemka emnqubeni kaKora noDatan noAbhiram, bajikelezisa; baphuma ooDatan noAbhiram, bema emnyango weentente zabo, nabafazi babo, noonyana babo, nabantwana babo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 28, 'Wathi uMoses, Niya kwazi ngale nto, ukuba uYehova undithumele ukwenza yonke le misebenzi; kuba andenzanga ngokuthanda kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 29, 'Ukuba aba bathe bafa ngokufa kwabantu bonke, nokuba bathe bathweswa isohlwayo sabantu bonke; uYehova akandithumanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 30, 'Ke ukuba uYehova uthe wenza into entsha, umhlaba wavula umlomo wawo, wabaginya, nento yonke abanayo, behla baye emhadini behleli; uya kwandula uqonde ukuba kutheni la madoda ehlekisa ngawo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 31, 'Akugqiba ukuwathetha onke la mazwi, waqhekeka umhlaba obuphantsi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 32, 'Ngoko umhlaba wawuvula umlomo wawo waza wabaginya bona nezindlu zabo nabo bonke abantu bakaKora nempahla yabo yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 33, 'Behla bona besaphilile, nento yonke ababenayo, baya emhadini, umhlaba wabavala, batshabalala phakathi kwebandla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 34, 'Onke oonyana bakaSirayeli ababebalindile ngaphakathi basaba ngenxa yokukhala kwabo; ngokuba babesithi, Hleze usiginye umhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 35, 'Kwandula ke kwaphuma umlilo ovela kuYehova waza watshisa amadoda angamakhulu amabini anamashumi amahlanu awayezisa isiqhumiso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 36, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 37, 'Thetha kuElazare, unyana ka-Aron, umbingeleli, ukuba azithabathe iingcedevu zomlilo ovuthayo, awubeke khona umlilo; ngokuba bathenjisiwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 38, 'Neengcedevu zabo bonayo ngakwimiphefumlo yabo, zozenza zibe ziipleyiti zokwaleka isibingelelo; ngokuba ayexhelele khona phambi koYehova, zangcwaliswa; ibe ngumqondiso koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 39, 'Wazithabatha ke umbingeleli uElazare izitya zesiqhumiso zobhedu, ababetshiswe ngazo; neepanele ezibanzi zesibingelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 40, 'Yaba sisikhumbuzo koonyana bakaSirayeli, ukuba kungabikho mntu wasemzini, ongoonyana baka-Aron, osondela ukuba aqhumisele ngesiqhumiso phambi koYehova; ukuze angabi njengoKora nakwinkoliso yabantu bakhe, njengoko uYehova wathethayo kuye ngoMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 41, 'Labakrokrela ooMoses noAron ngengomso lonke ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli, lisithi, Nina nibabulele abantu bakaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 42, 'Lababizela ndawonye ibandla uMoses noAron, bakhangela ententeni yokuhlangana; nalo ilifu liyisibekele, babonakala ubuqaqawuli bukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 43, 'Beza ooMoses noAron phambi kwentente yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 44, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 45, 'Suka kweli bandla, ndilitshabalalise kamsinya; Bawa ngobuso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 46, 'Wathi uMoses kuAron: “Thabatha ugcedevu uze ugalele umlilo ovela esibingelelweni phezu kwaso, ugalele nesiqhumiso phezu kwaso, uye ngokukhawuleza uye ebandleni, usicamagushele, ngenxa yokuba kuphume umsindo kaYehova; isibetho siqalile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 47, 'Wathabatha uAron njengoko uMoses wamwisela umthetho, wabaleka phakathi kwebandla; nanko ke, uqalile ukwahlukana phakathi kwabantu, wabavuthulula inkunkuma abantu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 48, 'Wema phakathi kwabafileyo nabahleliyo; sathintelwa isibetho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 49, 'Abo bafayo sisibetho baba lishumi elinesine lamawaka anamakhulu asixhenxe, ngaphandle kwabafayo ngenxa kaKora.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 16, 50, 'Wabuyela uAron kuMoses emnyango wentente yokuhlangana;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 2, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthabathe intonga kubo ngokwezindlu zooyise, kwiinkulu zabo zonke ngokwezindlu zooyise, iintonga zibe lishumi elinambini; bhala igama lomntu wonke kwintonga yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 3, 'Wobhala igama lika-Aron entongeni yakwaLevi, kuba yoba nye intonga yentloko yezindlu zooyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 4, 'Uzibeke ententeni yokuhlangana phambi kwesingqino, apho ndiya kuhlangana nawe khona;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 5, 'Kothi, iphupha lendoda endiyinyulileyo lityatyambe; yaye ndiza kuzibuyisela izikhalazo zoonyana bakaSirayeli abakhala ngazo ngenxa yenu kum.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 6, 'Wathetha ke uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli, yaza iinkulu zabo zamnika intonga, intonga kwinkulu yomzalwane wabo, zalishumi elinambini iintonga yaye intente ka-Aron yayiphakathi kweentente zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 7, 'Wazibeka uMoses imithwalo leyo emhlabeni phambi koYehova, ententeni yesingqino.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 8, 'Kwathi ngengomso, wangena uMoses ententeni leyo; nantso intonga ka-Aron, wendlu kaLevi, idubule, yadubula iintyatyambo, yavelisa iiamangile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 9, 'uMoses wasondeza bonke oonyana bakaSirayeli iintonga zonke phambi koYehova. Bakhangela, elowo wathabatha intonga yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 10, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Yibuyisele intonga ka-Aron phambi kwengqina, ibe ngumqondiso kubawexuki; uzisuse kum neendudumo zabo, ukuze bangafi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 11, 'Wenza ke uMoses, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho, wenjenjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 12, 'Bathetha oonyana bakaSirayeli kuMoses, bathi, Yabona, siyafa, siyabhubha, siyaphela sonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 17, 13, 'Nabani na osondela ententeni kaYehova uya kufa; Sodlula ekufeni na?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 1, 'Wathi uYehova kuAron, Wena noonyana bakho, nendlu kayihlo, nobuthwala ubugwenxa obenziwe kwindawo engcwele; wena noonyana bakho nobuthwala ubugwenxa bobubingeleli benu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 2, 'Abazalwana bakho, esizweni sakwaLevi, esizweni sikayihlo, wobasondeza nawe, banamathele kuwe, bakukhonze; ke wena noonyana bakho nokhonza phambi komnquba wesingqino.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 3, 'Boyigcina inkonzo yenu nenkonzo yomnquba uphela; kodwa mabangasondeli empahleni yengcwele nasesibingelelweni, hleze bafe, ningasondeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 4, 'Bohlangana nawe, bagcine umsebenzi wentente yokuhlangana emsebenzini wonke wenkonzo yentente; owasemzini akayi kuza kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 5, 'Gcinani inkonzo yengcwele nenkonzo yesibingelelo, ukuze kungabuyi kubuye umsindo koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 6, 'Yabonani, ndibathabathile abazalwana benu, abaLevi, phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli; ninikelwe ukuba nisebenze umsebenzi wentente yokuhlangana, kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 7, 'Wena noonyana bakho niya kwenza umsebenzi wobubingeleli benu ezintweni zonke eziphuma esibingelelweni, nangaphaya komkhusane; nokhonza; ndininikile ububingeleli benu njengesipho; yaye umxube osondelayo mawubulawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 8, 'Wathi uYehova kuAron, Yabona, mna ndikunika umsebenzi wezipho zam zonke ezingcwele zoonyana bakaSirayeli; ndiwunika wena noonyana bakho zibe ngumxhesho ongunaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 9, 'Yoba yeyakho kwizinto ezizezona zingcwele ezitshiswa ngomlilo: yonke iminikelo yabo yasemlilweni nayo yonke iminikelo yabo yasemlilweni nayo yonke iminikelo yabo yesono nayo yonke imibingelelo yabo yetyala abaya kuyinikela kum zingcwele kuwe noonyana bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 10, 'Niya kuyidla engcweleni kangcwele; yonke into eyindoda yozidla; mayibe ngcwele kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 11, 'Kwaye yeyakho; namaqashiso ezipho zabo, namaqashiso onke amaqashiso oonyana bakaSirayeli; ndikunika wena, noonyana bakho, neentombi zakho, nawe, ube ngummiselo ongunaphakade; bonke abahlambulukileyo endlwini yakho bowudla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 12, 'Yonke ioli etyebileyo, newayini entsha emnandi, nengqolowa, ulibo lwezo zinto baya kuzinika uYehova, ndikunika lona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 13, 'Zonke iintlahlela ezisezweni, abazizisa kuYehova, zoba zezakho; bonke abahlambulukileyo endlwini yakho mabadle.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 14, 'Zonke izinto ezingcwele kwaSirayeli zoba zezakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 15, 'Yonke into evula isizalo enyameni yonke abayizisa kuYehova, ebantwini nasezinkomeni, yoba yeyakho;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 16, 'Uze ukhululwe kumntwana onyanga-nye, ngokulinganisela kwakho iishekele ezintlanu ngokweshekele yengcwele, eziigera ezimashumi mabini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 17, 'Kodwa akunako ukuwakhulula ngokumisela amazibulo enkomo, namazibulo ezimvu, namazibulo eebhokhwe; bangcwele; igazi lawo ulitshize esibingelelweni, uqhumisele ngamanqatha awo abe livumba elithozamisayo, ukudla kwasemlilweni ke oko kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 18, 'Inyama yawo yoba yeyakho, njengetyeya eshukumayo, nanjengegxalaba lakho lasekunene.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 19, 'Yonke imisondezo engcwele, abayisondezayo oonyana bakaSirayeli kuYehova, ndiyinika wena, noonyana bakho, neentombi zakho ndawonye nawe, ukuba ibe ngumthetho ongunaphakade; ingumnqophiso wetyuwa ongunaphakade phambi koYehova. Nkosi kuwe, nakwinzala yakho, nakuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 20, 'Wathi uYehova kuAron, Ezweni labo akuyi kuba nalifa, akuyi kuba nasabelo phakathi kwabo; Ndim isahlulo sakho nelifa lakho phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 21, 'Uyabona, oonyana bakaLevi ndibanika zonke izishumi kwaSirayeli, ukuba zibe lilifa, ngenxa yomsebenzi wabo, wenkonzo yentente yokuhlangana;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 22, 'Oonyana bakaSirayeli mabangasondeli ententeni yokuhlangana ukususela ngoku, ukuze bangathwali isono baze bafe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 23, 'Ke bona abaLevi bosebenza umsebenzi wentente yokuhlangana, bathwale ubugwenxa babo; ibe ngummiselo ongunaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu, ukuze bangabi nalifa phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 24, 'Isishumi soonyana bakaSirayeli, abasizisa kuYehova umrhumo, ndasinika abaLevi sibe lilifa; ngenxa yoko ndathi kubo, Abayi kulidla ilifa phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 25, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 26, 'Thetha kubaLevi, uthi kubo, Ukuba nithe nathabatha koonyana bakaSirayeli isishumi endibanikayo, ukuba sibe lilifa lenu, nosondeza umsondezo waso kuYehova, osisahlulo seshumi sesishumi eso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 27, 'Lo mnikelo wenu uya kubalelwa kuni njengengqolowa yasesandeni nanjengokhozo lwesixovulelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 28, 'Nosondeza umsondezo kuYehova kuzo zonke izishumi zenu, enizithabathayo koonyana bakaSirayeli; nize ninike uAron umbingeleli umnikelo kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 29, 'Eziphoni zenu zonke nosondeza wonke umnikelo ophakanyiswa kuYehova, kweyona ilungileyo kuyo yonke, ube sisahlulo sayo esingcwele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 30, 'Uze uthi ke kubo, Ukuba nithabathile ezona zilungileyo kuzo, ziya kubalelwa kubaLevi, ziyimveliso yesixovulelo sewayini, ziyimveliso yesixovulelo sewayini;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 31, 'Zidleni kuzo zonke iindawo, nina nemizalwane yenu, kuba ngumvuzo wenu lowo ngomsebenzi wenu ententeni yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 18, 32, 'Ngako oko anisayi kusithwala isono, ukuba nithe nalususa ukulunga kwaso; ize ningazenzi inqambi izinto ezingcwele zoonyana bakaSirayeli, hleze nife.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses nakuAron, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 2, 'Oko ke ukuze kuqiniselwe umyalelo awawuwisayo uYehova, esithi, Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, bakuzisele imazi yenkomo ebomvu, egqibeleleyo, engathwali dyokhwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 3, 'Niyinike uElazare umbingeleli, ukuba ayikhuphele ngaphandle kweminquba, ixhelelwe phambi kobuso bakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 4, 'Umbingeleli uElazare wothabatha egazini layo ngomnwe wakhe aze atshize ngenxalenye yegazi layo izihlandlo ezisixhenxe kanye phambi kwentente yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 5, 'Woyitshisa inkomo phambi kwamehlo akhe; Mazitshiswe isikhumba sayo, nenyama yayo, negazi layo, ndawonye nomswane wayo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 6, 'Umbingeleli wothabatha umsedare nehisope nomthi omfusa aze aziphose ezo zinto phakathi kokutshiswa kwemazi yenkomo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 7, 'Umbingeleli wozihlamba iingubo zakhe, ahlambe emanzini, angene eminqubeni, abe yinqambi kude kuhlwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 8, 'Lowo ulitshisileyo wozihlamba iingubo zakhe emanzini, awuhlambe umzimba wakhe emanzini, abe ngongahlambulukanga kude kuhlwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 9, 'Uthuthu lwethokazi lenkomo indoda ehlambulukileyo yoluthabatha, ilubeke ngaphandle kweminquba endaweni ehlambulukileyo, lugcinelwe ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli, lube ngamanzi entsomi; kukuhlanjwa kwesono.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 10, 'Owola uthuthu lwethokazi lenkomo, wozihlamba iingubo zakhe, abe yinqambi, ahlwise; ibe ngummiselo ongunaphakade koonyana bakaSirayeli, nakowasemzini ophambukele phakathi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 11, 'Umntu ochukumisa ofileyo woba yinqambi iintsuku ezisixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 12, 'Wothi ngomhla wesithathu azihlambulule isono, nangomhla wesixhenxe wohlambuluka; Ukuba ke akazihlambululanga ngosuku lwesithathu, akayi kuba uhlambulukile ngomhla wesixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 13, 'Bonke abo bachukumisa ofileyo, bangazihlambululi isono, bawenza inqambi umnquba kaYehova; unqunyulwe kwaSirayeli loo moya; ngokuba engagalelwanga phezu kwakhe ngamanzi okuhlamba, woba yinqambi; ubunqambi bakhe busephezu kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 14, 'Nguwo lo umyalelo xa athe umntu wafela ententeni leyo: Bonke abangena ententeni leyo, nabo bonke abasukuba besesententeni leyo, boba ziinqambi iintsuku ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 15, 'Yonke into evulwayo, engenasigubungelo, engabotshwanga phezu kwayo, yoba yinqambi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 16, 'Umntu osukuba echukumisa umntu obulewe ngekrele, nokuba sisidumbu, nokuba lithambo lomntu, nokuba lingcwaba, woba yinqambi iintsuku ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 17, 'Baluzisa uthuthu lwenkomo etshiswayo yedini lesono kulowo uyinqambi, amanzi omthombo awagalela kulo ngesitya.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 18, 'Umntu ohlambulukileyo ufanele athabathe ihisope, ayifunxe emanzini, afefe ngayo intente, nasezityeni zonke, nakubantu ababelapho, nalowo uchukumise unyawo, nalowo woyisiweyo okanye obanjwe ukufa, okanye ingcwaba:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 19, 'Ohlambulukileyo makafefe oyinqambi ngomhla wesithathu nangomhla wesixhenxe; Wothi ngomhla wesixhenxe, azihlambe iingubo zakhe, ahlambe emanzini, ngokuhlwa abe uhlambulukile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 20, 'Kodwa umntu ongahlambulukanga aze angazihlambululi, loo mphefumlo wonqunyulwa ungabikho ebandleni, ngenxa yokuba uye wayenza inqambi ingcwele kaYehova; akatshizwanga ngamanzi okuhlamba ukungcola; akahlambulukile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 21, 'Woba ngumthetho ongayi kubuyela kubo, wokuba lowo ugalela amanzi omqondiso, azihlambe iingubo zakhe; nalowo uchukumisa amanzi okuhlamba woba yinqambi, ahlwise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 19, 22, 'Yonke into emchukumisayo oyinqambi yoba yinqambi; yaye umntu oyichukumisayo woba ngongahlambulukanga kude kuhlwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 1, 'Bafika oonyana bakaSirayeli, lonke ibandla, entlango yaseTsin ngenyanga yokuqala; bahlala abantu eKadeshe wafela khona uMiriyam, wangcwatyelwa khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 2, 'Akwabakho manzi apho ebandleni; babizela ndawonye ooMoses noAron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 3, 'Babambana abantu noMoses, bathi, Akwaba besife ukufa kwabazalwana bethu phambi koYehova!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 4, 'Yini na ukuba nilizise ibandla likaYehova kule ntlango, sifele kuyo, thina nemfuyo yethu?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 5, 'Yini na ukuba nisikhuphe eYiputa, nisizise kule ndawo imbi kangaka? asiyindawo yambewu, asiyoyamakhiwane, asiyiyo yeediliya, neyeerharnati; kwaye akukho manzi okusela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 6, 'Baphuma ooMoses noAron ebandleni, beza emnyango wentente yokuhlangana, bawa ngobuso, babonakala kubo ubuqaqawuli bukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 7, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 8, 'Thabatha intonga, ulibizele ndawonye ibandla, wena noAron umkhuluwa wakho, nithethe engxondorheni phambi kwamehlo abo; liya kubanika amanzi alo, ubakhuphele amanzi engxondorheni; liseze ibandla nemihlambi yalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 9, 'Wayithabatha uMoses intonga phambi koYehova, njengoko wamwiselayo umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 10, 'uMoses noAron balibizela ndawonye ibandla phambi kweliwa, bathi kulo: “Phulaphulani, nina banemvukelo! Sakhupha amanzi kweli litye na?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 11, 'Wasiphakamisa uMoses isandla sakhe, wayibetha ingxondorha ngentonga yakhe izihlandlo zazibini, aphuma amanzi amaninzi, lasela ibandla nemfuyo yalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 12, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses nakuAron, Ekubeni ningandivumelanga ukuba ndindingcwalise phambi koonyana bakaSirayeli, aniyi kusingenisa esi sikhungu ezweni endibanika lona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 13, 'Ngawo la amanzi aseMeribha; ngokuba bakreqa oonyana bakaSirayeli kuYehova, wazenza inqambi ngabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 14, 'uMoses wabuya wathuma abathunywa kukumkani wakwaEdom, obeseKadeshe, esithi, mzalwana, Sirayeli, uyazazi wena zonke iimbandezelo ezisihleleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 15, 'Behla oobawo, baya eYiputa, sahlala eYiputa imihla emininzi; asicaphukisa amaYiputa, thina noobawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 16, 'Sabiza kuYehova, waliva ilizwi lethu, wathuma isithunywa, sasikhupha eYiputa; yabona, siyiKadeshe, sisixeko esisekupheleni kwelizwe lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 17, 'Masicande ezweni lakho, asiyi kucanda emasimini nasezidiliyani, singaseli manzi equleni; sohamba emendweni wokumkani, singatyekeli ekunene nasekhohlo, side sidlule emideni yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 18, 'Wathi uEdom kuye, Musa ukuwela kum, hleze ndirhole ikrele lam, ndilwe nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 19, 'Bathi oonyana bakaSirayeli kuye, Sohamba ngomendo; ukuba mna nemfuyo yam singawasela amanzi akho, ndowahlawula; Ndiya nje, ndingenzi nantoni na eyenye, ndidlule ezinyaweni zam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 20, 'Wathi, Aniyi kudlula. Waza uEdom wamxabela ngamadoda amaninzi nangesandla esithe nkqi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 21, 'Ngenxa yoko wala uEdom ukubavumela oonyana bakaSirayeli ukuba bacande ezweni labo; Wemka ke uSirayeli, wemka kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 22, 'Banduluka eKadeshe oonyana bakaSirayeli, ibandla lonke, bafika entabeni yeHore.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 23, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses nakuAron entabeni yeHore, emdeni welizwe lakwaEdom, wathi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 24, '“uAron uya kuthatyathwa ebantwini bakowabo, ngenxa yokuba akayi kungena kwilizwe endilinike oonyana bakaSirayeli, ngenxa yokulivukela kwabo ilizwi lam emanzini aseMeribha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 25, 'Thabatha uAron noElazare unyana wakhe, ubanyuse entabeni yeHore.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 26, 'Umhlube ke uAron iingubo zakhe, umnxibe uElazare unyana wakhe, amthabathe uAron, amse ebantwini bakowabo, afele khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 27, 'Wenza uMoses njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho; benyuka eNtabeni yeHore phambi kwamehlo ebandla lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 28, 'uMoses wamhluba uAron iingubo zakhe, wazambathisa uElazare unyana wakhe; Wafela khona uAron encotsheni yentaba, behla uMoses noElazare entabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 20, 29, 'Lakubona lonke ibandla ukuba uAron ufile, bamlilela uAron imihla emashumi mathathu, yonke indlu kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 1, 'Ukumkani waseAradi, umKanan, owayehlala kwelasezantsi, weva ukuba amaSirayeli abeze ngeentlola. Waza walwa noonyana bakaSirayeli, wabathimba abanye kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 2, 'uSirayeli wamfungela uYehova, esithi, Ukuba uthe wabanikela aba bantu esandleni sam, ndoyiqalekisa imizi yabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 3, 'Waliva uYehova ilizwi lamaSirayeli, wawanikela amaKanan amaKanan baqalekisa bona nemizi yabo; wathi igama laloo ndawo yiHorma.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 4, 'Banduluka eNtabeni yeHore, ngendlela yoLwandle oluBomvu, bajikeleza ilizwe lakwaEdom; wadandatheka kakhulu abantu ngaloo ndlela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 5, 'Bathetha abantu kakubi ngoThixo nangoMoses, bathi, Nisikhuphe eYiputa, ukuze sifele entlango apha? ngokuba kungekho sonka namanzi; esi sonka sikhaphukhaphu yasicekisa umphefumlo wethu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 6, 'uYehova wathumela iinyoka ezinobuhlungu ebantwini, zabaluma abantu; kwafa abantu abaninzi bakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 7, 'Beza abantu kuMoses, bathi, Sonile, ngokuba sithethe kakubi ngoYehova nangawe; thandazani kuYehova ukuba azisuse kuthi ezi nyoka. Wabathandazela ke uMoses abantu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 8, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Zenzele inyoka eshushu, uyixhome emthini; yaye lowo ulunyiweyo uya kuphila, ukuba uthe wakukhangela kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 9, 'uMoses wenza inyoka yobhedu, wayixhoma esibondeni, yaye xa inyoka leyo yayiluma umntu, wayephila xa ebona inyoka yobhedu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 10, 'Banduluka oonyana bakaSirayeli, bamisa iintente eObhoti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 11, 'Banduluka eObhoti, bamisa eYebharim, entlango ephambi kwelakwaMowabhi, ngasempuma.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 12, 'Ukusuka apho banduluka baya kumisa iinkampu kwintlambo yaseSarede.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 13, 'Anduluka khona, amisa phesheya kweArnon, entlango, ezweni lama-Amori; ngokuba iArnon ngumda wakwaMowabhi, phakathi kwamaMowabhi nama-Amori.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 14, 'Kungenxa yoko le nto kuthiwa encwadini yeemfazwe zikaYehova, Oko wakwenzayo eLwandle oluBomvu, nasemithonjeni yaseArnon;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 15, 'nasemingxunyeni yezihlambo, ezihla ziye endaweni yokuhlala yaseAri, esemdeni wakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 16, 'Besuka khona, baya eBhere; Lilo eli iqula, awathetha ngalo uYehova kuMoses, esithi, Hlanganisa abantu, ndibanike amanzi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 17, 'Waza uSirayeli wavuma le ngoma: Tsiba, mthombo! cula ngayo:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 18, 'Bemba iqula izikhulu, zemba abathetheli babantu ngeentonga zabo, ngokomyalelo womthetheli-waka. Baphuma ke entlango, beza eMatana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 19, 'Basuka eMatana baya eNahaliyeli; basuka eNahaliyeli baya eBhamoti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 20, 'Bazishiya iiMoths, baya entilini ezweni lakwaMowabhi, endulini yePisga, ekhangelene neYesimon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 21, 'AmaSirayeli athumela abathunywa kuSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 22, 'ndicande ezweni lakho; Asiyi kusela manzi equla, kodwa sohamba emendweni wokumkani, side sidlule emdeni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 23, 'Ke uSihon akabavumelanga oonyana bakaSirayeli ukuba bacande ezweni lakhe; yaye wafika eYahashe walwa noSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 24, 'Bamoyisa oonyana bakaSirayeli ngohlangothi lwekrele, balihlutha ilizwe lakhe, bathabathela eArnon, besa eYabhoki, besa koonyana baka-Amon, ngokuba umda woonyana baka-Amon ubuliqele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 25, 'Bazithimba zonke ezo zixeko oonyana bakaSirayeli, yaye oonyana bakaSirayeli bahlala kuzo zonke izixeko zama-Amori naseHeshbhon nakwiidolophu zonke ezilapho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 26, 'Kuba iHeshbhon yayisisixeko sikaSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, owalwa nokumkani wokuqala wakwaMowabhi waza walithimba lonke ilizwe lakhe esandleni sakhe ukuya kufikelela eArnon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 27, 'Ngako oko abathetha ngemizekeliso bathi, Yizani eHeshbhon, umzi kaSihon wakhiwe, walungiswa;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 28, 'Ngokuba bekukho umlilo eHeshbhon, nelangatye emzini wakwaSihon; Wayibhukuqa iAri yakwaMowabhi, nabathetheli beentaba zeArnon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 29, 'Yeha, wena Mowabhi! Niphahlile nina bantu bakwaKamose! Oonyana bakhe ababesabile, neentombi zakhe wabanikela ekuthinjweni kuSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 30, 'Sabadubula; iHeshbhon yatshabalala ukuya kufikelela eDibhon, yaye sabatshabalalisa ukuya kufikelela eNofa ukuya kufikelela eMedebha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 31, 'Bahlala ke oonyana bakaSirayeli ezweni lama-Amori.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 32, 'uMoses wathumela ukuba kuyithabathe iYazere, bayithimba imizi, bawagqogqa ama-Amori abekuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 33, 'Bajika, benyuka ngendlela eya eBhashan; waphuma uOgi, ukumkani waseBhashan, eza kubakhawulela, yena nabantu bakhe bonke, ekulweni e-Edreyi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 34, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Musa ukumoyika; ngokuba ndimnikele esandleni sakho, yena nabantu bakhe bonke, nelizwe lakhe; uya kwenza kuye njengoko wenzayo kuSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, obemi eHeshbhon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 21, 35, 'Bamoyisa yena noonyana bakhe nabantu bakhe bonke, kwada akwabakho uphilayo, balithimba ilizwe lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 1, 'Banduluka oonyana bakaSirayeli, baya bamisa emfuleni wakwaMowabhi, ngasempumalanga kweYordan, malunga neYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 2, 'Wakubona uBhalaki, unyana kaTsipore, konke abekwenzile uSirayeli kuma-Amori.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 3, 'uMowabhi wanxunguphala kakhulu ngabantu, ngokuba bebaninzi; wakhwankqiswa uMowabhi ngoonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 4, 'Wathi uMowabhi kumadoda amakhulu akwaMidiyan, Ngoku esi sihlwele siya kudla konke okusijikelezileyo njengeenkomo, sidle ingca yelizwe. uBhalaki, unyana kaTsipore, ubengukumkani wakwaMowabhi ngelo xesha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 5, 'Wathuma abathunywa kuBhileham, unyana kaBhehore, kuPetros, osemlanjeni ezweni loonyana babantu bakowabo, ukuba bambize bathi, Yabona, kuphume abantu eYiputa; nabo bawugubungele umhlaba, bahlala ngasecaleni lam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 6, 'Yiza, undisindise aba bantu; ngokuba banzima kunam; mhlawumbi ndiya koyisa, ukuze sibe nokuboyisa kwaye sibagxothe ehlabathini; ngokuba ndiyazi ukuba osikelelayo usikelelwe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 7, 'Ngoko izikhulu zakwaMowabhi nezikhulu zakwaMidiyan zahamba nomvuzo wokuvumisa ezandleni zazo; beza kuBhileham, bamxelela amazwi kaBhalaki.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 8, 'Wathi kuwo, Lalani apha ngobu busuku; ndoninika ilizwi, njengoko uYehova aya kuthetha kum; Bahlala ke abathetheli bakwaMowabhi noBhileham.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 9, 'Wafika uThixo kuBhileham, wathi, Ngoobani na la madoda unawe?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 10, 'Wathi uBhileham kuThixo, uBhalaki unyana kaTsipore, ukumkani wakwaMowabhi, uthumele kum, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 11, 'Yabona, kukho uhlanga lwaseJiputa oluwugubungelayo umhlaba; yizani nindibone; mhlawumbi ndingaba nako ukuboyisa, ndibagxothe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 12, 'Wathi uYehova kuBhileham, Musa ukuhamba nawo; Musani ukubaqalekisa abantu, kuba basikelelwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 13, 'Wagqiba uBhileham kusasa, wathi kubathetheli bakaBhalaki, Hambani niye ezweni lenu; ngokuba uYehova uyala ukundivumela ndihambe nani.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 14, 'Besuka ke abathetheli bakwaMowabhi, baya kuBhalaki, bathi, Walile uBhileham ukuza nathi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 15, 'Waphinda uBhalaki wathuma abathetheli ababebekeke ngaphezu kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 16, 'Zafika ke kuBhileham, zathi kuye, uBhalaki, unyana kaTsipore, kwathiwa, Musa ukuthintela ukuza kum;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 17, 'Kuba ndokuzukisa kakhulu, ndikwenze konke ondixelela kona; yiza, undisindisele olu hlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 18, 'Waphendula uBhileham, wathi kubakhonzi bakaBhalaki, Angafanelana uBhalaki ethanda ukundinika indlu yakhe izele yisilivere negolide, andingekhe ndiwugqithe umlomo kaYehova, uThixo wam, ndenze okuncinane nokuba kokukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 19, 'Hlala apha ngobu busuku, ukuze ndiyazi into eya kundixelela yona uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 20, 'Wafika uThixo kuBhileham ebusuku, wathi kuye, Akufika la madoda eza kukubiza, suka uhambe nawo; kodwa nangona kunjalo, ilizwi endiya kukuxelela lona, kufuneka ulenze.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 21, 'Kwakusasa uBhileham, wayibopha idonki yakhe, wahamba nabathetheli bakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 22, 'Wavutha umsindo kaThixo ngokuba emkile. Sema isithunywa sikaYehova endleleni yomchasi. Wakhwela eesileni lakhe, nabakhonzi bakhe ababini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 23, 'Xa idonki yayibona ingelosi kaYehova imi endleleni ibambe ikrele layo elirholileyo; lathi gu bucala iesile, lasinga emaphandleni; uBhileham walibetha iesile, walijika endleleni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 24, 'Sema isithunywa sikaYehova endleleni yezidiliya, iludonga ngapha, iludonga ngapha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 25, 'Iesile lasibona isithunywa sikaYehova, laguqa, nonyawo lukaBhileham eludongeni, layibetha kwakhona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 26, 'Sahamba isithunywa sikaYehova, sema endaweni emxinwa, apho bekungekho ndlela yakucezela ekunene nasekhohlo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 27, 'Idonki leyo ithe yakusibona isithunywa sikaYehova, lasuka lawa, laqumba phantsi koBhileham, wavutha umsindo kaBhileham, walibetha ngentonga iesile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 28, 'Wawuvula ke uYehova umlomo we-esile, wathi kuBhileham, Ndikwenze ntoni na, ukuba undibethe kathathu nje?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 29, 'Wathi uBhileham kwiesile, Undiqumbisile nje, ukuba bendiphethe umkhonto esandleni sam, inene, ndithanda ukukubulala ngoku.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 30, 'Lathi iesile kuBhileham, Ubukhwele idonki yakho na, kususela kwakho oko unanamhla? Ngaba ndakha ndakwenza oko kuwe?” Wathi: “Hayi!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 31, 'Wawavula ke uYehova amehlo kaBhileham, wabona isithunywa sikaYehova simi endleleni, sirhole ikrele laso. Wathoba intloko yakhe, wawa ngobuso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 32, 'Sathi kuye isithunywa sikaYehova, Ulibethele ntoni na iesile lakho izihlandlo ezithathu? uyabona, ndiphumele kulwa nawe; ngokuba indlela yakho imbi emehlweni am.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 33, 'Idonki yandibona, yajika kathathu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 34, 'Wathi uBhileham kwisithunywa sikaYehova, Ndihlulekile; kuba bendingazi ukuba umi endleleni ngokundichasa; ndiphinde ndibuyele kuwe ukuba awundithandi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 35, 'Sathi isithunywa sikaYehova kuBhileham, Hamba naloo madoda; ke ilizwi endolithetha kuwe, uze uthethe lona lodwa. uBhileham wahamba nabathetheli bakaBhalaki.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 36, 'Weva uBhalaki ukuba uBhileham ufikile, waphuma wamhlangabeza emzini wakwaMowabhi, emdeni waseArnon, ngasemdeni wolwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 37, 'Wathi uBhalaki kuBhileham, Andikuthumelanga na ndikuthumela ukuba ndikubize? bekutheni ukuze ungezi kum?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 38, 'Wathi uBhileham kuBhalaki, Yabona, ndifikile kuwe; ndinawo amandla othetha nto ngoku? ilizwi aya kulibeka emlonyeni wam uThixo, ndiya kuthetha lona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 39, 'uBhileham wahamba noBhalaki, baya kufika eKiriyati-husoti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 40, 'Wabingelela uBhalaki iinkomo nempahla emfutshane, wazithumela kuBhileham nakubathetheli ababenaye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 22, 41, 'Ngengomso uBhalaki wamthabatha uBhileham, wamsa entabeni kaBhahali, ukuze alibone ikamva labantu khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 1, 'Wathi uBhileham kuBhalaki, Nditsalele apha izibingelelo zibe sixhenxe, undimisele khona iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe sixhenxe, neenkunzi zeegusha zibe sixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 2, 'Wenza ke uBhalaki njengoko wathethayo uBhileham; uBhalaki noBhileham baxhela inkunzi yenkomo nenkunzi yegusha kwisibingelelo ngasinye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 3, 'Wathi uBhileham kuBhalaki, Yima emlilweni wakho, ndihambe mna; mhlawumbi uYehova wondichasa; Wenyuka ke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 4, 'uThixo waqubisana noBhileham, wathi kuye, Ndalungisa izibingelelo zasixhenxe, ndaxhelela inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nenkunzi yemvu, kwisibingelelo ngesibingelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 5, 'uYehova wabeka ilizwi emlonyeni kaBhileham, lathi, Buya uye kuBhalaki, uthethe le nto.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 6, 'Wabuyela ke kuye, emi phambi kwedini lakhe elinyukayo, yena nabathetheli bonke bakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 7, 'Waprofeta wathi, uBhalaki, ukumkani wakwaMowabhi, undizise kwa-Aram, ezintabeni zasempumalanga, wathi, Yizani, msindiseni uYakobi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 8, 'Ndothini na ukuqalekisa angamqalekisiyo uThixo? Ndim nje, ingambanganga uYehova?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 9, 'Ngokuba ndiyambona, ndisencotsheni yamawa, ndisezindulini, ndiyambona; yabona, iintlanga ziya kuhlala zodwa, angabalwa phakathi kweentlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 10, 'Ngubani na ongalubalayo uthuli lwakwaYakobi, Nesahlulo sesine sakwaSirayeli ngokwenani? Mandife ukufa kwelungisa, Libe njengelalo ikamva lam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 11, 'Wathi uBhalaki kuBhileham, Yintoni na le nto undenze yona? Ndikuthabathele ukuba uziqalekise iintshaba zam, nanku uzithamsanqelisile;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 12, 'Waphendula yena, wathi, Oko akubekileyo uYehova emlonyeni wam, mandingakugcini na, ndikuthethe?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 13, 'Wathi uBhalaki kuye, Hamba siye ndaweni yimbi, apho uya kubabona; uya kubona kuphela ukugqithisela kwabo, ingabi bonke bephela; uze undicelele wona xa ulapho kum.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 14, 'Wamsa emhlabeni wakwaSofim, esangweni lasePisga, wakha izibingelelo ezisixhenxe; wabingelela inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nenkunzi yemvu, kwisibingelelo ngesibingelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 15, 'Wathi kuBhalaki, Yima apha ngasemlilweni wakho, ndihlangane noYehova khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 16, 'uYehova waqubisana noBhileham, wabeka ilizwi emlonyeni wakhe, wathi, Hamba uye kuBhalaki, uthethe naye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 17, 'Ekufikeni kwakhe kuye, nanko emi ngakumnikelo wakhe otshiswayo, kunye neenkosana zakwaMowabhi. Wathi uBhalaki kuye, Utsho uYehova?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 18, 'Wawuthetha ngomzekeliso wakhe, wathi, Yima, Bhalaki, uve; ndiphulaphule, nyana kaTsipore;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 19, 'uThixo akamntu ukuba axoke; nonyana womntu, ukuze azohlwaye; utsho kanti akunjalo? ethethile nje akaqondi?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 20, 'Yabona, ndamkele umthetho wokusikelela, wasikelela; kwaye andinako ukuyibuyisela umva.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 21, 'Akubona bubi kuYakobi, akubona nkohliso kuSirayeli; uYehova uThixo wakhe unaye, nesikhalo sokumkani siphakathi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 22, 'uThixo wabakhupha eYiputa; unamandla e-unicorn, ngokungathi kunjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 23, 'Akukho kuvumisa ngoYakobi, akukho kuvumisa ngoSirayeli; Ngeli xesha kuya kuthiwa kuYakobi nakuSirayeli, Yintoni na ayenzileyo uThixo!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 24, 'Yabona, abantu baya kuma njengengonyama enkulu, baziphakamise njengehobe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 25, 'Wathi uBhalaki kuBhileham, Musa ukubaqalekisa, uze ungabasikelele;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 26, 'Waphendula uBhileham wathi kuBhalaki, Ndathi, Bendingatshongo na kuwe, ndathi, Konke oko akuthethayo uYehova, ndiya kukwenza na?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 27, 'Wathi uBhalaki kuBhileham, Hamba ndikuse ndaweni yimbi; mhlawumbi kuya kumkholisa uThixo ukuba ufuna ndikubone apho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 28, 'uBhalaki wamsa uBhileham encotsheni yePehore, malungana noYesimon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 29, 'Wathi uBhileham kuBhalaki, Ndakhele apha izibingelelo zibe sixhenxe, undimisele apha iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe sixhenxe, neenkunzi zeegusha zibe sixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 23, 30, 'Wenza ke uBhalaki njengoko wathethayo uBhileham, wabingelela kwisibingelelo ngesibingelelo inkunzi entsha yenkomo nenkunzi yemvu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 1, 'Wabona uBhileham, ukuba uYehova ubefuna ukumthamsanqelisa uSirayeli, akasuka waya kuhlaba umkhosi njengakuqala, wabubhekisa ubuso bakhe entlango.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 2, 'Wawaphakamisa amehlo akhe uBhileham, wababona oonyana bakaSirayeli behleli ngokwezizwe zabo ezintenteni zakhe; uMoya kaThixo wamfikela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 3, 'Waqala ke umzekeliso wakhe, esithi, uBhileham unyana kaBhehore, otyhilwe amehlo, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 4, 'Wathi yena owawevayo amazwi kaThixo, wabubonayo ubuso boSomandla, weyiswa nguMoya, kodwa amehlo akhe avuleka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 5, 'Hayi, ukuba ntle kweentente zakho, Yakobi, Neminquba yakho, Sirayeli!', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 6, 'Njengeentlambo ezinentlambo, njengemiyezo ngasemlanjeni, njengemithi yekhala etyalwe nguYehova nanjengemisedare ngasemanzini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 7, 'Kuya kuphalala amanzi emithanjeni yakhe, imbewu yakhe ibe semanzini amaninzi, ukumkani wakhe aphakame ngaphezu koAgagi, buziphakamise ubukumkani bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 8, 'uThixo wamkhupha eYiputa; unamandla endongomane; uya kuzidla iintlanga zeentshaba zakhe, awaphule amathambo azo, aziphaluse ngeentolo zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 9, 'Wangqengqa, walala njengengonyama, nanjengengonyama enkulu; ngubani oza kumvusa? Unoyolo okusikelelayo, Uqalekisiwe okuqalekisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 10, 'Wavutha umsindo kaBhalaki kuBhileham, waqhwaba izandla; Wathi uBhalaki kuBhileham, Ndikubizele ukuba uziqalekise iintshaba zam, nanku, uzisikelele izihlandlo zazithathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 11, 'Ke ngoko, balekela ekhayeni lakho; ndikhumbule ukukuzukisa kakhulu; yabona, uYehova uyalucekisa uzuko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 12, 'Wathi uBhileham kuBhalaki, Andithethanga nam kubathunywa bakho, obubathumele kum;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 13, 'Angafanelana uBhalaki endinika indlu yakhe izele yisilivere negolide, andingekhe ndiwaphule umyalelo kaYehova, ngokwenza okulungileyo nokuba kokubi entliziyweni yam; kodwa oko akuthethayo uYehova, ndiya kuthetha kona?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 14, 'Kaloku yabona, ndiyahamba, ndiya ebantwini bakowethu; yiza ke, ndikuxelele okuya kukwenza olu hlanga kuhlanga lwakho ekupheleni kwemihla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 15, 'Waqala ke umzekeliso wakhe, esithi, uBhileham unyana kaBhehore, otyhilwe amehlo, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 16, 'Wathi, lowo uwevayo amazwi kaThixo nokwaziyo ukwazi kOyena Uphakamileyo, obona ubuso boSomandla ulala ubuthongo, kodwa amehlo akhe avulekile.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 17, 'Ndiya kumbona, kungekhona ngoku; Ndiya kumbona, kodwa kungekhona kufuphi; inkwenkwezi iya kuvela kwaYakobi, ivele intonga kwaSirayeli, ibethe eziphelweni zikaMowabhi, noonyana bonke bakaSete.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 18, 'uEdom abe bubutyebi, uSehire abe bubutyebi beentshaba zakhe; yaye uSirayeli uya kwenza ngenkalipho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 19, 'Umlawuli uya kuvela kwaYakobi, atshabalalise amasalela omzi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 20, 'Kwaye xa wabona uAmaleki, wathabatha umfanekiso wakhe waza wathi: uAmaleki wayengowokuqala phakathi kwezizwe; kodwa isiphelo sakhe siya kutshabalala ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 21, 'Wawabona amaKanan, eqhayisile, wathi, Isakhiwo sakho siqinile, nendlu yakho uyakha eweni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 22, 'Kodwa amaKanan aya kutshatyalaliswa ide iAsiriya iwathabathe ekuthinjweni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 23, 'Wathetha ngomzekelo wakhe, esithi, Ngubani na oya kubudla ubomi, ukuba uThixo uthe wenjenjalo?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 24, 'Kwaye iinqanawa ziya kuza zivela elunxwemeni lwaseKitim iyicinezele iAsiriya zize zicinezele uHebhere, yaye naye uya kutshabalala ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 24, 25, 'Wesuka ke uBhileham, wemka, wabuyela endaweni yakhe, wemka noBhalaki.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 1, 'uSirayeli wahlala eShitim, baza abantu bakrexeza neentombi zakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 2, 'Zababizela abantu emibingelelweni yoothixo bazo; badla abantu, baqubuda kwizithixo zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 3, 'AmaSirayeli azibandakanya noBhahali-pehore, waza uYehova wawavutha ngumsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 4, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Thabatha bonke abaziintloko zabantu, ubaxhome phambi koYehova, phezu kwelanga, ukuze ubuye umsindo kaYehova kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 5, 'Wathi uMoses kubagwebi bakwaSirayeli, Bulalani elowo emadodeni akowabo, elowo uzibophelele kuBhahali-pehore.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 6, 'Weza ke omnye woonyana bakaSirayeli, wamzisa umMidiyanekazi kubazalwana bakhe emehlweni kaMoses, nasemehlweni ebandla lonke loonyana bakaSirayeli, ababelila phambi komnyango wentente yakwaSirayeli ibandla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 7, 'Wakubona oko uPinehasi, unyana kaElazare, unyana ka-Aron umbingeleli, wema phakathi kwebandla, ephethe intshuntshe ngesandla sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 8, 'Wayilandela indoda leyo yakwaSirayeli ukuya ententeni, wabahlaba bobabini, indoda yakwaSirayeli nomfazi wayo esiswini. Ngoko ke isohlwayo soonyana bakaSirayeli siyaphetshwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 9, 'Abafayo ngesibetho baba ngamashumi amabini anesine amawaka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 10, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 11, 'uPinehasi, unyana kaElazare, unyana ka-Aron, umbingeleli, wawususa umsindo wam koonyana bakaSirayeli, ekukhweleteni kwakhe ngam, ukuze ndingabatshabalalisi oonyana bakaSirayeli ngekhwele lam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 12, 'Ngako oko uthi, Yabona, ndimnika umnqophiso wam woxolo,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 13, 'ube kuye nendlu yakhe emva kwakhe, umnqophiso ongabuyiyo wobubingeleli; ngokuba ebenekhwele ngoThixo wakhe, wabacamagushela oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 14, 'Igama lendoda engumSirayeli, eyahlatywayo, yabulawa kunye nomMidiyanekazi, belinguZimri, unyana kaSalu, umthetheli womkhosi woonyana bakaSimon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 15, 'Igama lenkazana leyo yahlatywayo ingumMidiyanekazi, belinguKoshebhi, intombi kaTsure; wayeyintloko yohlanga nendlu yasebukhosini yakwaMidiyan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 16, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 17, 'Wacinezeleni amaMidiyan, niwoyise;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 25, 18, 'Kuba banikhathaza ngeminqweno yabo abanilukuhlayo ngayo kwimeko kaPehore nakwimeko kaKoshebhi, intombi yenkosana yakwaMidiyan, udade wabo, owabulawa ePehore ngomhla wesibetho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 1, 'Emva kokufa kwesibetho, wathetha uYehova kuMoses nakuElazare, unyana ka-Aron, umbingeleli, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 2, 'nilibale lonke ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli, bethabathela kominyaka imashumi mabini ezelwe, banyuse, ngokwezindlu zabo, bonke abaphuma umkhosi kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 3, 'Wathetha uMoses noElazare umbingeleli kubo ezinkqantosini zakwaMowabhi ngaseYordan malunga neYeriko, besithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 4, 'Bala abantu, uthabathele kominyaka imashumi mabini ezelwe, unyuse; njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses, noonyana bakaSirayeli, ababephuma ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 5, 'uRubhen, amazibulo kaSirayeli, ngoonyana bakaRubhen; uEnoki, owazalelwa kuye indlu kaEnoki; kwaPalu, endlwini kaBhapalu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 6, 'kuHetseron ozala amaHetseron; kuKarmi ozala amaKarmi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 7, 'Yiyo leyo imizalwane yamaRubhen, ngokwababhaliswayo kubo ngamashumi omane anamathathu amawaka, anamakhulu asixhenxe, anamanci mathathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 8, 'Oonyana bakaPalu nguEliyabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 9, 'Oonyana bakaEliyabhi yayinguNemuweli noDatan noAbhiram. NgooDatan noAbhiram, ababazekayo ebantwini, balwa noMoses noAron eqenjini likaKora, ekulweni kwabo noYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 10, 'umhlaba wawuvula umlomo wawo, wabatshisa kunye neKore ekufeni kwesihlwele, ekutshatyalalisweni komlilo amadoda angamakhulu amabini anamanci mahlanu, aba ngumqondiso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 11, 'Kodwa oonyana bakaKora abazange bafe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 12, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaSimeyon ngokweentsapho zabo: KuNemuweli yintsapho kaNemuweli; nendlu kaYamin; eYagin, endlwini kaBhajagin;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 13, 'kwaSeraki, endlwini kaBhezerege; kuSawule indlu yakwaSawule.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 14, 'Yiyo leyo imizalwane yamaSimon: amashumi amabini anamabini amawaka, anamakhulu mabini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 15, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaGadi ngokwemizalwane yabo: kwaTsefon yindlu kaTsefon; ngoHagi wendlu kaBhahagi; kuSuni intsapho yamaSunni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 16, 'kuOsheni ozala amaBhasni; ngoEri, indlu kaBhaheri;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 17, 'kuArodi ozala ama-Arodi; ngoAreli indlu kaBhahareli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 18, 'Zizo ezi izizukulwana zoonyana bakaGadi, ngokwenani labo: amashumi amane amawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 19, 'Oonyana bakaYuda nguEre no-Onan; bafela ezweni lakwaKanan uEre no-Onan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 20, 'Oonyana bakaYuda bema ngokwemizalwane yabo; iSela, yindlu yabazalwayo; ePersi yintsapho yamaPersi; nguSeraki, wendlu kaBhezeregi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 21, 'Oonyana bakaPershe ngoonyana bakaPershe; eHetseron, endlwini yamaHetseron; ngoHamule, indlu kaBhahamule.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 22, 'Yiyo leyo imizalwane yakwaYuda, ngokwababhaliswayo kubo: ishumi elinesithandathu lamawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 23, 'Koonyana bakaIsakare ngokwemizalwane yabo: nguTola owazala isizwe sakwaTola; kumaPuwa kwisizwe sakwaPune;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 24, 'ngakuYashubhi, kwindlu kaYashubhi; eShimron, endlwini yamaShimron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 25, 'Zizo ezo ke inzala kaIsakare, ngokwababhaliswayo kubo: amashumi amathandathu anesine amawaka, anamakhulu mathathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 26, 'Koonyana bakaZebhulon ngokwemizalwane yabo: kuSerede ozala amaSardesi; kuElon, yindlu kaBhalon; ngoYahaleli, kwindlu kaYahalele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 27, 'Zizo ezo ke inzala zamaZebhulon ngokwenani labo: amashumi amathandathu anesihlanu amawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 28, 'Oonyana bakaYosefu ngokwemizalwane yabo nguManase noEfrayim.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 29, 'Koonyana bakaManase: nguMagire ozala amaGire; uMagire wazala uGiliyadi; eGiliyadi kwaphuma isizwe sakwaGiliyadi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 30, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaGiliyadi: KuYezere yintsapho yamaYezere; kwaHeleki kwindlu kaHeleki;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 31, 'nguAseriyeli ozala oonyana bakaSirayeli; noShekem indlu yabakwaShekem;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 32, 'kuShemida ozala uBhashemida; kuHefere ozala amaHefere.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 33, 'uTselofadi, unyana kaHefere, ebengenanyana, eneentombi zodwa; yaye amagama eentombi zikaTselofehadi yayinguMagala noNowa noHogela noMileka noTiresa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 34, 'Zizo ezo izizwe zakwaManase, yaye ababhaliswayo baba ngamashumi amahlanu anesibini amawaka anamakhulu asixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 35, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaEfrayim ngokweentsapho zabo: NguNashela yintsapho yamaShutela; eBheger, endlwini kaBhabhaki; eTahane, endlwini kaBhatahan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 36, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaSutela: kwaEran yintsapho kaBhaheran.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 37, 'Zizo ezi izizukulwana zoonyana bakaEfrayim, ngokwababhaliswayo kubo, baba ngamashumi amathathu anesibini amawaka anamakhulu mahlanu. Ngabo abo oonyana bakaYosefu ngokweenzala zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 38, 'Oonyana bakaBhenjamin ngokwemizalwane yabo: nguBhela ozala amaBhabheli; kuAshebele ozala uBhaasebele; ngoAhram, indlu ka-Akim;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 39, 'ngaseSufam, yindlu kaSufam; eHufame yintsapho kaBahufame.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 40, 'Oonyana bakaBhela nguArede noNahaman; eArede, endlwini kaBhaharadi; kuNahaman yintsapho kaBhanama.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 41, 'Ngabo abo oonyana bakaBhenjamin ngokweentsapho zabo, yaye ababhaliswayo baba ngamashumi amane anesihlanu amawaka anamakhulu mathandathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 42, 'Ngabo aba oonyana bakaDan ngokwemizalwane yabo: kuShuham ozala amaShuham. Yiyo leyo imizalwane yakwaDan ngokwemizalwane yabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 43, 'Yonke imizalwane yakwaShuham, ngokwababhaliswayo kubo, ngamashumi omathandathu anesine amawaka, anamakhulu mane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 44, 'Oonyana baka-Ashere ngokwemizalwane yabo: nguImna ozala uImna; kumaJesuit yintsapho yamaJesuits; nguBheriya, indlu kaBhabhariya.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 45, 'Koonyana bakaBheriya: kwaHebhere yintsapho yamaHebhere; kwaMalekiyeli, indlu kaMalekiyeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 46, 'Igama lentombi ka-Ashere belinguSara.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 47, 'Yiyo leyo imizalwane yoonyana baka-Ashere ngenani labo; ibingamashumi amahlanu anamathathu amawaka, anamakhulu mane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 48, 'Oonyana bakaNafetali ngokwemizalwane yabo: nguYatsele ozala amaYatsele; ngakuGuni indlu kaBhaguni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 49, 'eYizere, endlwini yamaYizere; kwaSilleme yintsapho kaBasilme.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 50, 'Zizo ezo iintsapho zakwaNafetali ngokweentsapho zabo, yaye ababhaliswayo baba ngamashumi amane anesihlanu amawaka anamakhulu mane.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 51, 'Ngabo abo ababalwayo koonyana bakaSirayeli: amakhulu omathandathu amawaka anawaka-nye, anamakhulu asixhenxe, anamanci mathathu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 52, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 53, 'Ilizwe liya kwabelwa bona, libe lilifa, ngokwenani lamagama;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 54, 'Abaninzi wobanika ilifa labaninzi, abambalwa nobanika ilifa elincinane; elowo uya kunikwa ilifa lakhe, njengoko babalwayo ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 55, 'Liya kwabelwa ilizwe ngamaqashiso, balidle ilifa ngokwamagama emizalwane yooyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 56, 'Ngokwesiphelo, ubutyebi bayo buya kwabelwa abaninzi nabambalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 57, 'Ngabo aba ababhaliswayo kubaLevi ngokweentsapho zabo: KuGershon yintsapho yamaGershon; eKehati, endlwini yamaHeti; ngaseMerari, kwindlu yamaMerari.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 58, 'Yiyo le imizalwane yakwaLevi: yintsapho yamaLibheni, yintsapho yamaHebhere, yintsapho yamaMagali, yintsapho yamaMushi, yintsapho yamaKore. Ke uKehati wazala uAmram.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 59, 'Igama lomka-Amram belinguYogebhede, intombi kaLevi, owazala uLevi eYiputa; uAmram wazala uAron noMosis noMiriyam udade wabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 60, 'uAron wazalelwa uNadabhi noAbhihu, uElazare noItamare.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 61, 'Yaye uNadabhi noAbhihu bafa ngenxa yokuzisa loo mlilo ungekho mthethweni phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 62, 'Ababalwayo kubo baba ngamashumi amabini anamathathu amawaka, yonke into eyindoda, ethabathela kunyana onyanga-nye inyuse; ngenxa yokuba ayengabhalwanga phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, ekubeni engazange anikwe lifa phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 63, 'Ngabo abo ababhaliswayo nguMoses noEleyazar umbingeleli owabalayo oonyana bakaSirayeli emathafeni akwaMowabhi ngaseYordan ngaseYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 64, 'Ke kubo kube kungekho namnye wabababalayo uMoses noAron umbingeleli, ekubabaleni kwabo oonyana bakaSirayeli entlango yaseSinayi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 26, 65, 'Kuba uYehova wathi ngabo: “Baya kufela entlango akwasala namnye kubo, yaba nguKalebhi unyana kaYefune, noYoshuwa, unyana kaNun.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 1, 'Zangena iintombi zikaTselofehadi, unyana kaHefere, unyana kaGiliyadi, unyana kaMagire, unyana kaManase, zendlu kaManase, unyana kaYosefu; ngawo la amagama eentombi zakhe; uMagla, uNowa, uHogla, uMilka, noTirsa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 2, 'Zema phambi koMoses naphambi koElazare umbingeleli, naphambi kwezikhulu, nebandla lonke, emnyango wentente yokuhlangana, zathi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 3, 'Ubawo wafela entlango, akakho eqeleni lababehlanganisene kuYehova kwiqela lamaKore; kodwa wafa esonweni sakhe, engenanyana.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 4, 'Yini na ke ukuba igama likabawo licinywe phakathi kwemizalwane yakhe, kuba engenanyana? Ke kaloku siphe ubutyebi phakathi kwabazalwana bakabawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 5, 'uMoses wasibeka isimangalo sawo phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 6, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 7, 'Iintombi zikaTselofehadi zathetha zalungisa, zathi, Zozinika ilifa phakathi kwabazalwana bakayise; yaye ilifa likayise malidlulele kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 8, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi, Xa ithe yafa indoda ingenanyana, nolidlulisela ilifa layo kwintombi yayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 9, 'Ukuba ithe ayaba nantombi, ilifa layo nilinike abantakwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 10, 'Ukuba ithe ayaba nabazalwana, ilifa layo nilinike abazalwana bakayise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 11, 'Ukuba uyise uthe akaba nabazalwana, ilifa layo ulinike oyena usondeleyo kuye wegazi emizalwaneni yayo, alidle ilifa; ube ngumyalelo wokugweba koonyana bakaSirayeli, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 12, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Nyuka uye kule ntaba yeAbharim, ulikhangele ilizwe endilinike oonyana bakaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 13, 'Ukuba uyayibona le nto, nawe uya kususwa ebantwini bakowenu, njengoko wahlanganiswayo umkhuluwa wakho uAron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 14, 'Kuba nawuvukela umyalelo wam entlango yaseSine ngexesha laxa ibandla lalixoxisana nalo, ngokundingcwalisa ngamanzi phambi kwamehlo alo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 15, 'Wathetha uMoses kuYehova, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 16, 'uYehova, uThixo wemiphefumlo yenyama yonke, makamisele indoda yokulawula ibandla;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 17, 'onokuthi aphume phambi kwabo, angene phambi kwabo, abakhuphe, abakhuphe; ukuze lingabi njengezimvu ezingenamalusi ibandla likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 18, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Thabatha uYoshuwa unyana kaNun, indoda okuyo umoya, ubeke isandla sakho phezu kwakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 19, 'ummise phambi koElazare umbingeleli, naphambi kwebandla lonke; wamwisela umthetho emehlweni abo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 20, 'Beka phezu kwakhe isidima sakho, ukuze liphulaphule lonke ibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 21, 'Uya kuma phambi kombingeleli uEleyazare, aze yena abuze kuye ngokwesiko leUrim phambi koYehova; Bophuma ngokomlomo wakhe, bangene ngokomlomo wakhe, yena noonyana bonke bakaSirayeli, nebandla lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 22, 'Wenza uMoses ngoko uYehova wamwisela umthetho ngako; wamthabatha uYoshuwa, wammisa phambi koElazare umbingeleli naphambi kwebandla lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 27, 23, 'Wabeka izandla zakhe phezu kwakhe, wamwisela umthetho, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho ngoMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 2, 'Bawisele umthetho oonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Ndiziseleni umbingelelo wam, nesonka sam semibingelelo yam, sibe livumba elithozamisayo kum, ngexesha elimisiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 3, 'Uze uthi kubo, Kuko oku ukudla kwasemlilweni eniya kuwuzisa kuYehova; iimvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo, zemini ngemini, zedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 4, 'Nilungise enye imvana kusasa, nilungise enye imvana ngokuhlwa;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 5, 'nesahlulo seshumi se-efa yomgubo ocoliweyo, ube ngumnikelo wokudla, ugalelwe ioli esisahlulo sesine sehin.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 6, 'Lidini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, liphuma entabeni yeSinayi, livumba elithozamisayo, kukudla kwasemlilweni ke oko kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 7, 'nomnikelo wayo othululwayo woba sisahlulo sesine sehin kwimvana enye; uya kugalela iwayini enxilisayo engcweleni, ibe ngumnikelo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 8, 'Enye imvana woyenza ngokuhlwa; Wowenza idini elinyukayo lakusasa, nomnikelo walo othululwayo, ukudla kwasemlilweni, ivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 9, 'Ngomhla wesabatha iinkunzi zeemvana ezigqibeleleyo ezineminyaka emibini ubudala nezahlulo ezibini zesishumi zomgubo ocoliweyo zibe ngumnikelo wokudla okuziinkozo ogalelwe ioli nomnikelo wawo othululwayo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 10, 'Lidini elinyukayo ke elo lesabatha ngesabatha, ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 11, 'Ekuthwaseni kweenyanga zenu nosondeza kuYehova idini elinyukayo; neenkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe mbini, nenkunzi yemvu ibe nye, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe sixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 12, 'nezahlulo zeshumi zomgubo ocoliweyo zibe zithathu, ube ngumnikelo wokudla, ugalelwe ioli, kuyo inkunzi entsha enye yenkomo; nezahlulo zeshumi zomgubo ocoliweyo zibe zibini, ube ngumnikelo wokudla, ugalelwe ioli, kuyo inkunzi enye yemvu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 13, 'nezahlulo zeshumi zomgubo ocoliweyo, ugalelwe ioli, ube ngukudla kwasemlilweni kuyo imvana enye. Lidini elinyukayo, livumba elithozamisayo, kukudla kwasemlilweni kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 14, 'umnikelo wazo othululwayo woba sisiqingatha sehin kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nesahlulo sesithathu sehin kuyo inkunzi yegusha, nesahlulo sesine sehin kuyo imvana. Lidini elinyukayo lenyanga ngenyanga yomnyaka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 15, 'Konikelwa ngenkunzi yegusha enye ibe ngumnikelo wesono kuYehova ngaphandle komnikelo otshiswayo othe rhoqo nomnikelo wawo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 16, 'Ngosuku lweshumi elinesine enyangeni yokuqala, yipasika kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 17, 'Ngomhla weshumi elinesihlanu waloo nyanga ngumthendeleko; izonka ezingenagwele zodliwa iintsuku ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 18, 'Ngomhla wokuqala kobakho intlanganiso engcwele; ningenzi namnye umsebenzi ngayo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 19, 'Nosondeza ukudla kwasemlilweni, idini elinyukayo kuYehova; neenkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe mbini, nenkunzi yemvu enye, neemvana ezisixhenxe; nibe ngongenakusoleka kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 20, 'Nomnikelo wazo wokudla woba ngumgubo ocoliweyo, ogalelwe ioli, izahlulo zeshumi zibe zithathu kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kuyo inkunzi yemvu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 21, 'Wosondeza izahlulo zeshumi zibe sixhenxe kuyo imvana enye, kuzo iimvana ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 22, 'Nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti ibe nye, ibe lidini lesono lokunicamagushela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 23, 'Lilungiselele ndawonye nedini elinyukayo lakusasa, lona idini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 24, 'Ngoko imihla yonke, iintsuku ezisixhenxe nolungiselela inyama yomnikelo otshiswayo, olivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 25, 'Ngomhla wesixhenxe kobakho intlanganiso engcwele kuni; ningenzi namnye umsebenzi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 26, 'Kananjalo, ngomhla wentlahlela, ukuba nizisa umnikelo omtsha wasemlilweni kuYehova emva kokuphela kweeveki zenu, yoba yindibano engcwele kuni; ningenzi namnye umsebenzi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 27, 'Wolungiselela idini elinyukayo, libe livumba elithozamisayo kuYehova; neenkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe mbini, nenkunzi yemvu enye, neemvana ezisixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 28, 'nomnikelo wazo wokudla womgubo ocoliweyo, ugalelwe ioli, izahlulo zeshumi zibe zithathu kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kuyo inkunzi yemvu inye;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 29, 'nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kuyo imvana enye, kuzo iimvana ezisixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 30, 'Nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti ibe nye, yokunicamagushela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 28, 31, 'Nize niyenze ndawonye nedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla (zoba zezigqibeleleyo kuni), neminikelo yazo ethululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 1, 'Ngenyanga yesixhenxe, ngolokuqala enyangeni leyo, kobakho intlanganiso engcwele kuni ningenzi namnye umsebenzi; yimini yesigodlo kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 2, 'Wosondeza idini elinyukayo, libe livumba elithozamisayo kuYehova; yanye inkunzi entsha, inkomo, nenkunzi yemvu yanye, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe sixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 3, 'Umsondezo wazo woba ngumgubo ocoliweyo, ugalelwe ioli, izahlulo zeshumi zibe zithathu kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kuyo inkunzi yemvu,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 4, 'nesahlulo seshumi ngasinye kuyo imvana enye kuzo iimvana ezisixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 5, 'nenkunzi yemvu ibe nye, yedini lesono, yokunicamagushela:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 6, 'ngaphandle komnikelo otshiswayo wenyanga nomnikelo wawo wokudla okuziinkozo nomnikelo otshiswayo othe rhoqo nomnikelo wawo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yawo ethululwayo ngokwesiko lawo, ibe ngumnikelo wasemlilweni olivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 7, 'Ngolweshumi enyangeni leyo, kobakho ibandla elingcwele kuni; kwaye niya kuyithoba imiphefumlo yenu; ungenzi namnye umsebenzi ngayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 8, 'Nosondeza idini elinyukayo kuYehova, ivumba elithozamisayo; yanye inkunzi entsha, inkomo, nenkunzi yemvu yanye, neemvana ezisixhenxe; buya kulunga kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 9, 'Umsondezo wazo woba ngumgubo ocoliweyo, ugalelwe ioli, izahlulo zeshumi zibe zithathu kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo, nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kuyo inkunzi yemvu inye,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 10, 'nesahlulo seshumi sibe sinye kuyo imvana enye, kuzo iimvana ezisixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 11, 'yanye inkunzi yemvu yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini lesono, nedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo wazo wokudla, kwaneminikelo yazo ethululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 12, 'Ngosuku lweshumi elinesihlanu enyangeni yesixhenxe, kobakho ibandla elingcwele kuni; nize ningenzi namnye umsebenzi wokukhonza, nimenzele umthendeleko uYehova iintsuku ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 13, 'Ninikele idini elinyukayo, ukudla kwasemlilweni ivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova; neenkunzi zeenkomo ezilishumi elinantathu, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezilishumi elinane; baya kufuna isiphene.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 14, 'Nomnikelo wazo woba ngumgubo ocoliweyo, ugalelwe ioli, izahlulo zeshumi zibe zithathu kuyo inkunzi entsha yenkomo inye, kuzo iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo ezilishumi elinantathu, nezahlulo zeshumi zibe zibini kwinkunzi yemvu inye, kuzo iinkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 15, 'nesahlulo seshumi ngasinye kuyo imvana inye kuzo iimvana ezilishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 16, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti ibe nye, ibe lidini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 17, 'Ngosuku lwesibini nobingelela iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe lishumi elinambini, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 18, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 19, 'nenkunzi yemvu ibe nye, ibe lidini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo wokudla, kwaneminikelo yazo ethululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 20, 'Ngosuku lwesithathu nosondeza iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe lishumi elinanye, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 21, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 22, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 23, 'Ngosuku lwesine nosondeza iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe lishumi, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 24, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo, ngokwenkqubo yazo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 25, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti ibe nye; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 26, 'Ngosuku lwesihlanu nosondeza iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe sithoba, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 27, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 28, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 29, 'Ngosuku lwesithandathu nosondeza iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe sibhozo, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 30, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 31, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 32, 'Ngosuku lwesixhenxe nosondeza iinkunzi ezintsha zeenkomo zibe sixhenxe, neenkunzi zezimvu zibe mbini, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo zibe lishumi elinane;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 33, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo yeenkunzi zeenkomo, iinkunzi zeegusha neenkunzi zeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 34, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 35, 'Ngosuku lwesibhozo kuya kubakho umthendeleko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 36, 'Nosondeza idini elinyukayo, ukudla kwasemlilweni, ivumba elithozamisayo kuYehova, ibe nye; ibe nye inkunzi entsha, ithole lenkomo, nenkunzi yemvu ibe nye, neemvana ezimnyaka mnye ezigqibeleleyo, zibe sixhenxe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 37, 'Umnikelo wazo wokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yazo ethululwayo kuyo inkunzi yenkomo, nenkunzi yegusha, nenkunzi yeemvana, ufanele ube ngangenani lazo ngokwesiko;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 38, 'nenkunzi yebhokhwe exhonti yedini lesono; ngaphandle kwedini elinyukayo lamaxesha onke, nomnikelo walo wokudla, kwanomnikelo walo othululwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 39, 'Niya kuzenzela ezi zinto kuYehova emithendelekweni yenu, ngaphandle kwezibhambathiso zenu neminikelo yenu yokuzithandela, iminikelo yenu etshiswayo neminikelo yenu yokudla okuziinkozo neminikelo yenu ethululwayo nemibulelo yenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 29, 40, 'uMoses wabaxelela oonyana bakaSirayeli njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 1, 'Wathetha uMoses kwiintloko zezizwe zoonyana bakaSirayeli, wathi, Yiyo le into awise umthetho ngayo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 2, 'Xa athe umntu wenza isibhambathiso kuYehova, nokuba ufunge isifungo sokuwubopha umphefumlo wakhe ngokuzikhanyeza; akalihlambeli ilizwi lakhe, uya kwenza ngako konke okuphuma emlonyeni wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 3, 'Ukuba umfazi uthe wenza isibhambathiso kuYehova waza wazibopha ngoxa esendlwini kayise ebutsheni bakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 4, 'Uyise uya kuziphulaphula izibhambathiso zakhe, nezibhambathiso zakhe, uthi cwaka uyise kuye; emva koko zonke izibophelelo zakhe ziya kuqina, kwaye zonke izibophelelo azenzileyo, ziya kuqina.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 5, 'Ukuba uyise uthe wamshiya ngomhla wokuva kwakhe oko; ukuba angabi nasinye kwizifungo zakhe azifungeleyo; uYehova womxolela, ngokuba ethe wamwisela umthetho ngako uyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 6, 'Ukuba ithe ngendoda, ithe yabhambathisa isibhambathiso, nokuba ithe ngelizwi layo eliphuma emlonyeni wayo, ebizibophe ngalo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 7, 'Yakuva indoda yakhe, yathi cwaka kuye ngomhla wevayo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 8, 'Ukuba ithe indoda yakhe yamnqanda ngomhla eyakuva ngayo oko; mayenze isibhambathiso kumkayo, ekuthethileyo ngomlomo wayo, ebophe umphefumlo wayo ngako, ekuyikhanyeni; uYehova uya kumxolela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 9, 'Sonke isibhambathiso somhlolokazi nesomfazi owaliweyo, abophe ngaso umphefumlo wakhe, soma phezu kwakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 10, 'Ukuba ithe yenza isibhambathiso endlwini yendoda yayo, nokuba ithe ibophe umphefumlo wayo ngako ngesifungo, isifungo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 11, 'Yakuva indoda yakhe, yathi cwaka kuye, akamvumela; emva koko zonke izibophelelo zakhe ziya kuqina, kwaye zonke izibophelelo azenzileyo, ziya kuqina.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 12, 'Kodwa ukuba indoda yakhe ithe yasitshabalalisa, mhla yakuva ngaso; ngoko okuphuma emlonyeni wakhe malunga nokuzibophelela kwakhe okanye malunga neqhina lomphefumlo wakhe akuyi kubakho; indoda yakhe yayisitshabalalisa; uYehova uya kumxolela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 13, 'Zonke izifungo nezifungo zokuwucinezela umphefumlo indoda yakhe ingasimisa, nokuba indoda yakhe ingasitshitshisa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 14, 'Ke ukuba indoda yakhe ithe cwaka kuye yonke imihla, woba siso oko; kulapho aqinisekisa khona zonke izibophelelo zakhe, okanye zonke izibophelelo zakhe eziphezu kwakhe; uyaziqinisa, ngokuba wayelele naye ngalaa mini wayivayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 15, 'Ukuba uthe wayiva, wayitshabalalisa; uya kubuthwala khona ubugwenxa bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 30, 16, 'Yiyo leyo imithetho ayimiseleyo uYehova phakathi kwendoda nomkayo, phakathi koyise nentombi yakhe, isemncinci endlwini kayise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 2, 'Xelela amaMidiyan koonyana bakaSirayeli; emva koko uya kusiwa ebantwini bakowenu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 3, 'Wathetha uMoses ebantwini, wathi, Zilungiseleni imfazwe, niwaxabele amaMidiyan, nixele kuYehova wakwaMidiyan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 4, 'Thumelani iwaka esizweni ukuba liye edabini ezizweni zonke zakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 5, 'Kumawaka akwaSirayeli, iwaka, esizweni, iwaka esizweni, ishumi elinamabini lamawaka axhobele imfazwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 6, 'uMoses wabathuma emfazweni, iwaka esizweni, bona noPinehasi, unyana wombingeleli uElazare, emfazweni, beneempahla ezingcwele, namaxilongo okukhalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 7, 'Awaxabela ke amaMidiyan, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses; babulala yonke into eyindoda.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 8, 'Ababulala ookumkani bamaMidiyan ngaphandle kwabo bonke ababulawayo; ezizezi: uEwi, noRekem, noShure, noHure, noRebha, ookumkani abahlanu bamaMidiyan; noBhileham, unyana kaBhehore, wababulala ngekrele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 9, 'Oonyana bakaSirayeli babathimba abafazi bakwaMidiyan, nabantwana babo, nemfuyo yabo yonke, nempahla yabo yonke, nempahla yabo yonke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 10, 'Imizi yabo yonke ababehlala kuyo, neengqili zabo zonke bazitshisa ngomlilo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 11, 'Bawathimba onke amaxhoba nezinto zonke ezithinjiweyo, abantu neenkomo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 12, 'Bandula ke babazisa abathinjwa namaxhoba nezinto eziphangiweyo kuMoses nakuEleyazare umbingeleli nakwibandla loonyana bakaSirayeli ababesenkampini entlango yakwaMowabhi naseYordan ngaseYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 13, 'Baphuma ooMoses noElazare umbingeleli nezikhulu zonke zebandla, baya kubakhawulela ngaphandle kweminquba.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 14, 'uMoses wanoburhalarhume kubo abathetheli bamaqela, namawaka abathetheli, namakhulu abathetheli-waka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 15, 'Wathi uMoses kubo, Nibakhuphe na abafazi bonke behleli?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 16, 'Yabona, yabenza oonyana bakaSirayeli kuYehova ngenxa kaPehore, ngelizwi likaBhileham; kwaza kwabakho ukufa phezu kwebandla likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 17, 'Yibulaleni ngoko yonke into eyindoda phakathi kosapho;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 18, 'Ke zonke iintsana zabafazi abazanga zibe nandoda ngokulala nayo; zigcineni nina.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 19, 'Hlalani ngaphandle kweminquba iintsuku ezisixhenxe. Bonke ababulele umntu, nabo bonke abasukuba bemchukumisa obulewe, zenzeni nyulu, nina nabo nibathimbileyo ngomhla wesithathu nangomhla wesixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 20, 'Zihlambeni zonke iingubo zenu, neempahla zonke zezintsu, nezinto zonke zoboya bebhokhwe, nezinto zonke ezenziwe ngomthi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 21, 'Wathi umbingeleli uElazare kumagorha aphume umkhosi, umthetho uYehova awamwisela uMoses umthetho ngawo waqinisekiswa ngawo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 22, 'igolide, nesilivere, nobhedu, nesinyithi, nebhekile, nelothe;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 23, 'Yonke into enokumelana nomlilo, woyigalela emlilweni, ihlambuluke; nangona kunjalo, kufuneka icocwe ngamanzi adibeneyo; yaye bonke abo bangenako ukumelana nomlilo, babasasaze emanzini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 24, 'Zihlambeni iingubo zenu ngomhla wesixhenxe; nohlambuluka ke, ningene emveni koko eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 25, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 26, 'Thatha inani lamaxhoba, abantu neenkomo, wena noElazare umbingeleli, neentloko zezindlu zooyise zebandla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 27, 'Ukwahlula ixhoba libe ziinxalenye ezimbini; phakathi kwabaphuma umkhosi, abaphuma umkhosi, naphakathi kwebandla lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 28, 'Nihlawule irhafu kumadoda omkhosi owaphuma umkhosiumkhosi kuYehova: umphefumlo ubemnye kumakhulu amahlanu, amadoda, neenkomo, namaesile, neegusha;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 29, 'Thabatha isiqingatha kuzo, unike uElazare umbingeleli, njengomnikelo ovela kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 30, 'Esiqingatheni soonyana bakaSirayeli wothabatha ibe nye, ibe nye, nakuzo iinkomo, nakuwo amaesile, nakuwo amaesile, nakuzo iinkomo, kuzo zonke iindidi zeenkomo, uzinike abaLevi abaluse impahla emfutshane inkonzo yomnquba kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 31, 'Wenza uMoses noElazare umbingeleli njengoko uYehova wamwisela umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 32, 'Ke amaxhoba lawo, awayeshiyeke ekuphangeni, awathimbayo amadoda omkhosi, yaba ngamakhulu omathandathu amawaka, anamanci asixhenxe anesihlanu amawaka;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 33, 'ngamashumi omathandathu anesibini amawaka eenkomo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 34, 'ngamashumi omathandathu amawaka anawaka elinye lamaesile;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 35, 'kubo bonke abafazi abangayazanga indoda ngokulala nayo, ngamashumi omathathu anesibini amawaka amadoda.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 36, 'Isiqingatha sesabelo sabaphuma umkhosi, saba ngamakhulu amathathu anamanci mathathu anesixhenxe samawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu amawaka eegusha;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 37, 'Irhafu kaYehova yeegusha yayingamakhulu amathandathu anamashumi amathandathu anesihlanu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 38, 'Iinkomo, ngamashumi omathathu amawaka, anesithandathu samawaka; kubo irhafu yokumkani ibingamashumi amathandathu anesibini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 39, 'Amaesile, ngamashumi omathathu amawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu; kubo irhafu kaYehova yaba ngamashumi amathandathu ananye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 40, 'Abantu ishumi elinesithandathu lamawaka; kubo irhafu kaYehova yaba ngabantu abangamashumi amathathu anesibini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 41, 'uMoses wamnika uElazare umbingeleli irhafu, engumnikelo kaYehova, njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 42, 'Isiqingatha soonyana bakaSirayeli, awabahlulayo uMoses emadodeni okulwa;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 43, 'Isiqingatha sebandla, ngamakhulu amathathu, anamanci mathathu anesixhenxe, anamakhulu mahlanu amawaka;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 44, 'ngamashumi omathathu anesithandathu amawaka eenkomo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 45, 'ngamashumi omathathu amawaka, anamakhulu mahlanu amaesile;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 46, 'neshumi elinesithandathu lamawaka abantu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 47, 'Wacaphula uMoses esiqingatheni soonyana bakaSirayeli into emashumi mahlanu, ebantwini nasezinkomeni, wazinika abaLevi ababesebenza ententeni kaYehova; njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 48, 'Basondela kuMoses abathetheli-waka, nabathetheli-waka, nabathetheli-khulu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 49, 'Bathi kuMoses, Abakhonzi bakho bawabalile amadoda okulwa, asesandleni sethu; akukho nanye engekhoyo kuthi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 50, 'Sazisa ke kuYehova ukudla kwasemlilweni, sawafumana elowo nalowo, amatye egolide, nemixokelelwane, nezacholo, nezacholo, namajikazi, namajikazi, neetafile, ukuba siyicamagushele imiphefumlo yethu phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 51, 'Wayithabatha uMoses noElazare umbingeleli igolide kubo, inguwo wonke umsebenzi owenziwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 52, 'Iyonke igolide yomrhumo ababeyizisa kuYehova yaba ziishekele ezilishumi elinesithandathu lamawaka, namakhulu asixhenxe anamanci mahlanu, evela kubathetheli-waka, nakubathetheli bekhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 53, 'Ngokuba amadoda okulwa azihlutha elowo indawo yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 31, 54, 'Wayithabatha uMoses noElazare umbingeleli igolide kubathetheli-waka nabamakhulu, bayizisa ententeni yokuhlangana, ukuze ibakhumbuze oonyana bakaSirayeli phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 1, 'Oonyana bakaRubhen noonyana bakaGadi baye benempahla emfutshane emininzi; alibona ilizwe laseYazere nelizwe laseGiliyadi, yayiyindawo yeenkomo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 2, 'Beza oonyana bakaGadi noonyana bakaRubhen, bathetha kuMoses, nakuElazare umbingeleli, nakumadoda amakhulu ebandla, bathi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 3, 'neAtaroti, neDibhon, neYazere, neNimra, neHeshbhon, ne-Elale, neSebham, neNebho, neBhehon;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 4, 'Ilizwe eloyiswa nguYehova phambi kwebandla likaSirayeli lilizwe lemfuyo, yaye abakhonzi bakho banemfuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 5, 'Bathi ngoko, Ukuba usibabale, abakhonzi bakho mabanikwe elo zwe, ukuba libe lelabo, ungasiwezi eYordan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 6, 'Wathi uMoses koonyana bakaGadi noonyana bakaRubhen, Abazalwana benu baya emfazweni, nihlale apha na nina?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 7, 'Yini na ukuba nizithethe iintliziyo zoonyana bakaSirayeli, ukuba bawele baye ezweni abanika lona uYehova?', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 8, 'Benjenjalo ooyihlo ekubathumeni kwam siseKadeshe-bharneha ukuba baye kuhlola ilizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 9, 'Xa benyuka baya kwintlambo yomlambo oqukuqelayo wase-Eshkoli baza balibona ilizwe, bazityhafisa iintliziyo zoonyana bakaSirayeli, ukuze bangangeni kwilizwe abanika lona uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 10, 'Wavutha umsindo kaYehova ngelo xesha, wafunga wathi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 11, 'Ngokuba akuyi kulibona nalinye kuloo madoda anyukayo ephuma eYiputa, ethabathela kominyaka imashumi mabini ezelwe, anyuse, ilizwe endalifungela uAbraham noIsake noYakobi; ngenxa yokuba bengandilandeli ngokupheleleyo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 12, 'ingenguKalebhi unyana kaYefune, umKeni, noYoshuwa, unyana kaNun; ngokuba babekufunge uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 13, 'Wavutha umsindo kaYehova koonyana bakaSirayeli, wawabhadulisa entlango iminyaka emashumi mane, sada satshabalala sonke isizwe, ebesenza okubi emehlweni kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 14, 'Yabonani, nisuke ngenxa yooyihlo, inkitha yaboni, niwongeza ubushushu bomsindo kaYehova kumaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 15, 'Xa nithe natyeka kuye, wophinda abasalise entlango; yaye uya kulutshabalalisa olu hlanga luphela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 16, 'Basondela kuye, bathi, Izibaya zempahla emfutshane siya kubakhela emhlambini wethu, nemizi yabantwana bethu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 17, 'Ke thina siya kuphuma sixhobile, sihambe phambi koonyana bakaSirayeli, side sibaseendaweni yabo; nabantwana bethu abancinane baya kuhlala kwizixeko ezikhuselekileyo ngenxa yabemi behlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 18, 'Asiyi kubuyela ezindlwini zethu, bade oonyana bakaSirayeli bazuze elowo ilifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 19, 'Kuba asiyi kubakhohlisa phesheya kweYordan nangaphaya; ngokuba ilifa lethu liphesheya kweYordan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 20, 'Wathi uMoses kubo, Ukuba nithe nenjenjalo, ekuphumeni kwenu kuYehova, nixhobele ukulwa,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 21, 'Nowela iYordan nixhobile phambi koYehova, ade azigxothe iintshaba zakhe phambi kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 22, 'Ilizwe liya kuthotywa ebusweni bukaYehova; eli lizwe libe bubutyebi benu phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 23, 'Ke ukuba aniyenzi loo nto, yabonani, noba nonile kuYehova; kwaye uqiniseke ukuba isono sakho sikufumene.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 24, 'Zakheleni imizi oonyana benu, nezibaya zempahla yenu emfutshane; wenze okuphuma emlonyeni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 25, 'Bathetha oonyana bakaGadi noonyana bakaRubhen, bathi, Abakhonzi bakho baya kwenza njengoko inkosi yam iwise umthetho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 26, 'Oonyana bethu, nabafazi bethu, neenkomo zethu, nemfuyo yethu yonke, yoba semizini yaseGiliyadi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 27, 'Ke abakhonzi bakho baya kuwela, bexhobele imfazwe, bonke bexhobele imfazwe phambi koYehova, njengoko yathethayo inkosi yam.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 28, 'uMoses wamwisela umthetho ngabo umbingeleli uElazare, noYoshuwa unyana kaNun, neentloko zezindlu zoonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 29, 'Wathi uMoses kubo, Ukuba oonyana bakaGadi noonyana bakaRubhen bawela nani iYordan, boyiswa bonke abaxhobileyo phambi koYehova, loyiswa ilizwe phambi kwenu; wandule ke ubanike ilizwe laseGiliyadi ukuba libe bubutyebi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 30, 'Ke ukuba abathanga bawele bexhobile nani, bohlala phakathi kwenu ezweni lakwaKanan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 31, 'Baphendula oonyana bakaGadi noonyana bakaRubhen, bathi, Siya kwenza njengoko uYehova wabawisela umthetho abakhonzi bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 32, 'Thina sohlala sixhobile phambi koYehova, singene ezweni lakwaKanan, libe lelethu ilifa lethu nganeno kweYordan ngasempumalanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 33, 'uMoses wabanika oonyana bakaGadi, noonyana bakaRubhen, nesiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase, unyana kaYosefu, nobukumkani bukaSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, nobukumkani bukaOgi ukumkani waseBhashan, nelizwe namadlelo alo, iidolophu ezisemaphandleni.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 34, 'Oonyana bakaGadi bakha iDibhon, neAtaroti, neArohere;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 35, 'neAtroti, neShofan, neYazere, neYogebheha;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 36, 'neBhete-nimra, neBhete-haran, imizi enqatyisiweyo, nezibaya.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 37, 'Oonyana bakaRubhen bakha iHeshbhon, ne-Elehali, neKiriyatayim;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 38, 'neNebho, neBhahali-mehon, awaguquka amagama awo, neSibhema; nezixeko bazakha ngamanye amagama.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 39, 'Oonyana bakaMagire, unyana kaManase, baya eGiliyadi, bayithimba, bawagqogqa ama-Amori abekuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 40, 'uMoses wamnika iGiliyadi uMagire, unyana kaManase; wahlala kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 41, 'uYayire unyana kaManase waya wayithimba imizana yakhe, wayibiza ngokuba yiHavoti-yahire.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 32, 42, 'uNobha waya wayithimba iKenati namagxamesi alapho, wathi yiNobha ngegama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 1, 'Zizo ke ezi iimfuduka zoonyana bakaSirayeli, abaphumayo ezweni laseYiputa ngokwemikhosi yabo, ngesandla sikaMoses noAron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 2, 'Wakubhala uMoses ukuphuma kwabo ngokweehambo zabo ngokomlomo kaYehova; Zizo ke ezi iimhambo zabo ngokweehambo zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 3, 'Banduluka eRamses ngenyanga yokuqala, ngosuku lweshumi elinesihlanu lwenyanga yokuqala; Ngengomso emva kwepasika, baphuma oonyana bakaSirayeli ngesandla esiphakamileyo, emehlweni amaYiputa onke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 4, 'AmaYiputa abafihla onke amazibulo awo, awawabulalayo uYehova phakathi kwawo; uYehova wabohlwaya noothixo bawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 5, 'Banduluka oonyana bakaSirayeli eRameses bamisa iinkampu eSukoti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 6, 'Banduluka eSukoti, bamisa e-Etam, enyeleni yentlango.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 7, 'Emva koko banduluka e-Etam babuyela ePi-hagiroti ephambi kweBhahali-tsefon baza bamisa iinkampu phambi kweMigdoli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 8, 'Emva koko banduluka ePihagiroti bawela ulwandle baya entlango baza bahamba uhambo lweentsuku ezintathu entlango ye-Etam baza bamisa iinkampu eMara.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 9, 'Banduluka eMara baya e-Elim, yaye e-Elim kwakukho imithombo yamanzi elishumi elinesibini nemithi yesundu engamashumi amathandathu; bamisa iintente khona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 10, 'Emva koko banduluka e-Elim bamisa iinkampu ngakuLwandle lwaseSkelf.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 11, 'Banduluka eShelfeshe, bamisa entlango yeZine.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 12, 'Banduluka entlango yaseSin, bahamba batyala iDofka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 13, 'Banduluka eDofka, beza kuAluse.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 14, 'Bemka ke eAlus, bamisa eRafidim, apho kwakungekho manzi okuba abantu basele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 15, 'Emva koko banduluka eRefidim bamisa iinkampu entlango yeSinayi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 16, 'Emva koko banduluka entlango yeSinayi bamisa iinkampu eKibroti-hataha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 17, 'Banduluka eKibroti-hataweva, bamisa eHatseroti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 18, 'Banduluka eHatseroti, bamisa iinkampu eRitma.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 19, 'Banduluka eRitma bamisa iinkampu eRimon-pere.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 20, 'Banduluka eRimon-peretse, bamisa eLibhena.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 21, 'Banduluka eLibhena, bamisa eRisa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 22, 'Banduluka eRisa bamisa iinkampu eKehelati.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 23, 'Banduluka eKehelati, bamisa iintente entabeni eSafer.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 24, 'Banduluka eNtabeni iSafa, bamisa iinkampu eHarada.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 25, 'Banduluka eHarada, baya kumisa iiMekelo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 26, 'Emva koko banduluka eMaheloti bamisa iinkampu eTahati.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 27, 'Banduluka eTahati, beza eTara.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 28, 'Banduluka eTara, bamisa eMitka.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 29, 'Banduluka eMitka, bamisa eHashmona.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 30, 'Emva koko banduluka eHasmona bamisa iinkampu eMoseroti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 31, 'Banduluka eMoseroti, bemka kwaBhenjakan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 32, 'Banduluka kwaBhenjan, bamisa iinkampu eHorhagidegade.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 33, 'Ekundulukeni kwabo eHore-hagidegadi bamisa iinkampu eYotebhata.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 34, 'Emva koko banduluka eYotebhata bamisa iinkampu eAbron.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 35, 'Emva koko banduluka eAbron bamisa iinkampu e-Etsiyon-gebhere.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 36, 'Emva koko banduluka e-Etsiyon-gebhere bamisa iinkampu entlango yeTsin, eyiKadeshe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 37, 'Banduluka eKadeshe, bamisa entabeni yeHore, ekupheleni kwelizwe lakwaEdom.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 38, 'uAron umbingeleli wenyuka waya entabeni yeHore ngokomyalelo kaYehova, wafela khona ngomnyaka wamashumi omane wokuphuma koonyana bakaSirayeli eYiputa, ngosuku lokuqala lwenyanga yesihlanu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 39, 'uAron ebeminyaka ilikhulu elinamanci mabini anamithathu ezelwe, ekufeni kwakhe entabeni yeHore.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 40, 'Weva umKanan, ukumkani waseAradi, obemi kwelasezantsi ezweni lakwaKanan ukuba bafikile oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 41, 'Banduluka eNtabeni yeHore, bamisa iintente eTalmon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 42, 'Banduluka eSalmona, beza ePunon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 43, 'Emva koko banduluka ePunone bamisa iinkampu eObhoti.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 44, 'Banduluka eObhoti, baya kuma eIye-abharim, emdeni wakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 45, 'Bemka eIime, bayimisa iDibongade.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 46, 'Bemka eDibongade baya kuhlala eAlmondi-Blataime.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 47, 'Banduluka eAlmon-dihlatayim, bamisa ezintabeni zeAbharim malunga neNebho.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 48, 'Banduluka ezintabeni zeAbharim, bamisa ezinkqantsoni zakwaMowabhi, ngaseYordan malunga neYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 49, 'Bamisa ngaseYordan, bethabathela eBhete-yeshimoti, besa eAbhele-shitim, ezinkqantosini zakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 50, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses ezinkqantosini zakwaMowabhi ngaseYordan, malunga neYeriko, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 51, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Xa nithe nayiwela iYordan, nisiya ezweni lakwaKanan;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 52, 'Bagxotheni ke ngoko bonke abemi belizwe phambi kwenu, niyitshabalalise yonke imifanekiso yabo eqingqiweyo, nizitshabalalise zonke izithixo zabo ezinqatyisiweyo, nizidilize zonke iziganga zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 53, 'Bagxotheni abemi belizwe, nihlale kulo; kuba ndininikile ilizwe elo ukuba nilihluthe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 54, 'Lahlula ilizwe ngamaqashiso, libe lilifa kwizizukulwana zenu; Onomnika ilifa elikhulu, libe likhulu, omncinane nibanike ilifa elincinane; ilifa lomntu wonke loba sendaweni eliya kuwela kuyo iqashiso lakhe; niya kulidla ilifa kwizizukulwana zooyihlo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 55, 'Kodwa ukuba akubagqogqanga abemi belizwe phambi kwakho; ndonishiya, nihlale njengamatye emehlweni enu, namatye emacaleni enu, nithotywe ezweni enihleli kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 33, 56, 'Kothi, njengoko ndagqibayo ukwenza kubo, ndenze ngako kuni;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 2, 'Bawisele umthetho oonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Xa nithe nafika ezweni lakwaKanan; (Lilo eli ilizwe eliya kuwela kuni njengelifa, ilizwe lakwaKanan nemida yalo.)', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 3, 'Umda wawo ngasezantsi wothabathela entlango yeTsin, use ngasemdeni wakwaEdom;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 4, 'Umda wenu wojika, uthabathele ezantsi, uye eqhineni leAkrabhim, udlule uye eSine; usuke ezantsi, uye eKadeshe-bharneha, udlulele eHatsaredare, udlulele eAshmon.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 5, 'Umda uya kusuka eAshmon, uye emlanjeni waseYiputa; umda wawo ume ngolwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 6, 'Umda wasentshonalanga umda wenu woba luLwandle Olukhulu; lo ngumda wenu wasentshonalanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 7, 'Umda wenu wangasentla uya kuba nguwo lo: Ukusuka kuLwandle Olukhulu uya kuthi ga kwiNtaba yeHore;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 8, 'nithabathela entabeni yeHore, nide nise eHamati; ukusuka emdeni yiSedade;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 9, 'wegqitha umda eZifron, uye eHasarenan; lo ngumda wenu wangasentla.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 10, 'Nize nizikhethele umda wenu wasempumalanga ukusuka eHatsare-nan ukuya eSefame.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 11, 'Umda uya kuhla usuka eSefame uye eRibhela, ngasempumalanga kwaseAyin; yaye umsonto uya kuhla uze udlulele ngakwicala loLwandle lwaseKinneret ngasempuma.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 12, 'Wehla umda waya eYordan, usiya eLwandle lweTyuwa; loba lilizwe lenu nelizwe lalo ngeenxa zonke kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 13, 'uMoses wabawisela umthetho oonyana bakaSirayeli, esithi, Lilo eli ilizwe enilihluthe ngeqashiso, awisa umthetho uYehova ukuba linikwe izizwe ezisithoba, nesiqingatha sesizwe, ndaweni-nye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 14, 'Ngokuba isizwe soonyana bakaRubhen ngokwezindlu zooyise, nesizwe soonyana bakaGadi, ngokwezindlu zooyise, sithabathé ilifa laso; nesiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase sanikwa ilifa laso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 15, 'Izizukulwana ezibini ezinesiqingatha zalifumana ilifa lazo nganeno kweYordan, malunga neYeriko, zibheke empumalanga, zibheke ngasempumalanga.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 16, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 17, 'Ngawo la amagama amadoda aya kunabela ilizwe: uElazare umbingeleli noYoshuwa unyana kaNun.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 18, 'Zithabatheleni isikhulu esinye kwisizwe ngasinye, sahlule ilizwe ngokwelifa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 19, 'Ngawo la amagama aloo madoda: Kwisizwe sakwaYuda, nguKalebhi unyana kaYefune;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 20, 'kwintsapho yoonyana bakaSimon nguSemuweli unyana ka-Amihudi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 21, 'kwisizwe sakwaBhenjamin nguElidade, unyana kaKislon;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 22, 'emizaneni yoonyana bakaDan, ukumkani uBhuki, unyana kaYogli;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 23, 'kwintsapho yoonyana bakaManase, ukumkani woonyana bakaYosefu, inguHaniyeli, unyana kaEfodi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 24, 'kwisizwe soonyana bakaEfrayim, ingukumkani uKemuweli, unyana kaSifetan;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 25, 'inkulu yesizwe soonyana bakaZebhulon, ibinguElishafan, unyana kaParanaki;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 26, 'kwintsapho yoonyana bakaIsakare, ukumkani uPaltiyeli, unyana ka-Asan;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 27, 'inkulu yendlu yoonyana baka-Ashere, ibinguAkihudi, unyana kaShelom;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 28, 'esizweni soonyana bakaNafetali ibinguPedayeli, unyana ka-Amihudi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 34, 29, 'Ngabo abo uYehova wabawisela umthetho wokuba bahlule ilifa loonyana bakaSirayeli ezweni lakwaKanan.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 1, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses entlango yakwaMowabhi, ngaseYordan, malunga neYeriko, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 2, 'Bawisele umthetho oonyana bakaSirayeli, ukuba banike abaLevi ilifa labo emizini abahlala kuyo; yabanika amadlelo abaLevi emizini yabo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 3, 'Baya kuba nemizi yokuhlala; amadlelo abo abe ngaweenkomo zabo, naweenkomo zabo, nawempahla yabo yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 4, 'Idlelo lezo zixeko liya kunikwa abaLevi, lithabathele eludongeni lwesixeko libe ziikubhite eziliwaka macala onke;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 5, 'nilinganise nithabathela ngaphandle komzi, iikubhite ezingamawaka amabini ngasempumalanga, zibe ziikubhite ezingamawaka amabini ngasemzantsi, neekubhite ezingamawaka amabini ngasentshonalanga, neekubhite ezingamawaka amabini ngasentla; yaye isixeko siya kuba sesazulwini, siya kuba ngamadlelo azo ezixeko.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 6, 'Imizi eniya kuyinika abaLevi yoba nemizi emithathu yokusabela, noyinika lowo unibuleleyo, abalekele kuyo; nokongeza kuyo imizi engamashumi amane anesibini.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 7, 'Zonke izixeko eniya kuzinika abaLevi zoba ngamashumi amane anesibhozo; wolinika kunye nedlelo labo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 8, 'Izixeko eniya kuzithabatha kwilifa loonyana bakaSirayeli; mnikeni into eninzi; kodwa kwabancinane, nize nibanike kancinane; ngasinye ezixekweni zaso siya kubanika abaLevi ngokwelifa laso, esidle ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 9, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 10, 'Thetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, uthi kubo, Xa nithe nayiwela iYordan, nongena ezweni lakwaKanan;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 11, 'nize nizinyulele ke izixeko eniya kuba zikhululekile; ukuze abalekele khona umbulali lowo ubulele umntu ngengozi.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 12, 'Yoba yimizi yenu leyo yokusabela kumphindezeli; ukuze angafi umbulali lowo, emi phambi kwebandla ukuze agwetywe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 13, 'Izixeko eniya kubanika zona zoba nezixeko ezithandathu zokusabela.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 14, 'Nobanika izixeko ezithathu nganeno kweYordan, nize nibanike izixeko ezithathu ezweni lakwaKanan, zibe ziidolophu ezikhululekileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 15, 'Loo mizi mithandathu yoba yeyokusabela koonyana bakaSirayeli, nakumphambukeli, nakowasemzini ophakathi kwenu;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 16, 'Ukuba uthe wambetha umntu ngentsimbi, wafa, ungumbulali; umbulali makabulawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 17, 'Ukuba uthe wambetha ngelitye, angafayo ngalo, wafa, ungumbulali; umbulali makabulawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 18, 'Nokuba uthe wambetha ngento engumthi, angáfa ngayo, wafa, ungumbulali; umbulali makabulawe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 19, 'Onxanelwe igazi wombulala umbulali; ukuba uthe waqubisana naye, wombulala.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 20, 'Ukuba uthe wamtyhalela ngentiyo, nokuba uthe wambetha ngezwi elikhulu, wafa;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 21, 'Okanye umbethe ngobutshaba ngesandla, wafa; ombethileyo wobulawa afe; ngokuba ungumbulali lowo; umphindezeli wegazi wombulala umbulali lowo, akuqubisana naye.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 22, 'Ukuba ke uthe wamtyhala ngesiquphe, kungekho lutshaba, nokuba wamgibisela nokuba yintoni na, engalindelanga;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 23, 'nokuba ngelitye, athe wafa umntu ngalo, engamboni, wamgibisela ngalo;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 24, 'Lize ligwebe ibandla phakathi kweqela labalindi nenani legazi ngokwemimiselo le:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 25, 'Ibandla limhlangule umbulali esandleni samagazi, limbuyisele ibandla emzini okhululekileyo, abebalekela kuwo; ahlale kulo ade afe umbingeleli omkhulu, athanjiswe ngeoli engcwele.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 26, 'Ukuba umbulali lowo uthe wangena nangaliphi na ixesha ngaphandle komda wesixeko esikhululekileyo ebebalekele kuso;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 27, 'Inani legazi lamfumana ngaphandle kwemida yomzi wakhe okhululekileyo, lathi inani legazi lambulala umbulali lowo makangabi natyala lagazi;', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 28, 'ngokuba wathanda ukuhlala emzini wakhe omkhulu, kwada kwafa umbingeleli omkhulu; kodwa emva kokufa kombingeleli omkhulu umbulali wobuyela emhlabeni welifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 29, 'Yoba ngumyalelo womgwebo kuni ezizukulwaneni zenu ezindaweni zonke enihlala kuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 30, 'Othe wabulala umntu, wobulawa umbulali lowo ngomlomo wamangqina; ke linye ingqina alinakungqina ngomntu ukuba ambulale.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 31, 'Ngaphezu koko, maningamkeli naluphi na ulwaneliseko ngenxa yomphefumlo wombulali ofanelwe kukufa, kodwa umele abulawe afe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 32, 'Uze ungamvumeli ukuba abuyele emzini okhululekileyo welizwe lakowabo, ade abhubhe umbingeleli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 33, 'Ize ningalihlambeli ilizwe enikulo, kuba igazi liyalihlambela ilizwe; nomhlaba awunakuhlanjululwa ngenxa yegazi eliphalazwe kuwo, ukuba kungengagazi lalowo uliphalazayo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 35, 34, 'Ize ningalihlambeli ilizwe enihlala kulo, endihleli kulo mna; kuba mna Yehova ndihleli phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 1, 'Zasondela iintloko zemizalwane yoonyana bakaGiliyadi, unyana kaMagire, unyana kaManase, zemizalwane yoonyana bakaYosefu, zathetha phambi koMoses, naphambi kwezikhulu, iintloko zezindlu zooyise oonyana bakaSirayeli:', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 2, 'Bathi ke, uYehova umwisele umthetho ukumkani wam ukuba abanike ilizwe oonyana bakaSirayeli ngokweqashiso, ukuba libe lilifa; yaye inkosi yam yayiyalelwe nguYehova ukuba ilifa likaSelofhade umzalwana wethu linike iintombi zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 3, 'Ukuba zithe zendela koonyana bezizwe zoonyana bakaSirayeli, loncitshiswa ilifa lazo elifeni loobawo, lisiwe elifeni lesizwe abathatyathelwe kuso, sisusiwe kwilifa lethu.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 4, 'Ekufikeni konyaka weNtlokoma woonyana bakaSirayeli, limele longezelelwe ilifa labo kwilifa lesizwe abasiwa kuso; ke ngoko, ilifa labo liya kushenxiswa kwilifa lesizwe soobawo.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 5, 'uMoses wabawisela umthetho oonyana bakaSirayeli ngokomlomo kaYehova, esithi, Imizalwane yoonyana bakaYosefu ilungisile ukuthetha.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 6, 'Lilo eli ilizwi awaliwisela umthetho uYehova ngeentombi zikaTselofehadi, wathi, Mazende kwabasukuba kufanelekile; mabatshate kumlibo kayise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 7, 'Ngoko ilifa loonyana bakaSirayeli alifanele lidlule kwesinye isizukulwana liye kwesinye, kuba oonyana bakaSirayeli bafanele bagcine elowo elifeni lesizukulwana sooyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 8, 'Yonke intombi enelifa esizweni soonyana bakaSirayeli yoba ngumfazi wesizwe sesizwe sikayise, ukuze oonyana bakaSirayeli badle ilifa ooyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 9, 'Ilifa aliyi kuphuma kwesinye isizukulwana liye kwesinye; kodwa sonke isizwe soonyana bakaSirayeli siya kuzigcina elifeni laso.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 10, 'Iintombi zikaTselofehadi zenza njengoko uYehova wamwisela umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 11, 'Ngokuba uMagala, noTirtsa, noHogela, noMilka, noNowa, iintombi zikaTselofehadi, zendela koonyana babazalwana bakayise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 12, 'Zendela emizalwaneni yoonyana bakaManase, unyana kaYosefu, laza ilifa labo lahlala emzalwaneni wooyise.', 'XHO22'),
(4, 36, 13, 'Yiyo leyo imiyalelo nezigwebo awabayalela ngazo uYehova ngoMoses oonyana bakaSirayeli kumathafa akwaMowabhi kufuphi neYordan malunga neYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 1, 'Ngawo la ke amazwi, awawathethayo uMoses kumaSirayeli onke phesheya kweYordan entlango, entlango malunga noLwandle oluBomvu, phakathi kweParan, neTofele, neLabhan, neHatseroti, neZagabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 2, '(Luhambo lweentsuku ezilishumi elinanye ukusuka eHorebhe ngendlela esuka kwintaba yakwaSehire ukuya eKadeshe-bharneha).', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 3, 'Ngomnyaka wamashumi omane, ngenyanga yeshumi elinanye, ngolokuqala enyangeni leyo, wathetha uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli ngako konke uYehova abemwisele umthetho ngako;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 4, 'Wababulala uSihon ukumkani wama-Amori, obemi eHeshbhon, no-Ogi ukumkani waseBhashan, obemi eAshtaroti e-Edreyi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 5, 'Waqala uMoses ukuwushumayela lo myalelo phesheya kweYordan ezweni lakwaMowabhi, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 6, 'Wathetha kuthi uYehova, uThixo wethu, eseHorebhe, wathi, Kukade nihleli kule ntaba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 7, 'Jikani, nihambe niye ezintabeni zama-Amori, nasezindaweni zonke ezikufuphi nazo, entlango, ezintabeni, nasezihlanjeni, nakwelasezantsi, naselwandle, nijikeleze ilizwe lamaKanan, nelizwe lamaKanan iintaba. iLebhanon ise emlanjeni omkhulu, umlambo umEfrati.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 8, 'Yabonani, ndinivelisela ihlabathi; Ngenani, nilidle ilifa ilizwe, awafungayo uYehova kooyihlo uAbraham, noIsake, noYakobi, ukuba wolinika bona, nembewu yabo emva kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 9, 'Ngelo xesha ndathetha kuni, ndathi, Andinakunithwala ndedwa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 10, 'uYehova uThixo wenu unandisile; nanku namhla ningangeenkwenkwezi zezulu, ukuba nibe baninzi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 11, 'Wanga uYehova uThixo wooyihlo, anandise ngaphezu kwenu kaliwaka, anisikelele njengoko wathethayo kuni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 12, 'Ndingathini na ukubuthwala ububi benu ninedwa, nemithwalo yenu, neengxabano zenu?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 13, 'Ndithabatheleni amadoda alumkileyo, aziingqondi, abadumileyo phakathi kwezizwe zakowenu, ndiwamise abe ziintloko zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 14, 'Wandiphendula, wathi, Kulungile ukuba siyenze ngokwelizwi lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 15, 'Ndabathabatha ke abaziintloko zezizwe zakowenu, amadoda alumkileyo, adumileyo, ndawamisa aba ziintloko zenu, abathetheli bewaka, nabathetheli balikhulu, nabathetheli bamashumi ngamahlanu, nabathetheli beshumi labathetheli bezizwe zakomawenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 16, 'Ngelo xesha ndabayalela abagwebi benu, ndathi, ‘Waphulaphuleni amatyala aphakathi kwabazalwana benu, nize nigwebe ngobulungisa phakathi komntu nomzalwana wakhe nomphambukeli akuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 17, 'Musani ukukhetha ubuso bomntu ekugwebeni; uthobele umncinane nomkhulu; musani ukuboyika ubuso bamntu; ngokuba umgwebo lo ngokaThixo; ukuba ityala linzima yizise kum ndilive.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 18, 'Ndaniwisela umthetho ngelo xesha ngezinto zonke enozenza.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 19, 'Sanduluka eHorebhe, sayicanda yonke intlango enkulu, eyoyikekayo, nayibonayo, sihamba endleleni yentaba yama-Amori, njengoko wasiwisela umthetho uYehova uThixo wethu; safika eKadeshe-bhareya.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 20, 'Ndathi ke kuni, Nifikile ezintabeni zama-Amori, aya kusinika zona uYehova uThixo wethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 21, 'Yabona, uYehova uThixo wakho ulibeke ihlabathi phambi kwakho; nyukani nilime, njengoko wathethayo uYehova uThixo wooyihlo kuni; musani ukoyika, ningatyhafi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 22, 'Nasondela ke elowo kuni, nathi, Masithumele amadoda, asikhokele, asihlolele ilizwe, asixelele indlela esohamba ngayo, nemizi esofika kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 23, 'Landithanda elo lizwi, ndathabatha kuni amadoda alishumi elinamabini, indoda yanye esizweni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 24, 'Ajika ke, anyuka intaba, afika entilini yomlambo wase-Eshkole, ayihlola.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 25, 'Athabatha esandleni sawo iziqhamo zelo zwe, asizisa, athi, Lilizwe elilungileyo eli, asinikayo uYehova uThixo wethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 26, 'Kodwa anivumanga ukunyuka, nawuphikisa umlomo kaYehova uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 27, 'Baduma ezintenteni zabo, bathi, Kungenxa yokuba esithiyile uYehova, wasikhupha ezweni laseYiputa, ukuze asinikele esandleni sama-Amori, asitshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 28, 'Siya kunyukela phi na? abazalwana bethu bazidimaza iintliziyo zethu ngokuthi: Abantu abadala nabade kunathi; imizi emikhulu, eludongeni oluya kufikelela emazulwini; kananjalo, sababona khona oonyana bakaBhahanake.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 29, 'Ndathi ke kuni, Musani ukuboyika, ningaboyiki;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 30, 'uYehova uThixo wenu, onikhokelayo, wonilwela, njengoko wakwenzayo kuni, phambi kwamehlo enu eYiputa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 31, 'Yaye entlango, apho wabonayo ukuba uYehova uThixo wakho wakuzala, kanye njengoko umntu ezala unyana wakhe, ngendlela yonke enahamba ngayo de nafika kule ndawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 32, 'Kodwa kule nto anikholwanga kuNdikhoyo uThixo wenu,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 33, 'owakukhokelayo endleleni, ekufuna apho ungamisa khona iintente zakho, emlilweni ebusuku ukuba akubonise indlela enohamba ngayo, ngelifu emini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 34, 'Wasiva ke uYehova isandi samazwi enu, wavutha ngumsindo, wafunga, wathi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 35, 'Ngokuqinisekileyo akukho namnye kwaba bantu esi sizukulwana singendawo uya kulibona elo lizwe lihle, endathembisa ngalo kooyihlo-mkhulu,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 36, 'hlangula uKalebhi unyana kaYefune; uya kulibona, ndimnike ilizwe awanyathela kulo, yena nabantwana bakhe, ngokuba umlandele uYehova ngokupheleleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 37, 'uYehova wandifuthela ngenxa yenu, wathi, Nawe akuyi kungena nalapho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 38, 'uYoshuwa unyana kaNun, oma phambi kwakho, nguye oya kungena khona; Mkhuthaze, ngokuba nguye oya kuwanika uSirayeli ilifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 39, 'Abantwana benu, enibe nisithi bothinjwa, nabantwana benu abangakwaziyo okulungileyo nokubi ngelo xesha, bona bongena khona, ndibanike lona, babe zizityebi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 40, 'Ke nina jikani, nihambe entlango ngendlela yoLwandle oluBomvu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 41, 'Naphendula nathi kum, Sonile kuYehova; sonyuka thina, silwe, njengoko wasiyalelayo uYehova uThixo wethu. Naxa elowo exhobile, exhobe exhobele imfazwe, nalungela ukunyuka intaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 42, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Yithi kubo, Ize ningenyuki niye kulwa; kuba andikho phakathi kwenu; hleze nigxothwe ziintshaba zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 43, 'Kungenxa yoko le nto ndithethe kuni; naza anaphulaphula, kodwa nawuvukela umyalelo kaYehova naza nenyuka induli ngekratshi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 44, 'Anihlasela ke ama-Amori ami kuloo ntaba, anisukela njengeenyosi, amtshabalalisa uSehire, esa eHorem.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 45, 'Wabuya walila phambi koYehova; akaliphulaphula uYehova ilizwi lenu, akakuphulaphula nani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 1, 46, 'Ngoko nahlala eKadeshe imihla emininzi, ngokwemihla enayihlalayo khona;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 1, 'Sanduluka, sabheka entlango ngendlela eya eShelefeshe, njengoko watshoyo uYehova kum; Sayijikeleza intaba yakwaSehire imihla emininzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 2, 'Wathetha uYehova kum, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 3, 'Sekulithuba elide niyijikeleza le ntaba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 4, 'Wabawisela umthetho abantu, wathi, Niya kucanda ezweni labazalwana benu, oonyana bakaEsawu, abemi kwaSehire; baya kukoyika; zigcineni ke ngokwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 5, 'Musa ukubaphazamisa; kuba ezweni labo andiyi kuninika nto, nokuba bububanzi bonyawo; ngokuba intaba yakwaSehire ndamnika uEsawu ukuba ayime.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 6, 'Wothenga inyama kubo ngemali, udle; uthenge kubo amanzi ngemali, usele.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 7, 'Ngokuba ukusikelele uYehova uThixo wakho emsebenzini wonke wezandla zakho; Uyayazi indlela yakho kule ntlango inkulu; kuba le minyaka imashumi mane uYehova uThixo wakho unani; akufuni nto.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 8, 'Sagqitha kubazalwana bethu, oonyana bakaEsawu, ababehleli kwaSehire, sahamba ngendlela yentlango ye-Elati ne-Etsiyon-gebhere, sajika sahamba ngendlela yentlango yakwaMowabhi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 9, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Musani ukuwahlisela ishwangusha amaMowabhi, uze ungalwa nawo ulwe nawo; kuba ezweni lawo andiyi kuninika lilifa; ngokuba ndilinike oonyana bakaLote ukuba libe lilifa labo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 10, 'AmaEma ahlala khona, eluhlanga olukhulu, olukhulu, olude njengama-Anaki;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 11, 'kananjalo babalelwa ekubeni ngamagorha, njengama-Anaki; ke amaMowabhi ababiza ngokuba ngamaEma.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 12, 'AmaHori ebemi kwaSehire ngenxa engaphambili; kodwa bandwendwa oonyana bakaEsawu, babatshabalalisa phambi kwabo, bemka endaweni yabo; njengoko benza ngako oonyana bakaSirayeli ezweni ababelihluthile, awabanika lona uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 13, 'Ndithi, yima ngoku, uthuthuzele umlambo waseSerede. Kwaye sawela umlambo iSeredi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 14, 'Ukuhamba kwethu eKadeshe-bharneha sada sawela umlambo iSerede, yaba yiminyaka emashumi mathathu anesibhozo; side siphele sonke isizukulwana samagorha phakathi komkhosi, njengoko uYehova wawafungelayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 15, 'Saye kananjalo isandla sikaYehova siphezu kwawo, ukuba awatshabalalise, ade aphume.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 16, 'Abhubha onke amagorha, afa phakathi kwabantu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 17, 'Wathetha uYehova kum, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 18, 'Namhla niya kuyiwela iAre, unxweme lwakwaMowabhi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 19, 'Ekusondeleni kwakho koonyana baka-Amon, uze ungabaphazamisi, ungabaphazamisi; kuba ilizwe loonyana baka-Amon andiyi kuninika lilifa; ngokuba ndayinika oonyana bakaLote ukuba bayime.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 20, 'Nangona kunjalo, kwakusithiwa lilizwe lamandulo; kumaxesha amandulo, iingxilimbela zazihlala kulo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 21, 'uhlanga olukhulu, olukhulu, olude njengama-Anaki; uYehova wabatshabalalisa phambi kwabo; bawangenela, bema esikhundleni sabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 22, 'Wenza koonyana bakaEsawu abemiyo kwaSehire, wawatshabalalisa amaHori phambi kwabo; bawalandela, bema esikhundleni sabo unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 23, 'Yaye iiAve ezazihlala eHasherem zenyuka zaya kutsho kuAsa, abaTshitshi ababevela eKatore bazitshabalalisa baza bahlala endaweni yazo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 24, 'Suka, uwele umlanjana oyiArnon; yabonani, ndiya kumnikela uSihon umAmori, ukumkani waseHeshbhon, nelizwe lakhe, esandleni senu; qalani ukuyithimba nilwe nayo edabini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 25, 'Namhlanje ndiya kuqala ukubeka ukunkwantya kwakho nokoyikeka kwakho phezu kweentlanga eziphantsi kwezulu lonke, eziya kuva ngawe, zigungqe, zoyike.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 26, 'Ndathumela abathunywa entlango yeKedemoti, baya kuSihon ukumkani waseHeshbhon, benamazwi oxolo, ndathi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 27, 'ndicande ezweni lakho; Ndiya kuhamba ngomendo, ndingaphambukeli ekunene nasekhohlo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 28, 'Ndithengisele inyama ngemali, ndidle; ndinike amanzi ngemali, ndisele; kodwa ndiya komba ngeenyawo zam;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 29, 'ngendlela benza ngayo kum oonyana bakaEsawu abemiyo kwaSehire, namaMowabhi abemiyo, ndada ndawela iYordan, ndaya ezweni aya kusinika lona uYehova uThixo wethu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 30, 'Akasivumela uSihon ukumkani waseHeshbhon ukuba sicande kuye; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho wamqinisa isibindi, wayenza ingqoshomba intliziyo yakhe, ukuze amnikele esandleni sakho, njengoko kunjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 31, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Yabona, ndiqalile ukumnikela kuwe uSihon nelizwe lakhe; qalani ukulihlutha, ukuze nilihluthe ilizwe lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 32, 'Waphuma uSihon wasihlangabeza, yena nabantu bakhe bonke, ukuba silwe neYahaze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 33, 'uYehova uThixo wethu wamnikela kuthi; samoyisa yena noonyana bakhe nabantu bakhe bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 34, 'Sazithimba zonke izixeko zakhe ngelo xesha, satshabhisa amadoda, nabafazi, nabantwana bemizi ngemizi; asisekho bani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 35, 'Imfuyo yodwa sayithimba, sayithimba imizi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 36, 'Ukususela eArohere, ekumda woMlambo iArnon, nokususela kwisixeko esikufuphi noMlambo umNayile ukuya eGiliyadi, akubangakho nasinye isixeko esomeleleyo kuthi; uYehova, uThixo wethu, usinike yonk’ into.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 2, 37, 'Kuphela eningafikanga kwilizwe loonyana baka-Amoni, nakuwo nawuphi na ummandla woMlambo iYabhoki nakwizixeko ezisezintabeni okanye kuko konke awasalela ngako uYehova uThixo wethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 1, 'Sajika senyuka saya eBhashan, waphuma uOgi ukumkani waseBhashan, wasihlangabeza, yena nabantu bakhe bonke, ukuba silwe ne-Edreyi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 2, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Musa ukumoyika; ngokuba ndiya kumnikela esandleni sakho, nabantu bakhe bonke, nelizwe lakhe; uya kwenza kuye njengoko wenzayo kuSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, obemi eHeshbhon.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 3, 'Ngoko uYehova uThixo wethu wamnikela uOge ukumkani waseBhashan nabo bonke abantu bakhe esandleni sethu; samoyisa yada yalambatha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 4, 'Sazithimba zonke izixeko zakhe ngelo xesha, yaye akubangakho sixeko singasithimbanga kubo, izixeko ezingamashumi amathandathu, ummandla wonke waseArgobhi, ubukumkani bukaOgi waseBhashan.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 5, 'Yonke loo mizi ibijikelezwe ngeendonga eziphakamileyo, namasango, nemivalo; kufuphi nezixeko ezininzi ezingenaludonga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 6, 'Sabaqalekisa, njengoko samtshabhisayo uSihon ukumkani waseHeshbhon, satshabhisa amadoda, nabafazi, nabantwana bemizi ngemizi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 7, 'Ke zona iinkomo namaxhoba aloo mizi sazithimbela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 8, 'Salithimba ilizwe ngelo xesha esandleni sookumkani bobabini bama-Amori, ababengasempumalanga kweYordan, lithabathela emlanjeni oyiArnon, lesa entabeni yeHermon;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 9, '(yiHermon yona, leyo amaTsidon ayibiza ngokuba yiSiriyon, ama-Amori ayibiza ngokuba yiSenire);', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 10, 'Zonke izixeko zaseNtlango neGiliyadi yonke nayo yonke iBhashan ukuya kufikelela eSalga nase-Edreyi, izixeko zobukumkani bukaOgi eBhashan.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 11, 'Ngokuba nguOgi yedwa, ukumkani waseBhashan, oseleyo kumaRafa; nantso isilili sakhe sisilili yentsimbi; Asiyiyo na iRabha yoonyana baka-Amon? zaba ziikubhite ezisithoba ubude bayo, neekubhite ezine ububanzi bayo, ngokwekubhite yomntu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 12, 'Eli lizwe saloyisayo ngelo xesha, ukususela eArohere kufuphi nomlambo iArnon, isiqingatha seentaba zaseGiliyadi nezixeko zayo, ndalinika amaRubhen namaGadi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 13, 'Enye inxalenye yaseGiliyadi neBhashan yonke, oko kukuthi, ubukumkani bukaOgi, ndawunika isiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase; nelizwe lonke laseArgobhi, neBhashan yonke, leyo bekusithiwa lilizwe lamaRafa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 14, 'uYayire, unyana kaManase, waloyisa lonke ilizwe laseArgobhi ukuya kufikelela kumda waseGeshuri neMagati; wazibiza ngegama lakhe, wathi yiBhashan-havoti-yahire unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 15, 'iGiliyadi ndayinika uMagire.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 16, 'AmaRubhen namaGadi ndawanika isiqingatha somfula ophuma eGiliyadi, uye emlanjeni oyiArnon, nomda weYabhoki, emdeni woonyana baka-Amon;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 17, 'neNtlango neYordan nomda wayo, ukususela eKinereti ukusa kuLwandle Lwentlango, uLwandle lweTyuwa, phantsi kweAshdode nePisga ngasempuma.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 18, 'Ndaniwisela umthetho ngelo xesha, ndisithi, uYehova uThixo wenu uninike eli lizwe ukuba nilihluthe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 19, 'Kodwa abafazi bakho, nabantwana bakho, nemfuyo yakho, ngenxa yokuba ndisazi ukuba unemfuyo eninzi, basala emizini yakho endikunike yona;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 20, 'ade uYehova abaphumze abazalwana benu njengani, bade nabo balidle ilifa ilizwe abanika lona uYehova uThixo wenu phesheya kweYordan; nibuyele ke elowo elifeni lakhe endininike lona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 21, 'Ndamwisela umthetho uYoshuwa ngelo xesha, ndathi, Amehlo akho makakubone konke akwenzileyo uYehova uThixo wenu kwaba kumkani bobabini; uYehova uya kwenjenjalo kuzo zonke izikumkani oya kuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 22, 'Musani ukuboyika; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wenu uya kunilwela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 23, 'Ndathandaza kuYehova ngelo xesha, ndathi:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 24, 'Nkosi yam, Yehova, wambonisa umkhonzi wakho ubukhulu bakho, nesandla sakho esithe nkqi; ngokuba nguwuphi na uthixo emazulwini nasehlabathini onokwenza ngokwemisebenzi yakho, nangamandla akho?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 25, 'Makhe ndiwele ndize ndibone ilizwe elihle phesheya kweYordan, intaba entle neLebhanon.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 26, 'Wandifuthela uYehova ngenxa yenu, akandiphulaphula; wathi uYehova kum, Kwanele; ungaphindi uthethe nam ngalento.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 27, 'Nyuka uye encotsheni yePisga, uphose amehlo akho entshonalanga, nasentla, nasezantsi, nasempumalanga, ulikhangele ngamehlo; ngokuba akuyi kuyiwela le Yordan.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 28, 'uYoshuwa mwisele umthetho, umomeleze, umkhaliphise, ngokuba yena uya kuhlala phambi kwaba bantu; yena uya kubadlisa ilifa, elilelo lizwe aya kulibona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 3, 29, 'Sahlala ke entilini ekhangelene neBhete-pehore.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 1, 'Khawuphulaphule ke, Sirayeli imimiselo nemithetho endiniyala ngayo, ukuba niyenze, niphile, ningene, nilihluthe ilizwe elo akunikayo uYehova uThixo wooyihlo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 2, 'Ize ningongezi nto ezwini endiniwisela umthetho ngalo, ningathabatha nto kulo, ukuze niyigcine imithetho kaYehova uThixo wenu, endiniwisela yona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 3, 'Amehlo enu akubonile oko uYehova wakwenzayo kuBhahali-pehore; ngokuba bonke abantu ababemlandela uBhahali-pehore, uYehova uThixo wakho ubatshabalalisile, bangabikho phakathi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 4, 'Kodwa nina nanamathelayo kuYehova uThixo wenu, nonke ngabanye nisaphila nanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 5, 'Yabonani, ndinifundise imimiselo namasiko, njengoko ndawiselwa umthetho nguYehova uThixo wam, ukuze nenze ngokunjalo ezweni eningena kulo ukuba nilihluthe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 6, 'Gcinani ningenzi; ngenxa yokuba bubulumko benu nokuqonda kwenu phambi kwamehlo eentlanga eziya kuyiva yonke le miyalelo, isithi: ‘Eneneni, olu hlanga lukhulu ngabantu abalumkileyo, abanengqondo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 7, 'Kuba luluphi uhlanga olukhulu uThixo asondele kulo, njengoko uYehova, uThixo wethu, esondele kulo naphi na apho simbiza khona?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 8, 'Luluphi na uhlanga olukhulu olunemithetho nemiyalelo, njengalo myalelo wonke ndiwuwiselayo namhla?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 9, 'Kodwa zigcine, uwugcine umphefumlo wakho kunene, hleze uyilibale into ayibonileyo amehlo akho, ingaphumi entliziyweni yakho yonke imihla yobomi bakho uze uwafundise oonyana bakho, noonyana boonyana bakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 10, 'Ingakumbi ngemini owama ngayo phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, eHorebhe, oko uYehova wathi kum, Ndihlanganisele abantu, ndibaphulaphule amazwi am, bafunde ukundiva; boyike yonke imihla yobomi babo emhlabeni, bafundise abantwana babo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 11, 'Yasondela, yema phantsi kwentaba; intaba isitsha ngumlilo esazulwini sezulu, kumnyama, namafu, kumnyama.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 12, 'Wathetha uYehova kuni esemlilweni; nasiva isandisa mazwi, anabona mbonakalo yaso; weva ilizwi lodwa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 13, 'Wanizisa ngomnqophiso wakhe awaniwisela umthetho ngawo, ukuba niwuzalise, lowo ngumthetho olishumi; wayibhala emacwecweni amabini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 14, 'Ngelo xesha uYehova wandiyalela ukuba ndinifundise imithetho nezigwebo, ukuze nizizalise kwilizwe enifudukela kulo ukuba nityebe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 15, 'Zigcineni ngoku; ngenxa yokuba anibonanga kwangaloo mini wathetha ngayo uYehova kuni eHorebhe phakathi komlilo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 16, 'ukuze ningazenzi iinqambi, ngokuzenzela umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, nokuba ngowayiphi na imbonakalo, njengendoda nenkazana;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 17, 'nemfano yazo zonke izinto eziphilileyo ezisemhlabeni, nemfano yeentaka zonke ezinamaphiko, eziphaphazela esibhakabhakeni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 18, 'Umfanekiselo wento yonke enyakazelayo emhlabeni, nomfanekiselo weentlanzi zonke ezisemanzini aphantsi komhlaba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 19, 'hleze amehlo akho uwaphakamisele esibhakabhakeni, uthi, walibona ilanga, nenyanga, neenkwenkwezi, nesibhakabhaka, uphetshethwe, ukuba uqubude kuzo, ukhonze abo ibakhonzayo iNkosi yakho. Uzahlule zonke iintlanga phantsi kwezulu lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 20, 'Ke nina uYehova unithabathileyo, wanikhupha kwiziko lesinyithi, amaYiputa, ukuba nibe ngabantu abalilifa kuye, njengoko ninjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 21, 'Ngaphezu koko, uYehova waba nomsindo kum ngenxa yenu waza wafunga ukuba andiyi kuyiwela iYordan nokuba andiyi kungena kwilizwe elihle uYehova uThixo wenu aya kuninika lona njengelifa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 22, 'kuba ndiya kufela kweli lizwe, andiyiweli iYordan; Ke nina niya kuwela, nilidle ilifa elo lizwe lihle.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 23, 'Zigcineni, ningawulibali umnqophiso kaYehova uThixo wenu, awawenzayo nani, nizenzele umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, umfanekiso wento yonke awalayo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 24, 'Ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho ungumlilo odlayo, unguThixo onekhwele.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 25, 'Wakuba ungazalanga mntwana nabazukulwana, wahlala kwelo zwe imihla emininzi, wazidubula, wazenzela umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, nokuba ngumfanekiso oqingqiweyo; amehlo kaYehova, uThixo wenu, ukuba amqumbise umdla:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 26, 'Ndibiza izulu nomhlaba namhlanje ukuba zibe ngamangqina kuni, okuba kungekudala niya kutshatyalaliswa ngokupheleleyo kwilizwe eniwela iYordan nisiya kulidla ilifa; anisayi kuyolula imihla yenu kulo, niya kuqalekiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 27, 'Woniphangalalisa uYehova phakathi kweentlanga, nisale nibambalwa ezintlangeni, aya kunisa kuzo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 28, 'Niya kukhonza oothixo, umsebenzi wezandla zomntu, umthi namatye, abangaboniyo, abangevayo, abangadliyo, abangevayo nevumba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 29, 'Ukuba nithe naquqela uYehova uThixo wenu, ekhona, nimfumana, ukuba nithe naquqela kuye ngentliziyo yenu yonke, nangomphefumlo wenu wonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 30, 'Ekubandezelekeni kwenu nasekubandezelekeni kwenu konke oku, ekupheleni kwemihla, nabuyela kuYehova uThixo wenu, niliphulaphule ilizwi lakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 31, 'Kuba uYehova uThixo wakho nguThixo onenceba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 32, 'Khanibuze ngoku, kwimihla yamandulo, eyayikho phambi kwenu, kususela ekumdaleni kukaThixo umntu ehlabathini, uthabathe, uthabathele esiphelweni sezulu, use kwesinye isiphelo samazulu, ukuba ikho na into enjengale, nokuba kwakha kwakho nje; uyeva?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 33, 'Bakha baliva na abantu izwi loThixo ethetha phakathi komlilo, njengoko walivayo wena, baphila noko?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 34, 'Okanye ngaba uThixo wayefuna ukuhlanganisa abantu phakathi kwabanye abantu ngezilingo, ngemiqondiso, ngezilingo, nangemfazwe, nangesandla esomeleleyo, nangesandla esoluliweyo, nangezoyikiso ezinkulu, nangako konke uYehova akwenzileyo? uThixo wakwenza iYiputa emehlweni akho?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 35, 'Makwazeke oko kuni, ukuze nazi ukuba uYehova nguThixo yena; akukho bani ingenguye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 36, 'Waliva ilizwi lakhe emazulwini ukuba anifundise; kwaye ehlabathini wabonisa umlilo wakhe omkhulu; naweva amazwi akhe emlilweni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 37, 'Wabathandayo nje ooyihlo, wayinyula imbewu yabo emva kwabo, wakukhupha eYiputa ngamandla akhe amakhulu, phambi kwamehlo akhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 38, 'ukuba azigqogqe phambi kwakho iintlanga ezinkulu ezomeleleyo kunawe, ukuba akungenise, akunike ilizwe lazo libe lilifa, njengoko kunjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 39, 'Yazi ke namhla, uze ukwazi ngentliziyo yakho, ukuba uYehova nguye uThixo emazulwini phezulu, nasehlabathini phantsi; akekho omnye;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 40, 'ugcine imithetho yakhe, nemithetho yakhe, endikuwiselayo namhla, ukuze usikelelwe, wena noonyana bakho emva kwakho, ukuze uyolule imihla yakho kwelo lizwe, uYehova uThixo wakho, omnikayo kude kuse ephakadeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 41, 'uMosis wazinqumla izixeko ezithathu nganeno kweJordan ekuphumeni kwelanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 42, 'ukuze abalekele khona umbulali lowo, owabulala ummelwane wakhe ngengozi, ebengamthiyanga ngenxa engaphambili; ukuze iphile, xa ithe yasabela komnye wale mizi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 43, 'NdinguBhetsere entlango, entlango yakwaRubhen; neRamoti yaseGiliyadi, ezweni lakwaGadi; neGolan, eBhashan, ezweni lakwaManase.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 44, 'Nguwo lo umyalelo awawumiselayo uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 45, 'Zizo ezi izingqino, nemithetho, namasiko, awawathethayo uMoses koonyana bakaSirayeli ekuphumeni kwabo eYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 46, 'Ngaphesheya kweYordan, entilini ephambi kweBhete-pehore, ezweni likaSihon ukumkani wama-Amori, obemi eHeshbhon, owamoyisayo uMoses noonyana bakaSirayeli ekuphumeni kwabo eYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 47, 'Balithimba ilizwe lakhe nelizwe likaOge ukumkani waseBhashan, ookumkani ababini bama-Amori ababengaphesheya kweYordan ngasempuma;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 48, 'lithabathela eArohere, eseludinini lomlanjana oyiArnon, lesa entabeni yeZiyon: yiHermon;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 4, 49, 'nentlango yonke engaphesheya kweYordan ngasempumalanga, yesa elwandle lwasentlango, phantsi kwemithombo yasePisga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 1, 'Wawabiza uMoses onke amaSirayeli, wathi kuwo, Yiphulaphuleni, maSirayeli, imimiselo nemithetho endiyithethayo kuni namhla, yivani, nifunde, niyenze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 2, 'uYehova uThixo wethu wenza umnqophiso nathi eHorebhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 3, 'uYehova akawenzanga noobawo bethu lo mnqophiso;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 4, 'uYehova wathetha kuni, ekhangelene nani entabeni phakathi komlilo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 5, '(Ngelo xesha ndema phakathi koYehova nani ukuze ndinixelele ilizwi likaYehova, ngenxa yokuba nanisoyika umlilo, ananyuka entabeni, nisithi:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 6, 'NdinguYehova, uThixo wakho, owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa, endlwini yobukhoboka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 7, 'Uze ungabi nathixo bambi ngaphandle kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 8, 'Uze ungazenzeli umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, nokuba ngowamnye umfanekiso wento esemazulwini phezulu, nephantsi komhlaba, nesemanzini aphantsi komhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 9, 'Uze ungaqubudi kwezo nto, ungazikhonzi; kuba mna Yehova, Thixo wakho, ndinguThixo onekhwele, ubuvelela ubugwenxa booyise koonyana, kwesesithathu nakwesesine isizukulwana sabandithiyileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 10, 'Ndibabale amawaka abandithandayo, abayigcinayo imithetho yam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 11, 'Uze ungafumane ulibize igama likaYehova uThixo wakho, kuba uYehova akayi kumyekela msulwa osebenzisa igama lakhe njengelize.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 12, 'Wugcine ungcwele umhla wesabatha, njengoko wakuwisela umthetho uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 13, 'Wosebenza imihla emithandathu, uwenze wonke umsebenzi wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 14, 'ke wona umhla wesixhenxe uyisabatha kaYehova uThixo wakho; Uze ungenzi namnye umsebenzi ngayo, wena, nonyana wakho, nentombi yakho, nesicaka sakho, nesicakakazi sakho, nenkomo yakho, neesile lakho, nokuba yiyiphi into ezitho zine, nokuba yiyiphi into ezitho zine, nokuba yiyiphi na ephakathi kwakho, nowasemzini ophakathi kwakho; ukuze uphumle umkhonzi wakho nomkhonzazana wakho njengawe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 15, 'Ukhumbule ukuba wawulikhoboka ezweni laseYiputa, wakukhupha kulo uYehova uThixo wakho ngesandla esomeleleyo nangesandla esoluliweyo; ngenxa yoko ukuwisele umthetho uYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba uwugcine umhla wesabatha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 16, 'Beka uyihlo nonyoko, njengoko akuwisele umthetho uYehova uThixo wakho; ukuze yande imihla yakho, nokuze kulunge kuwe ezweni elo akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 17, 'Uze ungabulali;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 18, 'Kwaye musa ukukrexeza.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 19, 'Uze ungebi nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 20, 'Uze ungangqini ubungqina obubuxoki ngommelwane wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 21, 'Kananjalo uze ungamnqweneli umfazi wommelwane wakho, ungayinqweneli indlu yommelwane wakho, nentsimi yakhe, nesicaka sakhe, nesicakakazi sakhe, nenkomo yakhe, ne-esile lakhe, nantoni na eyeyakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 22, 'La mazwi uYehova wawathetha ngezwi elikhulu ebandleni lenu lonke entabeni phakathi komlilo, nelifu, nesithokothoko; akongezi nto. Wayibhala emacwecweni amabini, wandinika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 23, 'Naliva ilizwi eliphuma emnyameni (ngokuba intaba isitsha ngumlilo), neza kum, zonke iintloko zezindlu zooyise, namadoda amakhulu enu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 24, 'Kwaye bathi: Qaphelani, iNkosi uThixo wethu isibonisile ubuqaqawuli bayo nobukhulu bayo, kwaye silivile ilizwi layo emlilweni; sibonile namhla, ukuba uThixo wathetha emntwini, waphila.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 25, 'Kutheni simele sife ngoku? ngokuba lo mlilo mkhulu uya kusitshisa; ukuba siliva ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wethu, siya kufa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 26, 'Kuba ngubani na phakathi kwenyama yonke owalivayo ilizwi likaThixo ophilileyo, ethetha phakathi komlilo, njengathi, waphila noko?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 27, 'Sondela, uve yonk’ into aya kuyithetha uYehova uThixo wethu; Sixelele yonk’ into aya kuyithetha kuwe uYehova uThixo wethu; sova ke, siyenze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 28, 'Waliva uYehova izwi lokuthetha kwenu ekuthetheni kwenu kum; Wathi uYehova kum, Ndiwavile amazwi aba bantu ababewathethile kuwe; Babenyanisile kuyo yonke into ababeyithetha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 29, 'Akwaba nje bebenentliziyo enjalo yokundoyika baze bayigcine yonke imiyalelo yam ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo, ukuze izinto zihambe kakuhle kubo nakoonyana bawo ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 30, 'Athi kubo, Buyelani ezintenteni zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 31, 'Ke wena, yima apha nam, ndiyithethe kuwe yonke imithetho nemiyalelo nemiyalelo, oya kubafundisa yona, ukuba bayenze ezweni elo ndibanika ukuba balime.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 32, 'Ngoko ke yenzani ngenyameko njengoko uYehova uThixo wenu eniyaleleyo, ningatyekeli ekunene nasekhohlo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 5, 33, 'Hambani ngeendlela zonke aniwisele umthetho ngazo uYehova uThixo wenu, ukuze niphile, nibe nempumelelo, niyolule imihla yenu emhlabeni oya kuwudla ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 1, 'Yiyo le imimiselo, nemiyalelo, nomthetho, aniwisele umthetho ngawo uYehova uThixo wenu, ukuba niwufundise, ukuba niwenze ezweni elo uya kulihlutha;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 2, 'ukuze umoyike uYehova uThixo wakho, uyigcine yonke imiyalelo yakhe nemithetho yakhe endikuwiselayo, wena nonyana wakho, nonyana wonyana wakho, yonke imihla yobomi bakho; ukuze yolulwe imihla yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 3, 'Khawuve, Sirayeli, ukuze izinto zinihambele kakuhle, nande, njengoko uYehova, uTHIXO wookhokho benu, wakuthembisayo, ezweni eliqukuqela ubisi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 4, 'Phulaphula, Sirayeli, uYehova uThixo wethu nguYehova yedwa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 5, 'Uze umthande uYehova uThixo wakho ngentliziyo yakho yonke, nangomphefumlo wakho wonke, nangamandla akho onke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 6, 'La mazwi ndikuwisela umthetho ngawo namhlanje, abe sentliziyweni yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 7, 'Uyifundise ngenyameko abantwana bakho, uthethe ngayo ekuhlaleni kwakho endlwini yakho, nasekuhambeni kwakho ngendlela, nasekuleleni kwakho, nasekuvukeni kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 8, 'Yibophe ibe ngumqondiso esandleni sakho, ibe njengebhanti phakathi kwamehlo akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 9, 'Wabhale emigubasini yendlu yakho nasemasangweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 10, 'Xa athe uYehova uThixo wakho wakungenisa kulo ilizwe abelifungele ooyihlo, ooAbraham noIsake noYakobi, ukuba akunike imizi emikhulu, emihle, ongayakhanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 11, 'nezindlu ezizele zizinto zonke ezintle, ongazizalisanga, namaqula ongawambanga, nesidiliya nesidiliya, ongazityalanga; nokuba nithe nadla, nohlutha;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 12, 'Zigcine, ungamlibali uYehova owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa, endlwini yobukhoboka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 13, 'Yoyika uYehova uThixo wakho, umkhonze, ufunge igama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 14, 'Nize ningalandeli thixo bambi, oothixo beentlanga ezingeenxa zonke kuni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 15, 'ngokuba nguThixo onekhwele, uYehova uThixo wakho phakathi kwakho, nguThixo onekhwele, hleze umsindo kaYehova uThixo wakho uvuthe phezu kwakho, akutshabalalise ehlabathini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 16, 'Musani ukumlinga uYehova uThixo wenu, njengoko wamlingayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 17, 'Gcinani imithetho kaYehova uThixo wenu, nezilumkiso zakhe, nemiyalelo yakhe, awakuwiselayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 18, 'Yenzani okulungileyo nokulungileyo emehlweni kaYehova, ukuze kulunge kuni, ningene nilidle ilifa ilizwe elihle awalifungela ooyihlo uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 19, 'ukuba azigxothe iintshaba zakho zonke phambi kwakho, njengoko wathethayo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 20, 'Kuthekani ukuba unyana wakho ekubuza kamva, esithi: ‘Lithini icebiso, imithetho nemiyalelo asiyalele yona uYehova uThixo wethu?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 21, 'Wothi kunyana wakho, Sibe singamakhoboka kaFaro eYiputa; wasikhupha uYehova eYiputa ngesandla esithe nkqi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 22, 'uYehova wenza eYiputa imiqondiso nezimanga, ezikhulu nezinzima, kuFaro, nakwindlu yakhe yonke, emehlweni ethu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 23, 'wasikhupha khona, ukuze asithabathe, ukuba asinike ilizwe elo awalifungela oobawo ngesifungo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 24, 'Wasiwisela umthetho uYehova, ukuba siyenze le mithetho yonke, ukuba simoyike uYehova uThixo wethu, silunge ngonaphakade, asigcine ebomini, njengoko kunjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 6, 25, 'Kuya kuba yinto efanelekileyo kuthi ukuba siyayinyamekela ukuyenza le miyalelo phambi koYehova uThixo wethu, njengoko wasiyalelayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 1, 'Xa athe uYehova uThixo wakho wakungenisa kulo ilizwe oya kulo ukuba ulihluthe, wagqogqa iintlanga ezininzi phambi kwakho, amaHeti, namaGirgashi, nama-Amori, namaKanan, namaPerizi, namaHeti, namaYebhusi; zisixhenxe iintlanga mkhulu nowomeleleyo kunawe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 2, 'Xa uYehova uThixo wakho wazinikela kuwe; boyise, baqalekise; Uze ungamanyanisi nabo, ungabi nanceba kubo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 3, 'Uze ungabatshabhi nabo; intombi yakho uze ungayiniki unyana wakhe, nentombi yakhe ungayizeki kunyana wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 4, 'Kuba yomtyekisa unyana wakho kum, akhonze thixo bambi; uya kuvutha umsindo kaYehova kuni, anitshabalalise ngoko nangoko.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 5, 'Yenjenje ke ukwenza kubo; zidilizeni izibingelelo zazo, nizidilize izimiso zazo, nibagawule izibonda zemithi yabo engcwele, niyitshise ngomlilo imifanekiso yazo eqingqiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 6, 'Ngokuba uluhlanga olungcwele kuYehova uThixo wakho; uYehova uThixo wakho uninyule ukuba nibe ngabantu bakhe abakhethekileyo ngaphezu kwezizwe zonke zehlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 7, 'uYehova akanithandanga yaye akaninyulanga, ngenxa yokuba naningaphezu kweentlanga zonke; ngokuba ubuyena umncinci kubo bonke abantu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 8, 'Kodwa ngenxa yokunithanda kukaYehova nokusigcina kwakhe isifungo awasifungela ookhokho benu, uYehova unikhuphe ngesandla esomeleleyo waza wanikhulula kwindlu yamakhoboka esandleni sikaFaro, ukumkani waseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 9, 'Yazi ke ngoku, ukuba uYehova uThixo wakho nguye uThixo, uThixo wenyaniso, obagcinelayo umnqophiso nenceba abamthandayo, abayigcinayo imithetho yakhe, ase ewakeni lezizukulwana;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 10, 'Baxeleleni abamthiyayo ekuhleni, ukuba batshatyalaliswe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 11, 'Gcina imiyalelo nemimiselo nezigwebo endikuyalela ukuba uzenze namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 12, 'Kothi, xa nithe nayiva le mithetho, niyigcine, nayenza, wonigcinela umnqophiso nenceba uYehova uThixo wenu, awabafungayo ooyihlo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 13, 'Wonithanda, anisikelele, anandise; Wosisikelela isiqhamo sesizalo sakho, nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho, ingqolowa yakho, newayini yakho entsha, neoli yakho, nesiqhamo senkomo yakho, namatakane empahla yakho emfutshane, emhlabeni lowo abewufungele ooyihlo ukukunika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 14, 'Wosikeleleka ngaphezu kweentlanga zonke; akusayi kubakho nto ingazaliyo, nasezinkomeni zakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 15, 'uYehova wozisusa zonke izifo kuwe; buya kuba ngumthwalo kuni bonke abanithiyayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 16, 'Uzitshabalalisile zonke iintlanga aya kuzisindisa wena uYehova uThixo wakho; malingabi nanceba kubo iliso lakho; ungabakhonzi oothixo bazo; kuba kuya kuba ngumgibe kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 17, 'Xa uthe entliziyweni yakho, Ezi ntlanga zininzi kunam; Ndingazisusa njani?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 18, 'Musa ukuzoyika; kodwa khumbula kakuhle awakwenzayo uYehova uThixo wakho kuFaro nakumaYiputa onke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 19, 'izilingo ezikhulu azibonileyo amehlo akho, nemiqondiso nezimanga nesandla esomeleleyo nesandla esoluliweyo awakukhupha ngaso uYehova uThixo wakho; uya kwenjenjalo uYehova uThixo wakho kuzo zonke iintlanga ozoyikayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 20, 'Ngaphezu koko, uYehova uThixo wakho uya kuthumela oonomeva kuzo, zide ezo ziseleyo, zizisithelisayo ebusweni bakho, zibhubhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 21, 'Musa ukuzoyika, ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho unawe, uThixo onamandla nowoyikekayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 22, 'uYehova uThixo wakho uya kuzigqogqa kancinane ezo ntlanga phambi kwakho; ize ningawadli kamsinya, hleze ande ande phezu kwenu amarhamncwa elizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 23, 'Kodwa uYehova uThixo wakho uya kuzinikela kuwe, azitshabalalise ngentshabalalo enkulu, zide zitshatyalaliswe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 24, 'Ookumkani bazo ubanikele esandleni sakho, uwacime amagama abo phantsi kwezulu; akukho mntu uya kuma ngakuwe ude uzitshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 25, 'Imifanekiso eqingqiweyo yoothixo bazo yitshise ngomlilo; isilivere negolide ekuyo, uze ungayinqweneli, ungayithabatheli kuwe, hleze uwe kuyo; ngokuba lisikizi kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 7, 26, 'Uze ungangenisi nanye into elisikizi endlwini yakho, ukuze ungaqalekiswa njengalo; ngokuba iyinto esingelwe phantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 1, 'Wonke umthetho endikuwiselayo namhla, zigcineni nize niwenze, ukuze niphile, nande, ningene nilime ilizwe elo walifungela ooyihlo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 2, 'Uze uyikhumbule yonke indlela akuhambise ngayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ngale minyaka imashumi mane entlango, ukuze uthotywe, ucikidelwe, ukwazi okusentliziyweni yakho, ukuba woyigcina imithetho yakhe, akuyi kuyigcina, kusini na.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 3, 'Wakuthoba, wakulambisa, wakudlisa imana obungayazi, ababengayazi ooyihlo; ukuze akwazise ukuba akaphili ngasonka sodwa umntu, uphila ngamazwi onke aphuma emlonyeni kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 4, 'Iingubo zakho azonakalanga bubudala kuwe, nomlenze wakho awudumbanga kule minyaka imashumi mane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 5, 'Khumbula ngentliziyo yakho ukuba uYehova uThixo wakho uyakuqeqesha wena, njengomntu emqeqeshayo unyana wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 6, 'Ngoko ke yigcineni imithetho kaYehova uThixo wenu, nihambe ngeendlela zakhe, nimoyike.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 7, 'Kuba uYehova uThixo wakho uya kukuzisa kwilizwe elihle, ilizwe elinemisinga yamanzi equkuqelayo, imithombo nemithombo evela kwiintlambo neenduli;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 8, 'Lilizwe lengqolowa, nerhasi, nezidiliya, namakhiwane, neerharnati; ilizwe leoli yeoli nobusi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 9, 'Ezweni, oya kudla isonka ungaswelanga sonka, akuyi kuswela nto kulo; lilizwe elimatye esisinyithi, ezindulini zalo womba ubhedu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 10, 'Udle, uhluthe, umdumise uYehova uThixo wakho, ngenxa yelizwe elihle omnike lona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 11, 'Uze uzigcine, ungamlibali uYehova uThixo wakho, ngokuthi ungayigcini imithetho yakhe, nemiyalelo yakhe, nemiyalelo yakhe, endikuwiselayo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 12, 'Yabonani, xa nithe nadla, nahlutha, nakha izindlu ezintle, nihlala kuzo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 13, 'Ukuba yande imfuyo yakho, neenkomo zakho, nesilivere yakho, negolide yakho, neento zonke onazo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 14, 'Yasuka yaba nekratshi intliziyo yakho, wamlibala uYehova uThixo wakho owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa endlwini yobukhoboka;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 15, 'owakukhokelela kwintlango enkulu eyoyikekayo, eneenyoka ezinobuhlungu, noonomadudwane, ekunxanelweni kwamanzi; owakhupha amanzi eweni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 16, 'owakudlisa imana entlango, ababengayazi ooyihlo, ukuze akuthobe, akulinge, akwenzele okulungileyo ekupheleni kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 17, 'Wathi ke wena entliziyweni yakho, Ngamandla am nokuqina kwesandla sam okundenzele obu butyebi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 18, 'Uze umkhumbule ke uYehova uThixo wakho, ngokuba nguye okunika amandla obutyebi, ukuba awumise umnqophiso wakhe abewufungele ooyihlo, njengoko kunjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 19, 'Ukuba uthe wamlibala uYehova uThixo wakho, walandela thixo bambi, wabakhonza, waqubuda kubo, ndiyaningqinela namhlanje, ukuba nobhubha ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 8, 20, 'Niya kutshabalala njengeentlanga awazitshabalalisayo uYehova phambi kwenu; ngenxa yokuba ungaliphulaphulanga ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 1, 'Yiva, Sirayeli, uya kuyiwela namhla iYordan, usiya kuzihlutha iintlanga ezinkulu ezomeleleyo kunawe, imizi emikhulu, enodonga olude ezisa ezulwini;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 2, 'uhlanga olukhulu, olude, oonyana baka-Enaki, obaziyo, obavileyo kwathiwa, Ngubani na onokuma phambi koonyana baka-Enaki?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 3, 'Yazini namhla, ukuba uYehova uThixo wakho nguye onikhokelayo; njengomlilo odlayo, uya kubadla, abawise phambi kwakho; bagqogqani ngoku, nibatshabalalise kamsinya, njengoko wathethayo kuni uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 4, 'Uze ungatsho entliziyweni yakho ekubagxotheni kukaYehova uThixo wakho ebusweni bakho, ukuthi, Kungobulungisa bam le nto uYehova wandingenisa, ukuba ndilidle ilifa eli lizwe; izisa phambi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 5, 'Akungenxa yobulungisa bakho, nangenxa yengqibelelo yentliziyo yakho, akuyi kulidla ilifa ilizwe labo; Kungokungendawo kwezo ntlanga, uYehova, uThixo wakho, wozigqogqa ebusweni bakho, alizalise ilizwi awalithethayo uYehova kooyihlo, ooAbraham noIsake noYakobi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 6, 'Yazi ukuba uYehova, uThixo wakho, akakunikanga eli hlabathi lilungileyo, ngenxa yobulungisa bakho; ngokuba ningabantu abaneenkani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 7, 'Khumbula, ungayilibali indlela owamcaphukisa ngayo uYehova uThixo wakho entlango: kususela kwimini owaphuma ngayo ezweni laseYiputa wada wafika kule ndawo, namvukela uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 8, 'Yaye iHorebhe yamcaphukisa uYehova kangangokuba uYehova waba nomsindo kuni waza wanitshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 9, 'Oko ndenyuka ndaya entabeni ukuya kuthabatha amacwecwe, amacwecwe omnqophiso abewenza uYehova nani, ndahlala iimini ezimashumi mane nobusuku obumashumi mane entabeni, ndingadli sonka, ndingaseli manzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 10, 'uYehova wandinika amacwecwe amatye amabini, ebhalwe ngomnwe kaThixo; kwakubhalwe kuyo onke amazwi uYehova awawathethayo kuni entabeni emlilweni ngomhla wokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 11, 'Ekupheleni kweemini ezimashumi mane nobusuku obumashumi mane, uYehova wandinika amacwecwe amatye amabini, angamacwecwe omnqophiso.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 12, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Vuka, umke apha kamsinya; ngokuba abantu bakho obakhuphileyo eYiputa bonile baphela; batyeka kamsinya endleleni endabawisela umthetho ngayo; bazenzela umfanekiso otyhidiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 13, 'Kwakhona uYehova wathetha kum, esithi: “Ndilubonile olu hlanga, yaye luhlanga oluneenkani;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 14, 'mandime, ndibatshabalalise, ndilicime igama labo phantsi kwezulu; ndikwenze uhlanga olunamandla, olukhulu kunabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 15, 'Ndajika ke ndehla entabeni, intaba isitsha ngumlilo, amacwecwe omabini omnqophiso esezandleni zam zozibini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 16, 'Ndabona, ndabona ukuba nonile kuYehova uThixo wenu, nasuka nazenzela ithole elixheliweyo; Naphambuka ngokukhawuleza kwindlela uYehova abeniyalele ngayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 17, 'Ndathabatha amacwecwe amabini, ndawaphosa ezandleni zam zozibini, ndawaqhekeza phambi kwamehlo enu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 18, 'Ndawa phantsi phambi koYehova, njengemini yokuqala, iimini ezimashumi mane nobusuku obumashumi mane; Andidlanga sonka, andiselanga manzi ngenxa yezono zenu zonke, enone ngazo ngokwenza okubi emehlweni kaYehova, ukuba nimqumbise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 19, 'Kuba bendiwoyika umsindo nokuvutha komsindo kaYehova ukuba anitshabalalise. Kodwa ngelo xesha uYehova wandiva.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 20, 'uYehova wamfuthela kunene uAron, wada wamtshabalalisa; ndathandaza noAron ngelo xesha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 21, 'Ndasithabatha isono sakho, ithole elo walenzayo, ndalitshisa ngomlilo, ndalisila, ndalisila, lada lacoleka njengothuli; yaye uthuli lwawo ndaluphosa emlanjeni weentaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 22, 'Yaye eTabhera naseMasa naseKibroti-hatafa namenza bubi uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 23, 'Nasekunisuseni kukaYehova eKadeshe-bharneha, esithi, Nyukani, nilihluthe ilizwe elo ndininikileyo; nawuphikisa umlomo kaYehova uThixo wakho, anakholwa nguye, analiphulaphula izwi lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 24, 'Namvukela uYehova kususela koko ndanaziyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 25, 'Ndawa ke phantsi phambi koYehova, ezo mini zimashumi mane nobusuku obumashumi mane, endawayo phantsi; ngokuba uYehova wathi uya kunitshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 26, 'Ndathandaza ke kuYehova, ndathi, Nkosi yam, Yehova, musa ukubatshabalalisa abantu bakho, ilifa lakho, obakhululeyo ngobukhulu bakho, obakhuphileyo eYiputa ngesandla esithe nkqi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 27, 'Khumbula abakhonzi bakho, ooAbraham, noIsake, noYakobi; musa ukukhangela inkani yaba bantu, nobubi babo, nesono sabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 28, 'Ilizwe enisikhuphe kulo malingatsho ukuthi, ‘Kungenxa yokuba uYehova engabangenisanga kwilizwe awayebathembise lona, yaye ngenxa yokuba wayebathiyile, wabathumela ukuba bababulalele entlango.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 9, 29, 'Ke ngabantu bakho nelifa lakho, obakhuphileyo ngamandla akho amakhulu, nangesandla sakho esolukileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 1, 'Ngelo xesha wathi uYehova kum, Zilungisele amacwecwe amabini, njengawokuqala, unyuke uye kum entabeni, uzenzele ityeya yomthi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 2, 'ndiwabhale emacwecweni lawo amazwi abesemacwecweni okuqala owawaqhekezayo, ndiwabeke etyeyeni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 3, 'Ndenza ke ityeya ngomthi welinden, ndakrola amacwecwe amatye amabini, njengawokuqala; ndenyuka entabeni, ndiphethe amacwecwe omabini esandleni sam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 4, 'Wayibhala emacwecweni, ngokombhalo wokuqala, imiyalelo elishumi uYehova awayithetha kuni ngomhla wokuhlangana entabeni phakathi komlilo; wandinika ke uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 5, 'Ndajika ke, ndehla entabeni, ndawabeka amacwecwe etyeyeni endayenzayo zinjalo ke, njengoko iNkosi yandiwisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 6, 'Bayishiya oonyana bakaSirayeli eBheroti-bhene-yahakan, baya eMosera; Wafela khona uAron, wangcwatyelwa khona; unyana wakhe uEleyazare waba ngumbingeleli esikhundleni sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 7, 'Banduluka khona, baya eGudegoda; ethabathela eGudegoda, esa eYotebhati, ezweni loMjelo wamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 8, 'Ngelo xesha uYehova wanyula isizwe sakwaLevi ukuba sithwale ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova, ukuze sime phambi koYehova simkhonze, sisikelele egameni lakhe de kube namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 9, 'Ngoko ke uLevi akanasabelo nalifa ndawonye nabazalwana bakhe; nguYehova ilifa lakhe, njengoko wakuthethayo uYehova uThixo wakho kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 10, 'Ndema ke mna entabeni, njengemini yokuqala, iimini ezimashumi mane nobusuku obumashumi mane; Naye uYehova wandiva ngelo xesha, yaye uYehova akafuna ukunitshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 11, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Suka uye ebantwini, bangene balime ilizwe elo, ndafungayo kooyise, ndathi, Ndiya kubanika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 12, 'Kaloku ke, Sirayeli, uYehova uThixo wakho, ufuna ntoni na kuwe, kungekuko ukumoyika uYehova uThixo wakho, uhambe ngeendlela zakhe zonke, umthande, umkhonze uYehova uThixo wakho ingqondo yakho yonke, nangentliziyo yakho yonke umoya,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 13, 'ugcine imithetho kaYehova, nemimiselo yakhe, endikuwiselayo namhla ngenxa yakho?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 14, 'Yabona, amazulu, nezulu lamazulu, nguYehova uThixo wakho, nehlabathi, neento zonke ezikhona;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 15, 'NguYehova kuphela owakholiswayo ngookhokho benu ukuba abathande, waza wanyula inzala yabo emva kwabo, nina phakathi kweentlanga zonke, njengoko kunjalo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 16, 'Guqukani ngoku ezintliziyweni zenu, ningabi saqaqadeka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 17, 'Ngokuba uYehova uThixo wenu nguThixo woothixo, yiNkosi yookumkani, nguThixo omkhulu, onamandla, onamandla, ongakhethi buso bamntu, ongamkeliyo umvuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 18, 'Ugweba ityala lenkedama nomhlolokazi, Uthanda owasemzini, ngokumnika ukudla, nempahla yokunxiba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 19, 'Ngoko ke bathandeni umphambukeli, ekubeni naningabaphambukeli nani ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 20, 'Yoyika uYehova uThixo wakho; nimkhonze, ninamathele kuye, nifunge igama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 21, 'Nguye okuncomayo, yaye nguThixo wakho okwenzele ezi zinto zinkulu nezoyikekayo azibonileyo amehlo akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 10, 22, 'Behla ooyihlo ukuya eYiputa, bekunye namadoda angamashumi amathandathu; Kaloku ke, uYehova uThixo wenu, unandisile njengeenkwenkwezi zezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 1, 'Ngoko ke uze umthande uYehova uThixo wakho, ugcine imiyalelo yakhe, nemithetho yakhe, nemiyalelo yakhe, nemithetho yakhe, imihla yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 2, 'Yazini ngokwenu namhla, ngokuba andithethi kuni, nyana bangabonanga, bangabonanga, ubugwenxa bukaYehova uThixo wenu, nobukhulu bakhe, nesandla sakhe esithe nkqi, nengalo yakhe eyolukileyo,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 3, 'nezimanga zakhe, nemisebenzi yakhe awayenzayo phakathi kweYiputa kuFaro ukumkani waseYiputa, nakwilizwe lakhe lonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 4, 'nento awayenzayo kwimikhosi yamaYiputa, namahashe ayo, neenqwelo zayo zokulwa; ukuba wabakhukulisa emanzini aseSekelefeshe, ekusukeleni kwabo, awabatshabalalisayo uYehova unanamhla;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 5, 'noko wakwenzayo kuni entlango, nada nafika kule ndawo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 6, 'noko wakwenzayo kuDatan noAbhiram, oonyana bakaEliyabhi, unyana kaRubhen, wathi umhlaba wawuvula umlomo wawo, wabaginya, nemizalwane yabo, neentente zabo, nengqwebo yabo yonke ekubadleni ilifa phakathi kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 7, 'Kodwa amehlo enu azibonile zonke izenzo zikaYehova ezikhulu azenzileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 8, 'Ize niyigcine ke yonke imithetho endiniwiselayo namhla, ukuze nomelele, nileyise ilizwe elo ningena kulo ukuba nilihluthe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 9, 'ukuze niyolule imihla emhlabeni lowo uYehova awalithembisa ookhokho benu ngesifungo sokuba uya kuwunika bona nenzala yabo ilizwe eliqukuqela ubisi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 10, 'Kuba ilizwe oya kulidla ilifa alinjengelizwe laseYiputa owaphuma kulo, apho wayihlwayelayo imbewu yakho, wayinkcenkceshela ngonyawo lwakho, njengomyezo wemifuno.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 11, 'Ke lona ilizwe eniya kulidla ilifa, lilizwe leentaba nezihlambo, elisela amanzi emvula yezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 12, 'Lilizwe alinyamekelayo uYehova uThixo wakho; ahlala ekulo amehlo kaYehova uThixo wakho, ethabathela ekuqaleni komnyaka, ade ase ekupheleni komnyaka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 13, 'Ukuba nithe nayiphulaphula ngenyameko imithetho yam, endiniwisela yona namhla, nimthande uYehova uThixo wenu, nimkhonze ngentliziyo yenu yonke, nangomphefumlo wenu wonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 14, 'ndininike iimvula zelizwe lenu ngexesha lazo, iimvula zokuqala nezeemvula zamva, niyihlanganise ingqolowa yakho, nomdiza wakho, neoli yakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 15, 'Ndiya kuthumela utyani ezweni lemfuyo yakho, udle, uhluthe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 16, 'Zilumkeleni, hleze zilahlekiswe iintliziyo zenu, niphambuke, nikhonze thixo bambi, niqubude kubo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 17, 'Ngoku ke uyavutha umsindo kaYehova, wawavala amazulu, ukuba kungabikho mvula, nelizwe linganikeli iziqhamo zalo; nokuze ningangxami nitshabalale ezweni elihle aninika lona uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 18, 'Ke ngoko, la mazwi am wabekeni ezintliziyweni zenu nasemoyeni wenu, niwabophe njengomqondiso ezandleni zenu, ukuze abe njengeqhina phakathi kwamehlo enu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 19, 'Uze uthethe ngawo koonyana bakho ekuhlaleni kwakho endlwini yakho, nasekuhambeni kwakho ngendlela, nasekulaleni kwakho, nasekuvukeni kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 20, 'uwabhale emigubasini yendlu yakho nasemasangweni akho:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 21, 'ukuze yande imihla yenu nemihla yoonyana benu emhlabeni lowo uYehova wayewuthembise ookhokho benu ngesifungo sokuba uya kubanika, njengemihla yamazulu emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 22, 'Kuba, ukuba nithe nawugcina ngenyameko lo mthetho wonke ndiniwiselayo ukuba niwenze, nimthande uYehova uThixo wenu, nihambe ngeendlela zakhe zonke, ninamathele kuye;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 23, 'Yaye ngokuqinisekileyo uYehova uya kuzigxotha zonke ezi ntlanga phambi kwenu, yaye niya kuzidla ilifa iintlanga ezinkulu nezinamandla kunani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 24, 'Yonke indawo eya kunyathela ngentende yonyawo lwenu yoba yeyenu: ukususela entlango naseLebhanon ukususela kuMlambo umEfrate kuse elwandle kwelinye icala lelizwe iya kuba yindawo yenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 25, 'Akukho bani uya kuma phambi kwenu, kuba uYehova uThixo wenu uya kubeka ukunkwantya kwenu nokoyikeka kwenu kulo lonke ilizwe eniya kulinyathela ngokwalo njengoko nithethileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 26, 'Yabonani, ndininika namhla intsikelelo nesiqalekiso;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 27, 'Ninoyolo, xa nithe nayiphulaphula imithetho kaYehova uThixo wenu, endiniwiselayo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 28, 'Uqalekisiwe, ukuba nithe aniyiphulaphula imithetho kaYehova uThixo wenu, nasuka natyeka endleleni endiniyalela yona namhlanje ngokulandela thixo bambi eningabazi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 29, 'Xa athe uYehova, uThixo wakho, wakungenisa kulo ilizwe oya kulo ukuba ulidle ilifa, wayisikelela intaba yeGerizim, nesiqalekiso phezu kwentaba ye-Ebhali.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 30, 'Ndakuthi, Àziphesheya kweYordan na, ngaphaya kwendlela yasentshonalanga, ezweni lamaKanan, amiyo eminqubeni eGiligali, entilini yentlango kaMore?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 31, 'Kuba niya kuwela iYordan, nisiya kulihlutha ilizwe elo aninikayo uYehova uThixo wenu, nilihluthe ke nime kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 11, 32, 'Yenzani ngenyameko yonke imiyalelo nezigwebo endizibeke phambi kwenu namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 1, 'Yiyo le imimiselo namasiko, owoyigcina, wenze ezweni elo, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wooyihlo, ukuba ulime yonke imihla yobomi bakho emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 2, 'Niya kuziqalekisa zonke iindawo eziya kuthi iintlanga nizidle ilifa zikhonze uthixo wazo ezintabeni eziphakamileyo nakwiinduli naphantsi kwemithi yonke eluhlaza;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 3, 'nizidilize izibingelelo zabo, niziqhekeze izimiso zabo zamatye, nizitshise ngomlilo iziqu zabo; yigawuleni imifanekiso eqingqiweyo yoothixo bazo nize niwacime amagama azo kuloo ndawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 4, 'Uze ungenjenjalo kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 5, 'Kodwa endaweni aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wenu ezizukulwaneni zenu zonke, ukuba alimise kuyo igama lakhe, kuleyo ndawo ahlala kuyo, eniya kuyimisela khona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 6, 'Zisani khona amadini enu anyukayo, nemibingelelo yenu, nezishumi zenu, nomnikelo wokudla esandleni senu, nezibhambathiso zenu, nemibingelelo yenu yokuqhutywa yintliziyo, namazibulo eenkomo zenu, nasempahleni yenu emfutshane;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 7, 'nidle khona phambi koYehova uThixo wenu, nivuye ngenxa yento yonke eniya kuyibeka izandla zenu, nina nezindlu zenu, akusikeleleyo ngazo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 8, 'Musani ukwenza ngokwezinto zonke esizenzayo apha namhla, ukuba wonke umntu ozibona lilungisa kwawakhe amehlo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 9, 'Kuba okwangoku anikafiki kwindawo yokuphumla nelizwe akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 10, 'Xa nithe nayiwela iYordan, nahlala ezweni elo, aninikayo uYehova uThixo wenu, ukuba libe lilifa lenu, waniphumza ezintshabeni zenu zonke ezingeenxa zonke kuni, nahlala ninoxolo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 11, 'Kothi ke kubekho indawo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho, alibeke kuyo igama lakhe; uya kuzisa khona zonke izinto endikuwisele umthetho ngazo; amadini enu anyukayo, nemibingelelo yenu, nezishumi zenu, nomrhumo wezandla zenu, nezibhambathiso zenu ezikhethekileyo, enibhambathise ngazo kuYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 12, 'nivuye phambi koYehova uThixo wenu, nina noonyana benu, neentombi zenu, nabakhonzi benu, nezicakakazi zenu, nomLevi emasangweni enu; ngokuba akanasabelo nalifa nani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 13, 'Uze uzigcine ungawanyuseli amadini akho anyukayo ezindaweni zonke ozibonayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 14, 'Ke endaweni leyo aya kuyinyula uYehova kwesinye sezizwe zakowenu, wowanyusa khona amadini akho anyukayo, ukwenze khona konke endikuwisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 15, 'Kodwa inyama ungayixhela emasangweni akho onke uze udle ukutya okunqwenelwa ngumphefumlo wakho ngokwentsikelelo kaYehova uThixo wakho akunikileyo; intliziyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 16, 'Musani ukulidla igazi; liphalaze njengamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 17, 'Uze ungasidli isishumi sakho sengqolowa, nesewayini yakho entsha, neseoli yakho, nesamazibulo eenkomo zakho, nempahla yakho emfutshane, nesibhambathiso sakho osifungeleyo, nombingelelo wakho wokuqhutywa yintliziyo, nowokuqhutywa yintliziyo iminikelo hayi umnikelo wesandla sakho:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 18, 'Uze uzidlele phambi koYehova uThixo wakho endaweni leyo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho, wena nonyana wakho nentombi yakho nekhoboka lakho nesicakakazi sakho nomLevi emasangweni akho; nibe nemihlali phambi koYehova uThixo wenu ngenxa yayo yonke into eniya kuyibeka izandla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 19, 'Uze uzilumkele ukuba ungamshiyi umLevi yonke imihla yobomi bakho emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 20, 'Xa athe uYehova uThixo wakho wawenza banzi umda wakho, njengoko abethethe ngako kuwe, uthi, Ndiya kudla inyama, ngokuba umphefumlo wakho unqwenela ukuyidla inyama; ungadla inyama, ngokunqwena konke komphefumlo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 21, 'Ukuba ithe yakude kuwe indawo leyo, athe uYehova uThixo wakho wayinyulela ukulibeka kuyo igama lakhe, woxhela iinkomo zakho, nempahla yakho emfutshane, akunikileyo uYehova, njengoko ndakuwiselayo umthetho, udle emasangweni akho onke into oyinqwenelayo umphefumlo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 22, 'Uya kubadla njengokudliwa kwexhama nexhama; oyinqambi nohlambulukileyo boyidla ngokulinganayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 23, 'Lumkani, ningalidli igazi, kuba igazi libubomi; musani ukudla ubomi nenyama.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 24, 'Ungalidli; uyawuphalaza njengamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 25, 'Musani ukuyidla; ukuze kulunge kuwe, wena nabantwana bakho emva kwakho, ukuba nenza okulungileyo emehlweni kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 26, 'Kuphela zizipho zakho ezingcwele onazo, nezibhambathiso zakho, onokuthi uhambe uye kwindawo aya kuyinyula uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 27, 'wenze amadini akho anyukayo, ngenyama negazi, esibingelelweni sikaYehova uThixo wakho; igazi lomnikelo wakho woligalela esibingelelweni sikaYehova uThixo wakho, uyidle inyama wena.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 28, 'Yivani nize niwaphulaphule la mazwi onke ndiniyalela wona, ukuze kulunge kuwe nakoonyana bakho emva kwakho ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo, ukuba uthe wenza okulungileyo nokufanelekileyo emehlweni kaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 29, 'Ngenxa enokuba uYehova uThixo wakho wazitshabalalisa phambi kwakho iintlanga, lowo ungena kuzo ukuba uzihluthe, ke wena wazilandela, wahlala ezweni lazo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 30, 'Zilumkele ukuba ungaweli emgibeni wokuzilandela emva kokuba zitshatyalalisiwe phambi kwakho; ukuze ungabuzi koothixo bazo, uthi, Zibe zisithini na ezi ntlanga ukubakhonza oothixo bazo? Ndiza kwenza njalo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 31, 'Uze ungenjenjalo kuYehova uThixo wakho; ngokuba ziyenzile koothixo bazo zonke izinto ezingamasikizi kuYehova, awazithiyileyo; ngenxa yokuba kwanoonyana bazo neentombi zabo babebatshisa oothixo bazo ngomlilo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 12, 32, 'Konke endikuwisela umthetho ngako, uze ukwenze ngenyameko;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 1, 'Xa kuthe kwabonakala kuwe umprofeti, nomphuphi wamaphupha, wakunika imiqondiso nezimanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 2, 'Kwathi, kwakusenzeka oko umqondiso nomqondiso awuthethileyo kuni, wathi, Masibaleke siye thixweni bambi eningabazanga, sibakhonze;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 3, 'Musani ukuwaphulaphula amazwi aloo mprofeti naloo mphuphi wamaphupha, kuba uYehova uThixo wenu unilinga ukuze azi ukuba niyamthanda na uYehova uThixo wenu ngentliziyo yenu yonke nangomphefumlo wenu wonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 4, 'Landela uYehova uThixo wakho, umoyike, ugcine imithetho yakhe, uliphulaphule ilizwi lakhe, umkhonze, unamathele kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 5, 'Ke loo mprofeti naloo mphuphi wamaphupha makabulawe; ngenxa yokuba wayethe makakulahlekise uYehova uThixo wakho owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa aze akukhulule endlwini yobukhoboka ukuze akulahlekise endleleni awakuyalela ukuba uhambe ngayo uYehova uThixo wakho kwi bususeni ke ububi phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 6, 'Xa athe umzalwana wakho, nokuba ngunyana kanyoko, nonyana wakho, nentombi yakho, nomfazi wesifuba sakho, nommelwane wakho, onjengomphefumlo wakho, lowo wakungcatshayo ngasese, wathi, Masikhonze thixo bambi; osinikileyo akwaziwa wena noyihlo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 7, 'ngoothixo beentlanga ezingeenxa zonke kuni, ezikufuphi kuni, ezikude lee kuwe, kuthabathela esiphelweni sehlabathi, kuse esiphelweni sehlabathi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 8, 'Musani ukukholwa nguye, musani ukumphulaphula; malingabi nanceba kuye iliso lakho, ungamxoleli, ungamsithelisi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 9, 'Mbulale ke; Isandla sakho siya kumbulala kuqala, kwandule ke isandla sabantu bonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 10, 'Makaxulutywe ngamatye, afe; ngokuba wazama ukukugxotha uYehova uThixo wakho, owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa, wakungenisa endlwini yobukhoboka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 11, 'Wonke uSirayeli uya kukuva oku aze oyike, angabi saphinda enze into embi njengaleyo yenziwe phakathi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 12, 'Xa uthe weva komnye umzi wakowenu, kwathiwa, Loo nto akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba uhlale khona, ukuthi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 13, 'Kwaphuma amadoda angamatshijolo phakathi kwenu, abaqweqwedisa abemi bomzi wabo, athi, Masihambe siye kukhonza thixo bambi eningabazanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 14, 'Ngoku ufanele ukubuza kwaye uphengulule kwaye ubuze ngenyameko; yabona, ukuba yinyani, injalo loo nto, ewe ewenzile amasikizi anjalo phakathi kwenu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 15, 'Babulaleni bonke abemi baloo mzi ngohlangothi lwekrele, nibabulale ngesiqalekiso, nento yonke ekuwo, kwanemfuyo yawo, ngohlangothi lwekrele.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 16, 'Hlanganisela onke amaxhoba aso esazulwini sendawo yaso, usitshise ngomlilo umzi namaxhoba aso onke, kuYehova uThixo wakho; kwaye kuya kubakho ithemba ngonaphakade; ayinakubuyiselwa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 17, 'Makungafaki nto yesiqalekiso esandleni sakho, ukuze abuye uYehova ekuvutheni komsindo wakhe, abe nenceba kuwe, abe nenceba kuwe, akwandise, njengoko wafungayo kooyihlo ngesifungo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 13, 18, 'Xa uthe waliphulaphula izwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, wayigcina yonke imithetho yakhe endikuwiselayo namhla, ukuba wenze okuthe tye emehlweni kaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 1, 'Oonyana bakaYehova uThixo wenu; musani ukuzenza mnyama, ningenzi mpandla phakathi kwamehlo akho ngenxa yofileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 2, 'Ngokuba niluhlanga olungcwele kuYehova uThixo wenu, yaye uYehova uninyule ukuba nibe luhlanga lwakhe olukhethekileyo phakathi kweentlanga zonke zomhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 3, 'Uze ungadli nanye into elizothe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 4, 'Zizo ezi izinto ezizitho zine enozidla: inkomo, negusha, netakane lebhokhwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 5, 'Ixhama, ixhama, ixhama, ixhama, ixhama, ixhama nexhama.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 6, 'Sonke isilwanyana esiluthe gqiphu uphuphu nesahlule uphuphu lwaso lwacanda kabini, esidla uphuphu phakathi kwezilo, siya kuyidla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 7, 'Kodwa uze ungawudli kwababethayo, nakweziziqhekeze izikhonkwane; njengenkamela, umvundla, nenkamela; ngokuba bayabetha, kodwa abazahluleli izikhonkwane; ngenxa yoko baziinqambi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 8, 'nehagu, ngokuba iluthe gqiphu uphuphu, kodwa ayiwetyisi; ningayidli inyama yazo, ningayidli inyama yazo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 9, 'Zonke izinto ezisemanzini nozidla: Zonke izinto ezinamaphiko namaxolo nozidla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 10, 'Yonke into engenamaphiko namaxolo nize ningayidli; anihlambulukile.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 11, 'Zonke iintaka ezihlambulukileyo nozidla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 12, 'Zizo ezi izinto eningasayi kuzidla: lukhozi, nentaka, nentaka;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 13, 'novuyo, inkonjane, nexhalanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 14, 'nehlungulu lonke ngohlobo lwalo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 15, 'nenciniba, nenqu, nenqu, nenquba ngohlobo lwazo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 16, 'Nesikhova, nembande;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 17, 'nokhozi, nexhalanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 18, 'nexhalanga, ixhalanga nelulwane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 19, 'Yonke into enyakazelayo, ephaphazelayo, iyinqambi kuni; ningazidli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 20, 'Zonke iintaka ezihlambulukileyo ningazidla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 21, 'Musani ukuyidla into ezifeleyo ngokwayo; mnike owasemzini emnyango, adle; okanye ungathengisa ngayo kowolunye uhlanga, ngokuba usisizwana esingcwele kuYehova uThixo wakho. Usenokungaliboni itakane ebisini lukanina.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 22, 'Uze uthabathe isishumi kuyo yonke imveliso yembewu yakho yelizwe eliphuma minyaka le.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 23, 'Uze udle isahlulo seshumi sengqolowa yakho, nesewayini yakho entsha, neseoli yakho, nesamazibulo eenkomo zakho, nawempahla yakho emfutshane, phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyulela ukulibeka kuyo igama lakhe; ukuze ufunde ukumoyika uYehova uThixo wakho ngamaxesha onke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 24, 'Ukuba inde indlela kuni, aninako ukuhamba ngayo; indawo ekude kuwe, aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba alimise kuyo igama lakhe, ekusikeleleni kwakho uYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 25, 'Ngoku ke, tshintshisa ngemali uze uyibophe esandleni sakho, uye kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 26, 'Uze unike imali ngayo nantoni na oyinqwenelayo umphefumlo wakho, inkomo okanye imfuyo okanye iwayini okanye isiselo esinxilisayo okanye ngayo nantoni na oyinqwenelayo umphefumlo wakho; udle khona phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, uvuye, wena nendlu yakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 27, 'NomLevi emasangweni akho; musa ukumshiya; ngokuba akanasabelo nalifa nani.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 28, 'Ekupheleni kweminyaka emithathu, wokhupha sonke isishumi somvuzo wakho waloo nyaka, usiphose emasangweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 14, 29, 'Beze ke umLevi (ngokuba akanasabelo, nokuba lilifa elivela kuni), neenkedama nomhlolokazi osemasangweni akho, badle bahluthe; ukuba akusikelele uYehova uThixo wakho emsebenzini wonke wezandla zakho owenzayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 1, 'Ekupheleni kweminyaka esixhenxe, uze wenze uyekelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 2, 'Nantsi indlela yokukhululwa: Wonke umntu oboleka ummelwane wakhe uya kumkhulula; makangayifuni entsatsheni yakhe, nokuba kumzalwana wakhe; ngokuba kubizwa ngokuba lusindiso lukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 3, 'Ungaphinda uyicele kumntu ongamaziyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 4, 'ngathi akukho hlwempu kuni; ngokuba uYehova wokusikelela kakhulu ezweni elo, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba libe lilifa, ulihluthe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 5, 'Xa uthe waliphulaphula ngenyameko ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, uze uyenze yonke le miyalelo ndikuyalela yona namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 6, 'Ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho uya kukusikelela njengoko wathethayo kuwe, woboleka iintlanga ezininzi ngezibambiso, ke wena ungabolekisi ngazo; uya kulawula iintlanga ezininzi, ke zona aziyi kukulawula.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 7, 'Xa kuthe kwakho ihlwempu kubazalwana bakho kwelinye lamasango akho, ezweni lakho akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, musa ukuyenza lukhuni intliziyo yakho, ungasivaleli isandla sakho kumzalwana wakho olihlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 8, 'Kodwa vula kakhulu isandla sakho kuye, uze ngokuqinisekileyo umboleke ngokokuswela kwakhe, ngokokuthanda kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 9, 'Zilumkele, kungabikho ingcinga embi entliziyweni yakho, ithi, Usondele umnyaka wesixhenxe, umnyaka woyekelelo; libe libi iliso lakho ngakumzalwana wakho olihlwempu, ungamniki nto; Ubize kuYehova ngani, ibe sisono kuni oko.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 10, 'Mnike, ingabi mbi intliziyo yakho, xa uthe wamnika; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho wokusikelela ngenxa yale nto kuyo yonke imisebenzi yakho, nakweyonke into oya kuyibamba ngesandla sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 11, 'Kuba amahlwempu akasayi kuba saphela ehlabathini; ngenxa yoko ndikuwisela umthetho, ndithi, vula isandla sakho kumzalwana wakho ofunyenweyo, olihlwempu ezweni lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 12, 'Xa athe umzalwana wakho ongumHebhere uthe wazithengisa kuwe, indoda nokuba yinkazana, wakukhonza iminyaka emithandathu; uze umkhulule kuwe ngomnyaka wesixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 13, 'Ukuba uthe wamndulula ekhululekile, uze ungamndululi eyedwa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 14, 'Umnike ngesisa empahleni yakho emfutshane, nasesanda sakho, nasesixovulelweni sakho; umnike oko akusikelele ngako uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 15, 'Khumbula ukuba ube ulikhoboka ezweni laseYiputa, wakukhulula uYehova uThixo wakho; Yiyo loo nto ndikuyalela oku namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 16, 'Nokuba uthe kuni, Andiyi kunishiya; ngokuba ekuthanda, kwanabendlu yakho, ngokuba izinto zilungile kuwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 17, 'Ke kaloku, thabatha ikhonkco uze umgqobhoze indlebe emnyango, yaye uya kuba ngumkhonzi wakho ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo wenjenjalo kwisicakakazi sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 18, 'Akuyi kuba nzima kuwe ukuba umndulule ahambe nawe ngokukhululekileyo; Kuba ubefanelwe ngumvuzo weentsuku ezimbini, ukuba akhonze iminyaka emithandathu; yaye uYehova uThixo wakho uya kukusikelela kuko konke okwenzayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 19, 'Onke amazibulo eenkomo zakho, nasempahleni yakho emfutshane, ùngcwele kuYehova uThixo wakho; Uze ungenzi namnye umsebenzi ngemazibulo enkomo yakho, ungawachebi amazibulo empahla yakho emfutshane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 20, 'Uze ukudlele phambi koYehova uThixo wakho unyaka nonyaka kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova, wena nendlu yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 21, 'Ukuba lineqhenqa, nokuba sisiqhwala, nokuba yimfama, nokuba lineqhenqa, uze ungalisondezi kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 22, 'Udla emasangweni akho; oyinqambi nohlambulukileyo boyidla kunye, njengexhama nexhama.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 15, 23, 'Kodwa igazi layo musani ukulidla; uyawuphalaza njengamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 1, 'Yigcine inyanga enguAbhibhi, wenze ipasika kuYehova uThixo wakho; ngokuba wakukhupha ngenyanga enguAbhibhi uYehova uThixo wakho eYiputa ebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 2, 'Uze ubingelele ipasika kuYehova uThixo wakho, impahla emfutshane neenkomo, kuloo ndawo uYehova aya kuyinyulela ukuba alibeke kuyo igama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 3, 'Uze ungasidli isonka esinegwele kunye nayo; iintsuku ezisixhenxe wodla izonka ezingenagwele kunye nayo, isonka sokubandezeleka; kuba waphuma ngokukhawuleza ezweni laseYiputa, ukuze uyikhumbule yonke imihla yobomi bakho ngomhla wokuphuma kwakho ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 4, 'Iintsuku ezisixhenxe kungabonwa gwele kuwe ezweni lakho lonke; akwasala nto kwinyama ebixhelwe ngokuhlwa ngosuku lokuqala kwada kwasa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 5, 'Uze ungayibhiyozeli ipasika ezixekweni zakho akunike zona uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 6, 'Ke endaweni aya kuyinyulela ukulibeka kuyo igama likaYehova uThixo wakho, apho woyibingelela khona ipasika ngokuhlwa, ukutshona kwelanga, ngexesha lokuphuma kwakho eYiputa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 7, 'Woyithabatha, uyidle, kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho; guquka kusasa, uye ezintenteni zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 8, 'Wodla izonka ezingenagwele imihla emithandathu; ke ngomhla wesixhenxe ùngumthendeleko kuYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 9, 'Zibalele iiveki ezisixhenxe; qala ukubala iiveki ezisixhenxe ukususela xa wawuqala ukusasaza irhengqa phezu kwengqolowa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 10, 'Yaye wenze umthendeleko weeveki zokumzukisa uYehova uThixo wakho ngerhafu yomnikelo wokuzithandela wesandla sakho, oya kuwunikela kuYehova uThixo wakho, njengoko uYehova uThixo wakho akusikeleleyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 11, 'ube nemihlali phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, wena, nonyana wakho, nentombi yakho, nesicaka sakho, nesicakakazi sakho, nomLevi osemasangweni akho, nomphambukeli, nenkedama, nomhlolokazi wakho ophakathi kwakho elizweni awayinyulayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba alimise khona igama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 12, 'Khumbula ukuba ube ulikhoboka eYiputa; uyigcine, uyenze le mithetho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 13, 'Uze wenze umthendeleko weminquba iintsuku zibe sixhenxe, wakuba uyibutha ingqolowa yakho, nomququ wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 14, 'Yiba nemihlali emthendelekweni wakho, wena, nonyana wakho, nentombi yakho, nesicaka sakho, nesicakakazi sakho, nomLevi, nomphambukeli, nenkedama, nomhlolokazi osemasangweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 15, 'Kangangeentsuku ezisixhenxe uze wenze umthendeleko wokumzukisa uYehova uThixo wakho kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova, kuba uYehova uThixo wakho uya kukusikelela kuyo yonke imveliso yakho nasemisebenzini yonke yezandla zakho. Yonwaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 16, 'Izihlandlo ezithathu ngomnyaka, yonke into eyindoda yakowenu yobonakala ebusweni bukaYehova uThixo wakho, kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula; ngomthendeleko wezonka ezingenagwele, nangomthendeleko weeveki, nangomthendeleko weminquba; yaye abazange bavele phambi koYehova bengenanto.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 17, 'Wonke umntu makanikele kangangoko anako, ngokwentsikelelo akunikileyo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 18, 'Zimisele abagwebi nabagcini emasangweni akho onke akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ngokwezizukulwana zakho; yaye baya kugweba abantu ngomgwebo wobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 19, 'Musa ukulonakalisa isiko; aniyi kuhoya mntu, ningamkeli sicengo; ngokuba isipho simfamekisa amehlo ezilumko, siphenula intetho yamalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 20, 'Landela bonke ubulungisa, ukuze uphile, ulidle ilifa ilizwe elo akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 21, 'Uze ungazigxumekeli aAshera, kufuphi nesibingelelo sikaYehova uThixo wakho, ozakhela sona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 16, 22, 'Uze ungazenzeli umfanekiso oqingqiweyo; into ayithiyileyo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 1, 'Uze ungabingeleli kuYehova uThixo wakho, nkomo, nagusha ineqhenqa, nokuba sisiphi na isifo; ngokuba lisikizi kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 2, 'Xa kuthe kwafunyanwa kuwe, kwelinye emasangweni akho, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, indoda nokuba yinkazana, eyenze okubi emehlweni kaYehova uThixo wakho, ngokwaphula umnqophiso wakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 3, 'Waya wakhonza thixo bambi, waqubuda kubo, ilanga, nenyanga, nesazulu, endingawisanga mthetho ngaso;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 4, 'Kwathi, ekuxeleni kwakho, weva, wabuza, wabona, kuyinyaniso, inyaniso, ukuba enziwe la masikizi kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 5, 'Ke ngoko, yikhuphela loo ndoda, nokuba yilaa nkazana, iyenzileyo ububi ngaphandle kwamasango akho, loo ndoda, nokuba yiloo nkazana, uyixulube ngamatye, ife;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 6, 'Lowo ufanelwe kukubulawa wobulawa ngomlomo wamangqina amabini, nokuba ngamathathu; kodwa ngamlomo walinye ingqina makangabulawa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 7, 'Ziya kuba phezu kwakhe izandla zamangqina ngaphambi kokuba ambulale, kwandule ke kufike izandla zabantu bonke ubutshayele ke ububi, bungabikho phantsi kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 8, 'Xa kuthe kwavela ityala kuni elikhulu enkundleni ngenxa yenu, phakathi kwegazi negazi, phakathi komthandazo nomthandazo, naphakathi kwesijeziso nesigwebo, ngokuba ngumcimbi lowo emasangweni enu; ninduluke ninyuke niye kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wenu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 9, 'Yiya kubabingeleli babaLevi, nakumgwebi oya kubakho ngaloo mihla, ubuze; kwaye baya kukuxelela umgwebo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 10, 'Yenza ngokwesigwebo abo baya kukunika sona ngoxa ulapho kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova; uze wenze ngenyameko ngako konke abaya kukuxelela kona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 11, 'Yenza ngokomyalelo abaya kukuyala ngawo, nangokwesiko abaya kusithetha kuwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 12, 'Nabani na ofuna ukuzibeka kwindawo yokuqala aze angamphulaphuli umbingeleli omi apho ukuze akhonze uYehova uThixo wakho okanye umgwebi wakho, loo mntu uya kufa; yaye bususe ububi kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 13, 'Bonke abantu baya kuva, boyike, bangabi saqhayisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 14, 'Xa uthe wafika kulo ilizwe akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ulihluthe, uhlale kulo, uthi, Ndiya kuzenza ukumkani, njengeentlanga zonke ezingeenxa zonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 15, 'Zinyuleleni abe ngukumkani wenu, entweni yonke aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wenu; nimenze ukumkani kubazalwana benu; uze ungakhethi mntu wasemzini ongengomzalwana wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 16, 'Kodwa makangawandisi amahashe, angabavumeli abantu ukuba babuyele eYiputa ukuze andise amahashe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 17, 'Makangazazeli bafazi, ize ityeke intliziyo yakhe; yaye akayi kuziqwebela isilivere negolide eninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 18, 'Wothi, xenikweni athe wahlala etroneni yobukumkani bakhe, azibhalele impinda yombhalo yalo myalelo encwadini, esusela kubabingeleli abangabaLevi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 19, 'Yoba ngakuye, ayifunde yonke imihla yobomi bakhe, ukuze afunde ukumoyika uYehova uThixo wakhe nokuwagcina onke amazwi alo mthetho nale mithetho imiselweyo ukuba ayiphumeze;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 17, 20, 'ukuze ingaphakami intliziyo yakhe phezu kwabazalwana bakhe nokuze angatyeki emyalelweni, aye ekunene okanye aye ekhohlo, ukuze ayolule imihla yakhe ebukumkanini bakhe, yena noonyana bakhe, phakathi koSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 1, 'Ababingeleli babaLevi, nesizwe sonke sakwaLevi, mabangabi nasabelo nalifa kunye namaSirayeli; bawadle amadini anyukayo kaYehova, nelifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 2, 'Ke ngoko, abayi kuba nalifa phakathi kwabazalwana babo; uYehova lilifa labo, njengoko wathethayo kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 3, 'Lityala lababingeleli babantu abasondeza umbingelelo, nokuba ziinkomo, nokuba ziigusha; banika umbingeleli isandla, nezidlele ezibini, nesidlele.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 4, 'Umnike ulibo lwengqolowa yakho, newayini yakho entsha, neoli yakho, neentlahlela zompahla yakho emfutshane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 5, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova uThixo wakho wamnyula kwizizukulwana zenu zonke ukuba eme akhonze egameni likaYehova, yena noonyana bakhe ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 6, 'Xa kuthe kwaphuma umLevi kwelinye lamasango akho, kwaSirayeli ephela, abephambukele khona, weza ngokunqwena konke kwentliziyo yakhe, endaweni aya kuyinyula uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 7, 'Ke ngoko makakhonze egameni likaYehova uThixo wakhe, njengabazalwana bakhe bonke, abaLevi, abemayo khona phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 8, 'Baya kudla izabelo ezilinganayo, ngaphandle koko kuthengiswe kwilifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 9, 'Xa ufikile kwilizwe akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho, uze ungafundisi ngokwezinto ezicekisekayo zezo ntlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 10, 'Maze kungafunyanwa namnye kuni otshisa unyana wakhe, nokuba yintombi yakhe emlilweni, nosiyatha, nosiyazi, nosiyazi, nosiyazi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 11, 'nosiyazi, nosiyazi, nosiyazi, nosiyazi, nofileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 12, 'Ngokuba bangamasikizi kuYehova bonke abenza ezo zinto; yaye ngenxa yezi zinto zicekisekayo uYehova uThixo wakho uya kuzigxotha phambi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 13, 'Uze ugqibelele kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 14, 'Kuba ezi ntlanga uzidle ilifa zaphulaphula abakhafuli nabakhafuli; kodwa ke nina, uYehova uThixo wenu akakuvumelanga ukuba nenjenjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 15, 'uYehova uThixo wakho uya kunivelisela umprofeti ophuma phakathi kwenu, kubazalwana benu, onjengam; Uze umphulaphule;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 16, 'Njengako konke enakubuzayo ngomhla wendibano kaYehova uThixo wakho eHorebhe, ‘Andisayi kuphinda ndilive ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wam, yaye andiyi kuphinda ndiwubone lo mlilo mkhulu niya kuwenza.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 17, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Balitsho kanye ilizwi labo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 18, 'ndiya kubavelisela umprofeti ephuma phakathi kwabazalwana babo, onjengawe, ndiwabeke amazwi am emlonyeni wakhe; Wobaxelela konke endiya kubawisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 19, 'Kuya kuthi ke, ukuba uthe akaliphulaphula ilizwi lam, eliya kulithetha egameni lam, mna ndiwafune kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 20, 'Kodwa umprofeti yena othe wakhukhumala, wathetha ilizwi egameni lam, endingamwiselanga mthetho ukuba alithethe, nothe wathetha egameni lathixo bambi: loo mprofeti uya kufa naye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 21, 'Xa ke uthe entliziyweni yakho, Sothini na ukulazi ilizwi angalithethanga uYehova?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 18, 22, 'Umprofeti uthe wathetha egameni likaYehova, alabakho loo nto, ayenzeka, lilizwi angalithethanga uYehova, kodwa umprofeti wathetha ngekratshi; musani ukumoyika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 1, 'Xa athe uYehova uThixo wenu wazitshabalalisa iintlanga, aninikayo uYehova uThixo wenu ezweni lazo, nizilandela, nihlale emizini yazo, nasezindlwini zazo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 2, 'Zikhethele izixeko ezithathu ezweni lakho, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba ulidle ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 3, 'Zilungisele indlela, ulabe ilizwe lakho, aya kukunika ilifa uYehova uThixo wakho, ulabe libe zahlulo zithathu, basabele khona bonke abagxothwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 4, 'Nantsi into yesibulala-mntu, esithe sasabela ukuhlala khona, ukuba abulale uwabo engazi, ebengamthiyile ngaphambili;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 5, 'Njengoko indoda isiya ehlathini nentsapho yayo ukuya kugawula iinkuni, isandla sakhe sigawula izembe ngezembe lokugawula umthi, yaye intloko yaphuncuka emphinini, ibetha usapho lwakhe, wafa; uya kusabela komnye waloo mizi, aphile;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 6, 'ukuba umphindezeli wegazi angamsukeli umbulali lowo, isavutha intliziyo yakhe, imfikele; ngokuba nde kwendlela; ukanti ebengamfanelanga ukufa, kuba ebengamthiyanga ngaphambili.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 7, 'Ngoko ke ndikuyalela, ndithi: Zikhetheleni izixeko ezithathu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 8, 'Ukuba uthe uYehova uThixo wakho uthe wakhulisa ilizwe lakho, njengoko wafungayo kooyihlo ngesifungo, walinika lonke ilizwe elo, awalithethayo ooyihlo, ukuba wokunika;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 9, 'Ukuba uthe wawugcina ukuba ukwenze konke endikuwiselayo namhla, ukuba umthande uYehova uThixo wakho, uhambe ngeendlela zakhe ngamaxesha onke; uze wakhe ezinye izixeko ezithathu ngaphandle kwezi zithathu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 10, 'ukuze kungaphalazwa gazi limsulwa ezweni lakho akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho njengelifa, lize ke igazi libe phezu kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 11, 'Xa athe umntu wamthiya ummelwane wakhe, wamlalela, wamvunukela, wambetha wafa, wasabela komnye wale mizi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 12, 'othumela ke amadoda amakhulu omzi wakowabo, ukuba ayithabathe khona, amnikele esandleni somphindezeli wegazi, ukuze afe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 13, 'Ze lingabi nanceba iliso lakho kuye; ke ulisuse ityala legazi elingenatyala kwaSirayeli, ukuze kulunge kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 14, 'Uze ungawushenxisi umda wendlu yakho, abawubekileyo elifeni lakho, kwakudala, oya kulidla ezweni elo akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba ulime.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 15, 'Ze kungesuki kume ngqina linye ngomntu ngenxa yobugwenxa, nokuba bubuphi na, nangenxa yesono nokuba sisiphi one ngaso; Loo nto iqiniselwe ngomlomo wamangqina amabini, nokuba kungomlomo wamangqina amathathu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 16, 'Xa lisuke lasuka ingqina elixokayo lingqine omnye umntu, ukuba unetyala;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 17, 'Ke loo madoda mabini abambeneyo oma phambi koYehova, phambi kwababingeleli nabagwebi abaya kubakho ngaloo mihla babe khona;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 18, 'Kwaye abagwebi bafanele baphande ngenkuthalo; Ke ukuba lingqina lobuxoki, lingqine ubuxoki ngomzalwana walo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 19, 'Yenzani ngoko kuye, njengoko ebeya kwenza ngako kumzalwana wakhe; ubutshayele ke ububi, bungabikho phakathi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 20, 'Bova ke abo baseleyo, boyike, bangaphindi benze ububi phakathi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 19, 21, 'Aliyi kuba nanceba iliso lakho; ke umphefumlo uhlawule ngomphefumlo, iliso ngeliso, izinyo ngezinyo, isandla ngesandla, unyawo ngonyawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 1, 'Xa uthe wazingenela iintshaba zakho, ngamahashe, neenqwelo zokulwa, nabantu abaninzi kunokuba ubabona, uze ungaboyiki; ngokuba unawe uYehova uThixo wakho, owakukhuphayo ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 2, 'Ekusondeleni kwenu ekulweni, wosondela umbingeleli, athethe ebantwini, athi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 3, 'Ndiya kuthi kubo, Yiva, Sirayeli, namhla usondela ukuba ulwe neentshaba zakho; mayingabi mbi intliziyo yenu, musani ukoyika, musani ukungcangcazela, musani ukuqhiphuka umbilini zizo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 4, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova uThixo wenu nguye ohamba nani ukuya kulwa neentshaba zenu ukuze anisindise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 5, 'Abakhonzi bothetha ebantwini, bathi, Nguwuphi na umntu owakhe indlu entsha, akayisungula? Makahambe abuyele endlwini yakhe, hleze afele emfazweni, itshatyalaliswe ngomnye umntu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 6, 'Ngubani na lo mntu watyala isidiliya, akadla? makahambe abuyele endlwini yakhe, hleze afele emfazweni, idliwe ngomnye;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 7, 'Ngubani na indoda eganelwe umfazi, aze amzeke? makabuyele endlwini yakhe, hleze afele emfazweni, abanjwe ngomnye;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 8, 'Izicaka ziya kuqhubeka zithetha ebantwini, zithi: “Nguwuphi na umntu owoyikayo nodakumbileyo? makabuyele endlwini yakhe, hleze ithi thaa intliziyo yabazalwana bakhe, njengoko yenjenjalo intliziyo yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 9, 'Emva kokuba abathetheli begqibile ukuthetha nabantu, uze umisele abathetheli-mkhosi ukuba bakhokele abantu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 10, 'Xa uthe wasondela emzini, usiya kulwa naso, xela uxolo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 11, 'Ukuba uthe wawuphendula unoxolo, wavula, zonke iintlanga ezifunyenwe kuwo ziya kuba ngabahlawuli bakho, zikukhonze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 12, 'Ukuba ke akafuni kuxolelana nawe, wesuka walwa nawe, wuthintele;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 13, 'Ukuba uYehova uThixo wakho uthe wawunikela esandleni sakho, woyibulala yonke into eyindoda kuyo ngohlangothi lwekrele.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 14, 'Ke nina nazithimbela abafazi, nabantwana, neenkomo, neento zonke ezibe ziphakathi komzi, amaxhoba awo onke; udle amaxhoba eentshaba zakho, akunikileyo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 15, 'Niya kwenjenjalo ezixekweni zonke ezikude kakhulu kuni, kungekhona phakathi kwezixeko zezi ntlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 16, 'Kodwa phakathi kwezixeko zolu hlanga aya kukunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho njengelifa, uze unganiki bomi kuyo nantoni na ephefumlayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 17, 'Babethe ke ngesiqalekiso; namaHeti, nama-Amori, namaKanan, namaPerizi, namaHeti, namaYebhusi; njengoko wakuwiselayo umthetho uYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 18, 'ukuze banganifundisi ukwenza amasikizi abo onke, abawenze koothixo babo; none kuYehova uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 19, 'Xa nithe nawungqinga umzi imihla emininzi, nisilwa ukuba niwuthimbe, ize ningonakalisi imithi yaso ngokuyigalela ngezembe; ngokuba ungadla kuzo, ungazigawuli umthi welizwe bubomi bomntu) ukuzisebenzisa ukubhloka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 20, 20, 'Kuphela yimithi oyaziyo ukuba ayisiyomithi engadliwayo; woyitshabalalisa, uyigawule; Yakhani iindonga ezilwa nani, nide niwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 1, 'Xa kuthe kwafunyanwa ubani ezweni elo, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, wofunyanwa ezweni elo; akwaziwa ukuba ubulewe ngubani na;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 2, 'Ophuma ke amadoda amakhulu akowenu nabagwebi benu, balinganise imizi ewayiliweyo ngeenxa zonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 3, 'Umzi okufuphi nababuleweyo, amadoda amakhulu aloo mzi, athabathe ithokazi lenkomo, elingabotshwanga, elingabotshwanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 4, 'Athi amadoda amakhulu aloo mzi ayizisa imazi yenkomo emlanjeni, ingazalelwanga, ingatyalwanga, ayinqamla intamo leyo emlanjeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 5, 'Basondela ababingeleli, oonyana bakaLevi; ngokuba benyule uYehova uThixo wenu, ukuba bamkhonze, badumise igama likaYehova; kwaye ngelizwi labo lonke idabi nalo lonke uhlaselo luya kuzanywa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 6, 'Ahlamba ke onke amadoda amakhulu aloo mzi, akufuphi kwababuleweyo, izandla zawo phezu kwemazi yenkomo emlanjeni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 7, 'Aphendule athi, Izandla zethu aziliphalazanga eli gazi, namehlo ethu akabonanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 8, 'Yehova, yiba nemfesane kubantu bakho amaSirayeli owawakhululayo; musa ukuphalaza igazi elimsulwa ngokomthetho wabantu bakho amaSirayeli. Negazi liya kubaxolela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 9, 'Wolisusa ke ityala legazi elimsulwa phantsi kwakho ukuba wenze okulungileyo emehlweni kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 10, 'Xa uthe wazingenela iintshaba zakho, wabanikela uYehova uThixo wakho esandleni sakho, wathimba;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 11, 'Wabona inkazana eyinzwakazi phakathi kwabathinjwa, wayinqwenela, wayinqwenela ukuba ibe ngumkakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 12, 'Ngoko mngenise endlwini yakho; achebe intloko yakhe, achebe iinzipho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 13, 'Makakhulule ingubo yakhe yokuthinjwa, ahlale endlwini yakho, enze isijwili uyise nonina inyanga iphela; emveni koko wongena kuye, ube yindoda yakhe, yena abe ngumkakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 14, 'Ukuba akukukholisanga, myeke aye apho athanda khona; uze ungamthengisi ngemali, ungenzi nto naye, ngokuba umphoxile.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 15, 'Xa ithe indoda inabafazi ababini, omnye ethandwa, omnye ethiyiwe, bayizalela abantwana, lowo uthandwayo nalowo uthiyiweyo; ukuba unyana wamazibulo uthiyiwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 16, 'Ke kaloku xa ebavumele ukuba badle ilifa oko anako oonyana bakhe, makangammiseli owamazibulo lowo uthandwayo phambi konyana walowo uthiyiweyo, owamazibulo ngokwenene;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 17, 'unyana lo wothiyiweyo makamamkele owamazibulo, amnike izahlulo ezibini zento yonke anayo; ngokuba yingqalo yamandla akhe; ubuzibulo bobakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 18, 'Xa indoda ithe yanonyana oyinjubaqa, oneenkani, ongaliphulaphuliyo ilizwi likayise, nelizwi likanina, wamohlwaya, akaphulaphula;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 19, 'Uyise nonina bamthabatha, bamsa kumadoda amakhulu omzi wakowabo, nasesangweni lendawo yakhe yokuhlala;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 20, 'Uze uthethe kumadoda amakhulu edolophana yakowabo, uthi, Lo nyana wethu uneenkani, uneenkani, akaliphulaphulanga ilizwi lethu; ulidlakudla nenxila.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 21, 'Onke amadoda omzi wakowabo amgibisela ngamatye, wafa; ubususe ububi phantsi kwakho; yaye wonke uSirayeli uya kuva aze oyike.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 22, 'Ukuba ubani wenze isono esilingene ukufa, wobulawa afe, umxhonywe emthini;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 21, 23, 'isidumbu sakhe singahlali phezu komthi ubusuku bonke, uze ungcwatywe kwangaloo mini; ngokuba oxhonyiweyo uqalekisiwe nguThixo; ukuze ilizwe lakho akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho libe lilifa, lingabi yinqambi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 1, 'uze ungathi, uyibona impahla yomzalwana wakho, nempahla yakhe emfutshane, ebhadula; zibuyisele kudade wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 2, 'Ukuba umzalwana wakho akakho ngakuwe, nokuba akumazi, uze uyizise endlwini yakho, ibe kuwe, ade ayifune umzalwana wakho, uyibuyisele kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 3, 'Uze wenjenjalo nakwiesile layo; enjenjalo nezambatho zakhe; nazo zonke izinto ezilahlekileyo zomzalwana wakho, aphulukene nazo, uze uzifumane, yenza kwaezo zinto; usenokungazifihli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 4, 'Uze ungathi, ulibona iesile lomzalwana wakho, nokuba yinkomo yakhe, iwile endleleni, uzisithelise kuyo; kufuneka umncede azichole kwakhona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 5, 'Umfazi makanganxibi iimpahla zendoda, nendoda ize inganxibi ingubo yenkazana; ngokuba bangamasikizi kuYehova uThixo wakho bonke abenza loo nto.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 6, 'Xa kukho intaka endleleni yakho, nokuba kuwuphi na umthi, nokuba kusemhlabeni, nokuba kumathole, nokuba ngamaqanda, yaza ke izalela unina, nokuba ngamaqanda, musa ukuthabatha nonina, nokuba lincinane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 7, 'Noko ke, mndulule unina, athabathe abancinane, ahambe nawe; ukuze kulunge kuwe, ukuze uyolule imihla yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 8, 'Xa uthe wakha indlu entsha, lwenzela udonga uphahla lwakho, ukuze ungazisi magazi endlwini yakho, xa athe wawa owayo phezu kwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 9, 'Uze ungahlwayeli ntlobo ntlobo zembewu esidiliyeni sakho, hleze inzala oyihlwayeleyo, nesiqhamo sesidiliya sakho singangcoliswa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 10, 'Uze ungalimi ngenkunzi yenkomo ne-esile.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 11, 'Musa ukunxiba iimpahla ezizintlobo ngeentlobo, ezinjengoboya nelinen kunye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 12, 'Zenzele imiqukumbelo ezizibeni zone zesambatho sakho ozigubungela ngaso.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 13, 'Indoda esukuba izeka inkazana, yamngena, yamthiya;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 14, 'Wayithetha kakubi ngayo, wayizisa ngegama elibi, usithi, Ndimthabathile lo mfazi, ndakufika kuyo, andiwufumananga umkhonzazana wayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 15, 'Uyise wentombi nonina bathabatha iimpawu zobuntombi bentombi leyo, bazise kumadoda amakhulu omzi ngasesangweni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 16, 'Wothi uyise wentombi kumadoda amakhulu, Intombi yam ndiyinikelo mfo ukuba ibe ngumkayo, wayithiya;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 17, 'Wammangalela, esithi, Andimfumananga umkhonzazana wentombi yakho; kodwa, ezi iimpawu zobuntombi bentombi yam yandlala ingubo leyo phambi kwamadoda amakhulu omzi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 18, 'Oyithabatha amadoda amakhulu aloo mzi, ayibethe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 19, 'Bafanele bamnike ikhulu leeshekele zesilivere, balinike uyise wentombi, ngokuba wayiphathe kakubi intombi yakwaSirayeli; abe ngumfazi wayo; akayi kumshiya yonke imihla yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 20, 'Ukuba ke eli lizwi liyinyaniso, azafunyanwa iimpawu zobuntombi entombini;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 21, 'Bayithabatha intombazana leyo emnyango wendlu kayise, bayigibisela ngamatye amadoda omzi wakowayo, yafa, ngokuba yenze ubudenge kwaSirayeli, ngokukrexeza endlwini kayise; yisuseni ke ububi phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 22, 'Xa indoda ithe yafunyanwa imlala umkamntu, bobulawa bobabini, loo ndoda ilele naloo nkazana, kwanaloo mfazi; ubususe ke ububi kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 23, 'Xa ithe intombi eyintombi yayiganelwe indoda, yaza indoda leyo yayifumana phakathi komzi, yalala nayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 24, 'Bakhupheni ngoko bobabini ngaphandle kwesango laloo mzi, nibaxulube ngamatye, bafe; intombazana leyo, ngokuba ingabizanga isesixekweni; nendoda, ngokuba imonile umkayo; ngoko ke, bususeni ububi phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 25, 'Ukuba indoda ithe yafumana ephandleni intombi eganiweyo, yaza loo ndoda yayilala nayo, wofa loo mfo uyileleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 26, 'Ke musani ukuyenza nto intombi; entombini akukho sono silingenwe kukufa, njengoko kunjalo naxa indoda ithi imvunukele ummelwane wayo, imbulale afe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 27, 'Ngokuba wamfumana endle, yakhala intombi eganiweyo, akwabakho uyisindisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 28, 'Xa athe ubani wafumana intombi eyintombi engaganiweyo, wayibamba, walala nayo, bofunyanwa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 29, 'loo mfo uyileleyo womnika uyise wentombi amashumi omahlanu eeshekele zesilivere, ibe ngumkakhe; ngokuba emhlazisile, akayi kumshiya yonke imihla yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 22, 30, 'Indoda mayingamzeki umkayise, ingawuhluli ingubo kayise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 1, 'Umntu oxulutywe ngamatye, okanye onqunyulwe ilungu lomzimba, makangangeni ebandleni likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 2, 'Makungabikho mntwana ukrexezayo ungena ebandleni likaYehova; makangangeni ebandleni likaYehova, kude kuse kwisizukulwana seshumi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 3, 'Makungabikho mAmon nomMowabhi ungenayo ebandleni likaYehova; kude kuse kwisizukulwana sabo seshumi abayi kungena ebandleni likaYehova ngonaphakade;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 4, 'ngenxa yokuba benganikhawulelanga ngesonka namanzi endleleni ekuphumeni kwenu eYiputa; nangenxa yokuba baqesha uBhileham unyana kaBhehore, wasePetore, kwaMesopotamiya, ukuba aqalekise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 5, 'Akavuma ke uYehova uThixo wakho ukumphulaphula uBhileham; kodwa uYehova uThixo wakho wakuguqulela isiqalekiso saba yintsikelelo, ngenxa yokuba wayekuthanda uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 6, 'Uxolo nokulungelwa kwabo akuyi kulufuna naphakade, yonke imihla yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 7, 'Musani ukumcekisa umEdom; ngokuba engumzalwana wakho; uze ungamthiyi umYiputa; ngokuba ubungumphambukeli ezweni lakowabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 8, 'Oonyana babo besizukulwana sesithathu baya kungena ebandleni likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 9, 'Xa umkhosi uhlasela iintshaba zakho, zikhusele kuko konke okubi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 10, 'Ukuba kuthe kwakho nabani na phakathi kwenu ongahlambulukanga ngenxa yokungcola, noziphawulayo ebusuku, wophuma emke enkampini, angangeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 11, 'Kuthi xa kuhlwayo, azihlambe ngamanzi; latshona ilanga, wabuyela eminqubeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 12, 'Woba nendawo engaphandle kweminquba, apho uya kufuduka khona;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 13, 'Zilumkele izixhobo zakho; ukuba uthe waphambukela kubo, wemba, ubuye, ukugqume oko kuvela kuwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 14, 'ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho uhambahamba phakathi kweminquba yakho, ukuba akusindise, azihlangule iintshaba zakho kuwe; ke ngoko, umandlalo wakho woba ngcwele, ukuze bangaboni nto ingcolileyo kuwe, baphambuke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 15, 'Musa ukumhlangula umkhonzi osaba enkosini yakhe, eze kuwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 16, 'Sohlala nawe phakathi kwenu, kuloo ndawo sithe sayinyula kwelinye isango emasangweni akho, apho sithande khona kakhulu; musani ukumxina.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 17, 'Makungabikho ng’awukazi phakathi kweentombi zakwaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 18, 'Uze ungawuzisi umvuzo wehenyukazi nomvuzo wenja endlwini kaYehova uThixo wakho, ngenxa yaso nasiphi na isibambiso; kuba kwanazo zombini ziyinto ecekisekayo kuYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 19, 'Musa ukumboleka umzalwana wakho nzala; obolekisa ngemali, obolekisayo ngokudla, nabani na obolekayo unenzala;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 20, 'Uyakwazi ukumboleka omnye umntu ngenzala; uze ungamboleki kakhulu umzalwana wakho, ukuze akusikelele uYehova uThixo wakho ezintweni zonke osa isandla sakho kuzo, kulo ilizwe oya kulo ukuba ulihluthe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 21, 'Xa uthe wabhambathisa isibhambathiso kuYehova uThixo wakho, musa ukulibala ukusizalisekisa; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho uya kubuza kuwe; Oko kuya kuba sisono kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 22, 'Ke ukuba uthe akwafunga, akuyi kuba sono oko kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 23, 'Okuphuma emlonyeni wakho, kugcine, ukwenze; ewe, ube lidini lokuqhutywa yintliziyo, njengoko wamfungelayo uYehova uThixo wakho, owenze ngomlomo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 24, 'Xa uthe wafikelela esidiliyeni sommelwane wakho, wodla iidiliya ezininzi ngokuthanda kwakho; kodwa ungafaki nto emgqomeni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 23, 25, 'Xa uthe wangena entsimini yommelwane wakho engekavunwa, waluvuna ukhula ngesandla sakho; kodwa musa ukuphosa rhengqa kwingqolowa yommelwane wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 1, 'Xa ithe indoda yazeka inkazana, yamzeka, akwabakho mfazi ukuba angabi nanceba emehlweni ayo, ngokuba ufumene ukungcola kuyo; wambhalela incwadi yokwahlukana, wamnika, wamndulula endlwini yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 2, 'Ukuba ithe yaphuma endlwini yayo, yoya yaba ngowandoda yimbi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 3, 'Ukuba indoda yokugqibela iyamthiya ize imbhalele incwadi yoqhawulo-mtshato ize iyibeke esandleni sakhe ize imgxothe endlwini yakhe; nasekufeni kwendoda yesibini, eyamzekayo ukuba abe ngumkayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 4, 'Indoda yakhe yokuqala eyamqhawulayo ayiyi kumthabatha abe ngumfazi wayo emva kokuba enziwe inqambi; ngokuba lisikizi phambi koYehova; yaye ungalibeki ityala ilizwe elo akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba ulidle ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 5, 'Xa indoda ithe yazeka umfazi omtsha, mayingayi emfazweni, ize ingazithwali ngumthwalo nawuphi na umsebenzi; Woba mnye umnyaka ekhululekile endlwini yakhe, avuye umfazi wakhe amthabathileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 6, 'Makungabikho ubambisa umntu ngesibambiso ngaphantsi okanye umphezulu, kuba oko kukubambisa ngomphefumlo womntu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 7, 'Xa ithe indoda yafunyanwa isiba omnye ebazalwaneni bayo, phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli, mkhonze njengekhoboka, mhlawumbi ithengise ngaye; liya kufa ke elo sela; yaye bususe ububi phantsi kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 8, 'Zilumkele iqhenqa, unikele ingqalelo uze wenze kanye njengoko baya kunifundisa ababingeleli babaLevi; yenzani njengoko ndabawisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 9, 'Khumbula oko uYehova uThixo wakho wakwenzayo kuMiriyam endleleni ekuphumeni kwenu eYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 10, 'Xa uthe wamboleka umzalwana wakho, uze ungangeni endlwini yakhe, uye kuthabatha ibambiso kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 11, 'Wena yima ngaphandle, ithi loo ndoda uyibolekayo ikukhuphele isibambiso ngaphandle kwelizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 12, 'Ukuba ithe indoda yaba sisisweli, musa ukuya kulala unesibambiso sayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 13, 'Lakutshona ilanga, buyisela kuye isibambiso eso, alale ngengubo yakhe, akusikelele; kube bubulungisa bakho phambi koYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 14, 'Musa ukumcudisa olihlwempu, nolihlwempu elingumsebenzi wasemini, nokuba ngowabazalwana bakho, nokuba ngowabaphambukeli abasezweni lakho, emasangweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 15, 'Mnike umvuzo wakhe ngemini yakhe, lingatshoni ilanga kuyo; ngokuba elusizana, emise intliziyo yakhe kulo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 16, 'Aba oyise mabangabulawa ngenxa yabantwana, nabantwana mabangabulawa ngenxa yooyise; elowo uya kubulawa ngenxa yesono sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 17, 'Musa ukuligqwetha ilungelo lomphambukeli nelenkedama; nempahla yomhlolokazi ingazithabatheli idini;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 18, 'Kodwa khumbula ukuba wawulikhoboka eYiputa, waza uYehova uThixo wakho wakukhulula khona; ke ngoko, ndikuyalela ukuba wenze le nto.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 19, 'Xa uthe wagawula isivuno sakho emhlabeni wakho, walibala kakhulu emhlabeni, akuyi kuwuthabatha; zibe zezomngeneleli, nenkedama, neyomhlolokazi, ukuze uYehova uThixo wakho akusikelele emsebenzini wonke wezandla zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 20, 'Xa uthe wawuncothula umnquma wakho, uze ungabuyi ugalele amasebe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 21, 'Xa uthe wavuna isidiliya esidiliyeni sakho, uze ungasivuni kamva;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 24, 22, 'Khumbula ukuba ube ulikhoboka ezweni laseYiputa; ke ngoko, ndikuyalela ukuba wenze le nto.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 1, 'Xa kuthe kwabambana abantu, besa ematyaleni, bogwetyelwa ngabagwebi; apho baya kuligwebela ilungisa, bagwebe abangendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 2, 'Ukuba ongendawo uthe wafanelwa kukubethwa, umgwebi amlalise phantsi, ambethe phambi kobuso bakhe, ngokwetyala lakhe, ngokwesilinganiso.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 3, 'Angayibetha imivumbo emashumi mane, ingabi ngaphezu koko; ukuze ukuba uthe akagqithanga kuye, wambetha imivumbo emininzi kunale, akuphathe kakubi umzalwana wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 4, 'Ungayifaki isicheme inkunzi entsha, xa ibhula ingqolowa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 5, 'Xa bathe bahlala ndawonye abantu bezalana, wafa omnye engenabantwana, umfazi womfi makangendeli kwindoda yasemzini; umzalwana wendoda yakhe makangene naye, amthabathe abe ngumkakhe, afeze uxanduva lwakhe womzalwana wakhe ngenxa yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 6, 'Yaye owamazibulo aya kumzala uya kuphumelela egameni lomntakwabo ofileyo, ukuze igama lakhe linganqunyulwa kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 7, 'Ukuba indoda ithe ayakunanza ukumzeka umfazi womntakayise, makanyuke umkamfi lowo, aye esangweni kumadoda amakhulu, athi, Umzalwana wam, indoda yam iyala ukuliphakamisa igama lomzalwana wayo kwaSirayeli, ayiyi kuwumisa loo myalelo umsebenzi womninawa womyeni wam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 8, 'Ambiza ke amadoda amakhulu omzi wakowabo, athetha naye; Wema phambi kwayo, wathi, Andithandi ukumthabatha;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 9, 'Wofika umfazi womntakwayo kuyo phambi kwamadoda amakhulu, ayikhulule imbadada ezinyaweni zayo, ayitshicele ebusweni, amphendule, athi, Kwenjiwa nje loo ndoda kwindlu yomzalwana wayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 10, 'Kothiwa ke igama layo kwaSirayeli nguNdlw’-ihlangulwa-zihlangu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 11, 'Xa amadoda asukuzanayo, wasondela umfazi wenye ukuze asindise indoda yakhe esandleni salowo uyibethayo, yaye yena wolula isandla sakhe wayibamba ngasese;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 12, 'Sinqumle kaloku isandla sakhe, malingabi nanceba kuye iliso lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 13, 'Usenokungabi nobukhulu obahlukeneyo engxoweni yakho, enkulu nencinane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 14, 'Musa ukuba nemilinganiselo eyahlukeneyo endlwini yakho, enkulu nencinane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 15, 'Ke yiba nelitye elizalisekileyo, elilelobulungisa, nelitye elizalisekileyo, elilelobulungisa, ukuze izaliseke imihla yakho emhlabeni lowo, akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 16, 'Kuba bangamasikizi kuYehova uThixo wakho bonke abenza ezo zinto, nabo bonke abangemalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 17, 'Khumbula awakwenzayo kuwe ama-Amaleki endleleni, ekuphumeni kwenu eYiputa;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 18, 'owakuhlangabezayo ngendlela, wakubetha emhlana wakho, zonke ezityhafileyo emva kwakho, udiniweyo, udiniwe; akamoyika uThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 25, 19, 'Kothi, ekukuphumzeni kukaYehova uThixo wakho ezintshabeni zakho zonke ezingeenxa zonke kuwe, ezweni elo akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba ulime, usicime isikhumbuzo sika-Amaleki phantsi kwezulu soze uyilibale.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 1, 'Xa uthe wangena ezweni akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho ukuba ulihluthe, walihlutha, wohlala kulo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 2, 'uthabathe ulibo kwintlahlela yonke yomhlaba, owukhuphayo ezweni lakho akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ukuphose engobozini, uye kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula uYehova uThixo wakho beka igama lakhe apho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 3, 'uye kumbingeleli othe wakho ngelo xesha, uthi kuye, Namhlanje ndiyaxela kuYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba ndifikile ezweni, awafungayo uYehova koobawo ngesifungo, ukuba wosinika lona nika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 4, 'Umbingeleli makayithabathe ingobozi esandleni sakho, ayibeke phambi kwesibingelelo sikaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 5, 'Thetha, uthi phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, Ubawo ebengumAram eselunxwemeni lotshaba; wehla waya eYiputa, wahlala khona engumphambukeli, enabambalwa; yaba ligorha apho enkulu, inabemi abaninzi uluntu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 6, 'AmaYiputa asinqula ngomsindo, asicinezela, asenza amakhoboka anzima.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 7, 'Xa sasibiza kuYehova, uThixo woobawo, uYehova waweva amazwi ethu waza wakubona ukubandezeleka kwethu nomsebenzi wethu nokubandezeleka kwethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 8, 'uYehova wasikhupha eYiputa ngesandla esomeleleyo, nangesandla esoluliweyo, nangoloyiko olukhulu, nangemiqondiso, nangezimanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 9, 'Wasisa kule ndawo, wasinika eli lizwe, ilizwe elibaleka amasi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 10, 'Khawubone, ndizise ulibo lweziqhamo zomhlaba lowo undinikileyo, Yehova. Yibeke phantsi phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, uqubude phambi koYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 11, 'Uyonwabele zonke izinto ezilungileyo akunikileyo uYehova uThixo wakho, wena nendlu yakho, wena, nomLevi, nomphambukeli ophakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 12, 'Ukuba uthe wasinikela emvuzweni wakho wonke, ngomnyaka wesithathu ongumnyaka wesishumi, wazinika umLevi, nomphambukeli, nenkedama, nomhlolokazi, ukuba bawudle emasangweni akho adliwe emizini yenu igcwaliswe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 13, 'uthethe phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, uthi, Ndizikhuphile ezingcwele endlwini yam, ndiyinike umLevi, nomphambukeli, nenkedama, nomhlolokazi, ngokwemithetho yakho yonke, oyithethileyo wandinika bona andigqithanga kwimithetho yakho, andiyilibali;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 14, 'Andidlanga nto kuso ekuzileni kwam, andithabathanga nto kuso ngenxa yobunqambi, andinikanga nto yayo kwabangasekhoyo; Ndaliphulaphula ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wam, ndenza njengoko wandiwisela umthetho ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 15, 'Vela uvela esakhiweni sakho esingcwele emazulwini, ubasikelele abantu bakho, amaSirayeli, nomhlaba lo usinikileyo, njengoko wafungayo koobawo ngesifungo, ilizwe elibaleka amasi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 16, 'Namhlanje uYehova uThixo wakho ukuwisele umthetho, ukuba uyenze le mithetho nezigwebo; kugcine, ukwenze ngentliziyo yakho yonke, nangomphefumlo wakho wonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 17, 'Nimazile namhlanje uYehova ukuba unguThixo wenu nokuba nihambe ngeendlela zakhe nokugcina imiyalelo yakhe imisiwe nemiyalelo yakhe nezigwebo zakhe nokuliphulaphula ilizwi lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 18, 'uYehova uninyule namhla, ukuba nibe ngabantu bakhe abakhethekileyo, njengoko wakuthethayo kuni, niyigcine yonke imithetho yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 26, 19, 'aniphakamise ngaphezu kweentlanga zonke azenzileyo, ngendumiso, negama, nembeko; nibe ngabantu abangcwele kuYehova uThixo wenu, njengoko wakuthethayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 1, 'uMoses namadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli babawisela abantu umthetho, esithi, Yigcineni yonke imithetho endiniwiselayo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 2, 'Ngemini eniyiwelayo iYordan ningena kwilizwe aninika lona uYehova uThixo wenu, zilungisele amatye amakhulu, niwaqabe ngodongwe,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 3, 'uwabhale kuwo onke amazwi alo myalelo, wakuba ugqithile, ungene ezweni akunikayo uYehova uThixo wakho, ilizwe elibaleka amasi nobusi; njengoko uYehova uThixo wooyihlo wathethayo kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 4, 'Nothi, nakuyiwela iYordan, nimise la matye ndiniwisela umthetho ngawo namhla, entabeni ye-Ebhali, niwafuke ngodongwe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 5, 'wakhele apho isibingelelo kuYehova uThixo wakho, isibingelelo samatye; uze ungaphakamiseli isixhobo sentsimbi phezu kwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 6, 'Wosakha ngamatye apheleleyo isibingelelo sikaYehova uThixo wakho, unyuse phezu kwaso amadini anyukayo kuYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 7, 'nibingelele imibingelelo yombulelo, nidle khona, nivuye phambi koYehova uThixo wenu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 8, 'Wabhale ematyeni lawo onke amazwi alo myalelo ngokucacileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 9, 'Wathetha uMoses nababingeleli babaLevi koonyana bakaSirayeli bonke, esithi: “Zilinde, uphulaphule, Sirayeli! namhla nibe ngabantu bakaYehova uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 10, 'Liphulaphule ke ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, wenze imithetho yakhe nemimiselo yakhe, endikuwiselayo namhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 11, 'Ngaloo mini uMoses wabayalela abantu, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 12, 'Bema entabeni yeGerizim, ukuba basikelele abantu, ekuweleni kwabo iYordan; uSimon, noLevi, noYuda, noIsakare, noYosefu, noBhenjamin;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 13, 'Baya kuma entabeni ye-Ebhali, baqalekise; uRubhen, uGadi, uAshere, noZebhulon, uDan noNafetali.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 14, 'Mabathethe abaLevi, bathethe ngezwi elikhulu kumadoda onke akwaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 15, 'Uqalekisiwe umntu owenza umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, umfanekiso oqingqiweyo, olisikizi kuYehova, umsebenzi wezandla zengcibi, awubeke endaweni esitheleyo; Baphendula bonke abantu, bathi, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 16, 'Uqalekisiwe oqeqeshwe nguyise nokuba ngunina; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 17, 'Uqalekisiwe oshenxisa umda wommelwane wakhe; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 18, 'Uqalekisiwe olahlekisa imfama; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 19, 'Uqalekisiwe ojika isigwebo sabasemzini, nenkedama, nomhlolokazi; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 20, 'Uqalekisiwe olala nomkayise; ngokuba eyambethe ingubo kayise. Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 21, 'Uqalekisiwe olala nantoni na; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 22, 'Uqalekisiwe olala nodade wabo, nentombi kayise, nokuba yintombi kanina; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 23, 'Uqalekisiwe olala noninazala; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 24, 'Uqalekisiwe obetha ummelwane wakhe ngasese; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 25, 'Uqalekisiwe owamkelayo isohlwayo sokubulala umntu, omsulwa; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 27, 26, 'Uqalekisiwe ongawamisiyo amazwi alo myalelo ukuba awenze; Bathi bonke abantu, Amen!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 1, 'Ke ukuba uthe waliphulaphula izwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, wayigcina yonke imithetho yakhe, wakwenza endikuwiselayo namhla: wokuphakamisa uYehova uThixo wakho, ngaphezu kweentlanga zonke zehlabathi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 2, 'Yaye zonke ezi ntsikelelo ziya kuza kuwe zize zikufumane ukuba uthe waliphulaphula ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 3, 'Wosikelelwa phakathi komzi, usikelelwe emaphandleni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 4, 'Iya kusikelelwa isiqhamo sesizalo sakho nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho nesiqhamo seenkomo zakho, inkonyana yenkomo yakho nempahla yakho emfutshane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 5, 'Mayisikelelwe ingobozi yakho, nobuncwane bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 6, 'Woba nentsikelelo ekungeneni kwakho, ube nentsikelelo ekuphumeni kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 7, 'uYehova wozinikela zixatyelwe phambi kwakho iintshaba zakho ezivukelana nawe; ziya kukuhlasela ngandlela-nye, zikubaleke ngeendlela ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 8, 'uYehova wokusikelela empahleni yakho, nasezintweni zonke osa isandla sakho kuzo; yaye uya kukusikelela ezweni elo akunika lona uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 9, 'uYehova wonenza nibe ngabantu abangcwaliselweyo kuye, njengoko wakufungelayo, xa uthe wayigcina imithetho kaYehova uThixo wakho, wahamba ngeendlela zakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 10, 'Kwaye bonke abantu behlabathi baya kubona ukuba igama likaYehova libizwe kuyo; baya kukoyika wena.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 11, 'uYehova wokusikelela ngezinto ezilungileyo, esiqhameni sesizalo sakho, nesiqhamo senkomo yakho, nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho, emhlabeni lowo awafungayo uYehova kooyihlo ukuba wokunika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 12, 'uYehova uya kukuvulela ubuncwane bakhe obulungileyo, amazulu, ukuze unise imvula ilizwe lakho ngexesha elifanelekileyo, awusikelele wonke umsebenzi wesandla sakho; woboleka iintlanga ezininzi ngezibambiso, ke wena akuyi kuboleka nto kuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 13, 'uYehova wokwenza ube yintloko, ungabi ngumsila; uya kuba phezulu kuphela, ungabi phantsi; xa uthe wayiphulaphula imithetho kaYehova uThixo wakho, endikuwiselayo namhla, ukuba uyigcine, uyenze;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 14, 'uze ungatyeki emazwini onke endiniwisela umthetho ngawo namhla, uye ekunene nasekhohlo, ukulandela thixo bambi, ubakhonze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 15, 'Ke ukuba uthe akwaliphulaphula izwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba uyigcine yonke imithetho yakhe nemiyalelo yakhe endikuwiselayo namhla; zibe phezu kwakho ezo ziqalekiso zonke, zikufumane;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 16, 'Niya kuqalekiswa phakathi komzi, niqalekiswe emasimini;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 17, 'Mayiqalekiswe ingobozi yakho, novimba wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 18, 'uqalekisiwe isiqhamo sesizalo sakho, nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho, nesiqhamo senkomo yakho, nongeniselo lwempahla yakho emfutshane.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 19, 'Woqalekiswa ekungeneni kwakho, uqalekiswe ekuphumeni kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 20, 'uYehova wokuthumela iziqalekiso, nokuthethiswa, nokuthethisa, ezintweni zonke osa isandla sakho kuzo, ude ubhubhe, ubhubhe kamsinya; ngenxa yobubi bezenzo zakho ozenzileyo kum.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 21, 'uYehova wosibangela sinamathele kuwe isibetho ade akutshabalalise ungabikho emhlabeni oya kuwudla ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 22, 'uYehova wokohlwaya ngendyikitya yokufa nangecesina nangesifo sokudumba esitshisayo nangomlilo omkhulu nangekrele nangezinkemba nangokungunda; ziya kukusukela ude ubhubhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 23, 'Izulu lakho phezu kwentloko yakho loba lubhedu, umhlaba ophantsi kwakho ube sisinyithi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 24, 'uYehova woyenza imvula yelizwe lakho ibe luthuthu nothuli; iya kuhla iza kuwe ivela emazulwini, ude utshabalale.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 25, 'Woninikela uYehova phambi kweentshaba zenu; niya kuwahlasela ngandlela-nye, nisaba kuzo ngeendlela ezisixhenxe, nigungqiswe ezikumkanini zonke zehlabathi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 26, 'Izidumbu zenu zoba kukudla kweentaka zonke zezulu, nokwamarhamncwa asendle, kungabikho bani uziqwengayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 27, 'uYehova wokohlwaya ngeqhenqa laseYiputa, nangeqhenqa, nangeqhenqa, nangejaduka, ongayi kuphola kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 28, 'uYehova wokubetha ngokugeza, ngobumfama, nangokuphambana kwentliziyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 29, 'Uya kuphuthaphutha emini njengemfama ephuthaphutha emnyameni, ungabi nampumelelo ezindleleni zakho; yaye uya kuhlala ucinezelwe yaye uthinjwa, kungabikho bani ukuhlangulayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 30, 'Wozeka umfazi, alalwe ndoda yimbi; uya kwakha indlu, ungahlali kuyo; tyala isidiliya, kodwa ungavuni isiqhamo saso.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 31, 'Imfuyo yakho yoxhelwa phambi kwamehlo akho, ungayidli; 30 Ke iesile lakho liya kuthatyathwa phambi kobuso bakho, aliyi kubuyela kuwe; yonikwa iintshaba zakho impahla yakho emfutshane, ungasweli nto ukubasindisa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 32, 'Oonyana bakho neentombi zakho baya kunikwa olunye uhlanga, akhangele amehlo akho aze abe buhlungu ukubabona imini yonke, ungabi namandla esandleni sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 33, 'Isiqhamo somhlaba wakho nomsebenzi wakho wonke wodliwa luhlanga ongalwaziyo; yaye uya kuqhubeka utyunyuzwa, yaye uya kuhlala unoyolo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 34, 'ukuze ubhudiswe kukubona amehlo akho oya kukubona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 35, 'uYehova wokubetha emadolweni akho nasezinyaweni zakho, ngenxeba elingapholiyo, ethabathela entendeni yonyawo ase entloko.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 36, 'uYehova wokusa kuhlanga eningalwaziyo wena nooyihlo; nikhonze khona thixo bambi, imithi namatye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 37, 'Yaye niya kuba yintlekisa nesigculelo phakathi kweentlanga zonke aya kukusa kuzo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 38, 'Wozisa imbewu eninzi emhlabeni, uhlanganise into encinane; ngokuba iya kudliwa ziinkumbi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 39, 'Tyalani izidiliya, nizisebenze, ningaseli wayini noko, ningavuni zidiliya; ngokuba baya kudliwa ziimpethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 40, 'Woba neminquma ezindaweni zakho zonke, ungazithambisi ngeoli noko; kuba umnquma wakho wothwala isiqhamo sawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 41, 'Uya kuzala oonyana neentombi, ungabi nakonwaba noko; ngokuba baya kuthinjwa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 42, 'Yonke imithi yakho nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho siya kudliwa ziinkumbi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 43, 'Owasemzini ophakathi kwakho uya kusuka eme phezu kwakho; kwaye uya kuhla kakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 44, 'Wokuboleka yena, ungamboleki wena; woba yintloko yena, ube ngumsila wena.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 45, 'Zoza ke phezu kwakho ezo ziqalekiso zonke, zikusukele, zikubambe, ude ubhubhe; ngokuba ungaliphulaphulanga ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, ukuba uyigcine imithetho yakhe nemithetho yakhe owise umthetho ngayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 46, 'ibe ngumqondiso nesimanga kuwe, nakoonyana bakho kude kuse ephakadeni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 47, 'ngenxa yokuba ungamkhonzanga uYehova uThixo wakho ngovuyo nangentliziyo echwayithileyo ngenxa yobutyebi bento yonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 48, 'Ke ngoko, khonzani iintshaba zenu eya kuthi iNkosi izithumele ngokuchasene nani ngendlala nonxano kwaye niswele yonke into; abeke idyokhwe yentsimbi entanyeni yakho, akutshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 49, 'uYehova wokuzisela abantu bephela, abaphuma eziphelweni zehlabathi, abatshwebele njengexhalanga; luhlanga olulwimi lungenako ukuqonda;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 50, 'luhlanga olunobuso obuvutha, obungayihloniphi indoda enkulu, olungenanceba kumncinane;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 51, 'Nodla isiqhamo semfuyo yakho, nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho, ude ubhubhe; ukutshabalalisile.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 52, 'Lokungqinga emasangweni akho onke, zide ziwe iindonga zakho eziphakamileyo, ezinqabileyo, ozithembileyo ezweni lakho lonke; lukufikele emasangweni akho onke ezweni lakho lonke akunike lona uYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 53, 'udle isiqhamo sesizalo sakho, inyama yoonyana bakho neentombi zakho akunikileyo uYehova uThixo wakho, ekungqingweni nasekuxinweni, olokulukuhlayo ngako iintshaba zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 54, 'Indoda esukuba inembeko, nemfesane kakhulu phakathi kwakho, yoba libi kumzalwana wayo, nomfazi wesifuba sayo, namasalela abantwana bayo abasaseleyo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 55, 'ukuze inganiki namnye kubo inyama yabantwana bayo ayidlayo, ngenxa yokuba ingasenanto ekungqingweni nasekuxinweni, olokulukuhla ngako iintshaba zakho, emasangweni akho onke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 56, 'Umfazi olula phakathi kwenu, ongayi kuba nabuganga bakubeka intende yonyawo lwakhe emhlabeni, ngenxa yobulali nobulali, libe libi iliso lakhe endodeni yesifuba sakhe, nakunyana wakhe, nakwintombi yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 57, 'nomntwana ophuma phakathi kwemilenze yakhe, nangenxa yabantwana bakhe, abo aya kubazala; kuba uya kuzidla ngokufihlakeleyo ngenxa yokungabikho kwayo yonk’ into yokungqinga nexhala oluya kukulukuhla ngalo utshaba lwakho emasangweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 58, 'Ukuba anithanga nikunyamekele ukuwenza onke amazwi alo myalelo, abhaliweyo kule ncwadi, ukuze niloyike eli gama lizukileyo, loyikekayo, uYehova uThixo wenu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 59, 'uYehova wokwenza kube yimisebenzi yakho ebalulekileyo, nezohlwayo zoonyana bakho, ube sisibetho ezikhulu, nezifo ezihlala zihleli, ezinzima, ezingunaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 60, 'Uya kukuzisela zonke izifo zaseYiputa owawuzoyika; kwaye baya kunamathela kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 61, 'Nako konke ukufa, nayo yonke isohlwayo esingabhaliweyo encwadini yalo myalelo, wozinyusa uYehova phezu kwenu ude ubhubhe;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 62, 'nisale nibantu bambalwa, nakuba naningangeenkwenkwezi zezulu ukuba baninzi; ngokuba ungaliphulaphulanga ilizwi likaYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 63, 'Njengokuba uYehova wanithandayo, ukuba anenzele okulungileyo, anandise; ngoko ke, uYehova uya kukholeka kuni ukunitshabalalisa, anitshabalalise; yaye ngokuqinisekileyo niya kuthatyathwa ezweni elo uya kulidla ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 64, 'Woniphangalalisa uYehova ezintlangeni zonke, athabathele esiphelweni sehlabathi, ase ekupheleni kwehlabathi; yaye apho uya kukhonza abanye oothixo ababengabazi wena nookhokho bakho, abenziwe ngomthi namatye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 65, 'Kwaye phakathi kwezo ntlanga aniyi kufumana kuphumla, nentende yeenyawo zenu ayisayi kuzola; aze ke uYehova aninike intliziyo eyaphukileyo namehlo anorhatyazo nodandatheko lwengqondo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 66, 'Kwaye ubomi bakho buya kujinga phambi kwakho; unkwantya imini nobusuku, bungakhuseleki ubomi bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 67, 'Kusasa uya kuthi: “Ewe, bekungokuhlwa! ngokuhlwa uya kuthi, Kwowu, bekungomso! ngokoyikeka kwentliziyo yakho, oya kunkwantya ngako, nangenxa yokubona aya kukubona amehlo akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 28, 68, 'uYehova wokubuyisela eYiputa ngeenqanawa, njengoko ndathi kuni, Aniyi kuphinda niyibone; yaye apho niya kuthengiswa kwiintshaba zenu ukuze nibe ngamakhoboka namakhoboka, yaye akukho bani uya kunithenga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 1, 'Ngawo la amazwi omnqophiso, awamwisela uMoses umthetho ngawo uYehova, ukuba awenze noonyana bakaSirayeli ezweni lakwaMowabhi, ngaphandle komnqophiso awawenzayo nabo eHorebhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 2, 'uMoses wababiza bonke oonyana bakaSirayeli, wathi kubo, Nikubonile konke akwenzileyo uYehova phambi kwenu ezweni laseYiputa, kuFaro, nakubakhonzi bakhe bonke, nakwilizwe lakhe lonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 3, 'izilingo ezikhulu azibonileyo amehlo akho, kwanemiqondiso emikhulu nezimanga;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 4, 'Ke akaninikanga uYehova intliziyo yokubona, namehlo abo, neendlebe zabo, unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 5, 'Ndanihambisa entlango iminyaka emashumi mane; Iingubo zakho azonakalanga bubudala kuwe, neembadada zakho azonakalanga bubudala ezinyaweni zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 6, 'Anidlanga sonka, aniselanga wayini nasiselo sinxilisayo, ukuze nazi ukuba ndinguYehova uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 7, 'Nakufika kule ndawo, wasixabela uSihon ukumkani waseHeshbhon, no-Ogi ukumkani waseBhashan, sabaxabela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 8, 'Salithabatha ke ilizwe labo, salinika amaRubhen, namaGadi, nesiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase, ukuba libe lilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 9, 'Wagcineni amazwi alo mnqophiso, niwenze, ukuze nibe nempumelelo ezintweni zonke enisukuba nizenza.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 10, 'Yimani nonke namhla phambi koYehova uThixo wenu; neentloko zezindlu zenu, namadoda enu amakhulu, nabakhonzi benu, namadoda onke akwaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 11, 'abantwana benu, nabafazi benu, nowasemzini ophakathi kwenu, ethabathela emahlathini ase equleni lakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 12, 'wenze umnqophiso noYehova uThixo wakho, nesifungo sakhe, asenzayo uYehova uThixo wakho nawe namhla;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 13, 'aniqinise namhla nibe ngabantu bakhe, nibe nguThixo wenu, njengoko wathethayo kuni, njengoko wathethayo kuni ooAbraham, noIsake, noYakobi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 14, 'Ndenza lo mnqophiso nani nodwa nesi sifungo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 15, 'Kodwa ngubani na omi nathi apha namhlanje phambi koYehova uThixo wethu, ongekhoyo apha nathi namhlanje?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 16, 'Kuba niyayazi nina indlela esahlala ngayo ezweni laseYiputa, nendlela esacanda ngayo phakathi kweentlanga enadlula kuzo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 17, 'Wabona izinto zabo ezinezothe, nemifanekiso yazo eyenziwe ngomthi namatye, nesilivere, negolide, phakathi kwazo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 18, 'Makungabikho ndoda, namfazi, nantsapho, nasizwe sintliziyo ijikayo namhla kuYehova, uThixo wethu, ukuba sikhonze oothixo bezo ntlanga; kungabikho ngcambu ivelisa inyongo nenyongo phakathi kwenu;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 19, 'Kwaye akuba eweva amazwi esi siqalekiso, wazisikelela entliziyweni yakhe, esithi: Ndiya kuba noxolo, nokuba ndihamba ngeminqweno yentliziyo yam, ndisongeza ukunxila enxanweni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 20, 'uYehova akayi kuba nanceba kuye, kodwa umsindo kaYehova nekhwele lakhe uya kuvuka kuloo mphefumlo, ziwele phezu kwakhe zonke iziqalekiso ezibhaliweyo kule ncwadi, alibize uYehova igama lakhe phantsi kwezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 21, 'Yaye uYehova uya kumahlula kuzo zonke izizwe zakwaSirayeli ukuba abe mbi, ngokwemfundiso yonke yomnqophiso ebhalwe kule ncwadi yomthetho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 22, 'Siso eso isizukulwana senu siya kubonakala emva kwenu, aze athi umphambukeli ovela kwilizwe elikude, ekuboneni kwakhe ukohlwaywa kwelo lizwe nezifo azibeke kulo uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 23, 'yaye lonke ilizwe layo libe yisalfure netyuwa nomlilo ovuthayo, ukuze lingahlwayeli, lingahlwayeli, kungabikho ngca, njengokubhukuqwa kweSodom neGomora, iAdima Tsebhoyim awayitshabalalisayo uYehova ekuyitshabalaliseni kwayo umsindo wakhe nobushushu bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 24, 'Zothi ke zonke iintlanga, Yini na ukuba uYehova walenze eli lizwe? Kuthetha ukuthini ukuvutha komsindo onjalo?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 25, 'Bathi ke abantu, Kungokuba bewushiyile umnqophiso kaYehova uThixo wooyise, awawenzayo nabo ekubakhupheni kwakhe ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 26, 'Bahamba baya kukhonza abanye oothixo baza babanqula, oothixo ababengabazi nawayengabanikanga yena.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 27, 'Wavutha ke umsindo kaYehova lo mhlaba ukuze azise kuwo zonke izifundo ezibhaliweyo kule ncwadi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 28, 'uYehova wabanyothula emhlabeni wabo ngomsindo nangomsindo nangobushushu obukhulu, wabaphosa kwelinye ilizwe, njengoko kusenjalo namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 29, 29, 'Izinto ezifihlakeleyo zezikaYehova uThixo wethu, kodwa izinto ezityhiliweyo zezethu noonyana bethu ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo, ukuze siwaphumeze onke amazwi alo mthetho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 1, 'Xa zithe zanifikela zonke ezo zinto, intsikelelo nesiqalekiso, endizibeke phambi kwenu, wazikhumbula phakathi kweentlanga zonke, athe wakuphangalalisela kuzo uYehova uThixo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 2, 'Uze ubuyele kuYehova uThixo wakho, ulithobele ilizwi lakhe ngako konke endikuyalela kona namhlanje, wena noonyana bakho ngentliziyo yakho yonke nangomphefumlo wakho wonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 3, 'Wokuguqulela uYehova uThixo wakho ukuthinjwa kwakho, abe nemfesane kuwe, abuye akubuthe ezintlangeni zonke, akuchithachithileyo uYehova uThixo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 4, 'Ukuba ubani kuni ugxothelwe esiphelweni samazulu, uYehova uThixo wakho wonihlanganisela khona, anikhuphe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 5, 'Wokuzisa uYehova uThixo wakho kulo ilizwe ababelihluthile ooyihlo, ulime; uya kunenzela okulungileyo, akwandise ngaphezu kooyihlo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 6, 'Woyalusa intliziyo yakho uYehova uThixo wakho, nentliziyo yembewu yakho, ukuba umthande uYehova uThixo wakho ngentliziyo yakho yonke, nangomphefumlo wakho wonke, ukuze uphile.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 7, 'Wozizisa zonke ezi ziqalekiso uYehova uThixo wakho phezu kweentshaba zakho nakwabo bakuthiyileyo, abanitshutshisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 8, 'Uya kubuya ke wena, uliphulaphule ilizwi likaYehova, wenze yonke imiyalelo yakhe endikuwiselayo namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 9, 'Wandise uYehova uThixo wakho emsebenzini wonke wesandla sakho, isiqhamo sesizalo sakho, nesiqhamo senkomo yakho, nesiqhamo somhlaba wakho, kulunge; ngokuba uYehova uya kubuya akholiswe nguwe, kulunge, njengoko wabakholisayo ooyihlo:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 10, 'ukuba uthe waliphulaphula izwi likaYehova uThixo wakho, wayigcina imithetho yakhe nemiyalelo yakhe, ebhaliweyo encwadini yalo myalelo, wabuyela kuYehova uThixo wakho ngentliziyo yakho yonke, nangomphefumlo wakho wonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 11, 'Ngokuba lo myalelo ndikuwiselayo namhla awukude kuwe, awukude nokuba kude.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 12, 'Awukho emazulwini, apho ningathi, Ngubani na oya kusinyukela emazulwini, asithabathele, ukuze sive, siwugqibe?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 13, 'Nani phesheya kolwandle, nithi, Ngubani na oya kusiwelela ulwandle, asithabathele, siwuve, siwenze?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 14, 'Ngokuba ilizwi eli lisondele kunene kuwe, emlonyeni wakho nasentliziyweni yakho, ukuba ulenze.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 15, 'Yabona, ndibeke phambi kwakho namhla ubomi nokulunga, ukufa nobubi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 16, 'Kungenxa yoko le nto ndikuyalela namhlanje ukuba umthande uYehova uThixo wakho, uhambe ngeendlela zakhe, ugcine imiyalelo yakhe nemithetho yakhe nezigwebo zakhe, ukuze uphile, wande; yaye uYehova uThixo wakho uya kukusikelela ezweni oya kulidla ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 17, 'Ke ukuba ithe yalahleka intliziyo yakho, aweva;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 18, 'Namhla ndithi kuni, niya kudaka kuphele, aniyi kuyolula imihla yenu emhlabeni, nawela iYordan nisiya kuwuhlutha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 19, 'Ndingqinisisa amazulu nehlabathi namhla ngani, ukuba ndibeke phambi kwenu ubomi nokufa, intsikelelo nesiqalekiso; zinyulele ke wena ubomi, ukuze uphile, wena nembewu yakho;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 30, 20, 'ukuze umthande uYehova uThixo wakho, uliphulaphule ilizwi lakhe, unamathele kuye, ngokuba bubomi bakho nokolulwa kwemihla yakho, ukuze uhlale emhlabeni awufungelayo uYehova ooyihlo ooAbraham noIsake noYakobi, ukuba ndibanike wona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 1, 'Wahamba ke uMoses, wawaxelela onke amaSirayeli loo mazwi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 2, 'wathi kubo, Namhlanje ndiminyaka ilikhulu elinamanci mabini ndizelwe; Andisenako ukungena nokuphuma; Waphinda wathi uYehova kum, Akusayi kuyiwela le Yordan.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 3, 'NguYehova uThixo wakho oya kunikhokela, azitshabalalise ezi ntlanga phambi kwakho, uzidle ilifa; noYoshuwa, nguye oya kunikhokela, njengoko watshoyo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 4, 'uYehova uya kwenza kuzo njengoko wenzayo kuSihon no-Ogi, ookumkani bama-Amori, nakwilizwe lowabatshabalalisayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 5, 'uYehova wozinikela phambi kwenu, ukuze nenze ngokwemithetho yonke endiniyalele yona.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 6, 'Yomelelani nikhaliphe; musani ukoyika, musani ukuboyika; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho nguye ohamba nawe; Akayi kukulahla, akayi kukufulathela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 7, 'Wandula ke uMoses wambiza uYoshuwa waza wathi kuye phambi koonyana bakaSirayeli bonke: “Yiba nesibindi uze ukhaliphe, kuba wena uya kuhamba nesi sizwana uye kwilizwe awathembisa ngalo uYehova kooyise ukuba wobanika lona nika; yaye uya kubenza babe lilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 8, 'NguYehova okhokelayo; yena uya kuba nawe, akayi kukulahla, akayi kukulahla; musani ukoyika, musani ukoyika.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 9, 'Wawubhala uMoses lo myalelo, wawunika ababingeleli, oonyana bakaLevi, abathwala ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova, namadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli onke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 10, 'uMoses wabawisela umthetho, wathi, Ekupheleni kweminyaka esixhenxe, ngexesha lokubhiyozela umnyaka woyekelelo, ekubhiyozeleni kweminquba,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 11, 'Xa onke amaSirayeli eza kubonakala phambi koYehova uThixo wakho, kuloo ndawo aya kuyinyula, awulese lo mthetho phambi koonyana bakaSirayeli bonke, apho awuphulaphuleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 12, 'Bahlanganisele ndawonye abantu, amadoda nabafazi nabantwana, nomphambukeli osemasangweni akho, ukuze beve, bafunde, bamoyike uYehova uThixo wenu, bawagcine ngenyameko onke amazwi alo myalelo:', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 13, 'beve oonyana babo, ababengazi, bafunde ukumoyika uYehova uThixo wenu, ekuhlaleni kwenu emhlabeni, eniwela iYordan nisiya kuwuhlutha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 14, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Yabona, isondele imihla yakho yokuba ufe; Wamemeza uYoshuwa, wema ententeni yokuhlangana, ukuze ndimyalele. Bahamba ooMoses noYoshuwa, babazisa ententeni yokuhlangana.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 15, 'Wabonakala uYehova ententeni efini; lathi zinzi ilifu emnyango womnquba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 16, 'Wathi uYehova kuMoses, Yabona, uya kulala nooyihlo; basuke aba bantu bakrexeze noothixo basemzini belizwe abaya kuma kulo, bandishiye, bawaphule umnqophiso wam endawenza nabo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 17, 'Uya kwandula ke uvuthe umsindo wam kubo ngaloo mini, ndize ndibashiye ndize ndibusithelise ubuso bam kubo, batshabalale, bafikelwe ziintlekele neembandezelo ezininzi; ngaloo mini, baya kuthi: Ngaba asisayi kubunyamezela obu bubi, ngenxa yokuba uThixo wethu engekho phakathi kwethu?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 18, 'Yaye ndiya kubufihla ngokuqinisekileyo ubuso bam ngaloo mini ngenxa yobubi bonke ababenze ngokuphethukela kwabanye oothixo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 19, 'Ngoku ke zibhaleleni le ngoma, niyifundise oonyana bakaSirayeli; bayibeke emlonyeni wabo, ukuze le ngoma ibe bubungqina bam koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 20, 'Kuba ndithe ndabazisa kwelo zwe ndafunga kooyise ngesifungo, elibaleka amasi nobusi; baya kudla, bahluthe, batyebe; bajike baye thixweni bambi, babakhonze, badlale ngam, bawaphule umnqophiso wam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 21, 'Xa bathe bahlelwa bububi obuninzi, isuke le ngoma ingqina ngabo; ngokuba ayisayi kulityalwa emlonyeni wabantwana babo; ngokuba ndiyazazi iingcinga zabo ukuba basaxhalabile, nangoku, ndingekabangenisi ezweni endabafungayo kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 22, 'Wayibhala uMoses loo ngoma ngaloo mini, wayifundisa oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 23, 'Wamwisela umthetho uYoshuwa unyana kaNun, wathi, Yomelela, ukhaliphe, kuba uya kubangenisa wena oonyana bakaSirayeli kwelo zwe ndabafungela lona; mna ndiya kuba nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 24, 'Wagqiba uMoses ukuwabhala amazwi alo myalelo encwadini, ada agqitywa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 25, 'uMoses wabawisela umthetho abaLevi ababethwele ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 26, 'Thabathani le ncwadi yomthetho nize niyibeke ecaleni kwetyeya yomnqophiso kaYehova uThixo wenu, ibe bubungqina kuni apho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 27, 'Ngokuba ndiyazazi iingxaki zakho, nentamo yakho elukhuni; yabonani, andisahlali nani namhla, nigwilikile kuYehova; Kuya kuba njani na emva kokufa kwam?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 28, 'Ndihlanganiseleni onke amadoda amakhulu emizalwane yenu, nabakhonzi bakho, ukuze ndiwathethe la mazwi apho bawevayo khona, ndibize izulu nomhlaba phezu kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 29, 'Kuba ndiyazi ukuba emva kokufa kwam niya kutshabalala kuphele, nityeke endleleni endiniwisele umthetho ngayo; nokwehlelwa yintlekele ekupheleni kwemihla; ngokuba uya kwenza okubi emehlweni kaYehova, ukuba umqumbise ngemisebenzi yezandla zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 31, 30, 'Wawathetha ke uMoses amazwi ale ngoma, lada layiva lonke ibandla lakwaSirayeli, lada lagqitywa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 1, 'Yivani, mazulu, ndithethe; liveni, hlabathi, amazwi omlomo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 2, 'Ichaphaze njengemvula imfundiso yam, Ichaphaze njengombethe intetho yam, Njengomvumbi phezu kwezityalo ezithambileyo, nanjengemvumbi engceni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 3, 'Ngokuba ndiya kuvakalisa igama likaYehova; nimnike ubukhulu uThixo wethu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 4, 'NguLiwa, ugqibele umsebenzi wakhe, ngokuba zonke iindlela zakhe zisesikweni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 5, 'Bakhahlelekile, asingoonyana bakhe ibala, Isizukulwana esingendawo, esingendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 6, 'Nimbuyekeza ngaloo ndlela na uYehova, bantundini bazizidenge nabazizidenge? Andithi nguyihlo okuthengileyo? Akakwenzi na ukuba akuqinisekise?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 7, 'Khumbula iimini zasephakadeni, Qonda iminyaka yezizukulwana ngezizukulwana; Buza kuyihlo, wokuxelela; amadoda amakhulu akho, aya kukuxelela.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 8, 'Xa Oyena Uphakamileyo wazabela ilifa lazo phakathi kweentlanga, Ekubahlulahluleni kwakhe oonyana baka-Adam, Wayimisa imida yeentlanga ngokwenani loonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 9, 'Ngokuba isabelo sikaYehova ngabantu bakhe; uYakobi sisiphelo selifa lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 10, 'Wamfumana ezweni eliyintlango, Entlango, enkangala; wamsa kuyo yonke indawo, wamqeqesha, wamlondoloza njengokhozo lweliso lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 11, 'Njengokhozi luphaphazela phezu kwamantshontsho alo, luphaphazele phezu kwamantshontsho alo, luwolule amaphiko alo, luthabathe, luthwale ngamaphiko alo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 12, 'Ngoko uYehova yedwa wamkhokela, kungekho thixo wumbi kunye naye.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 13, 'Wamsa ezigangeni zehlabathi, ukuba adle imveliso yelizwe; wamdlisa ubusi engxondorheni, nangeoli elulwalweni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 14, 'Ubisi lweenkomo, nobisi lwezimvu, namanqatha eemvana, neenkunzi zeegusha zesizwe saseBhashan, neenciniba, kunye namanqatha ezintso zengqolowa; Wasela igazi elimsulwa leediliya.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 15, 'Watyeba ke uYeshurun, wakhaba; utyebile, utyebile, utyebile; Wasuka wemka kuThixo owamenzayo, Walidela iLiwa losindiso lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 16, 'Bamsola thixweni bambi, bamqumbisa ngezinto ezinezothe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 17, 'Babingelela kwiidemon, kungekhona uThixo; oothixo ababengabazi, abangoothixo abatsha abavele bavuka, ababengabahlonele ooyihlo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 18, 'Awunakulikhumbula iLiwa elakuzalayo, Ungamlibalanga uThixo owakudalayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 19, 'Wakubona uYehova, wabalahla ngenxa yokuhleka koonyana bakhe neentombi zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 20, 'Wathi, Ndiya kubusithelisa ubuso bam kubo, ndibone ukuba koba yintoni na ukuphela kwabo; kuba bayintsapho embi kakhulu, abantwana abangenalukholo kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 21, 'Bandikhweletisa ngongeThixo; bandiqumbisile ngamampunge abo, ndaba nobukhwele ngabangebantu; ndiya kubohlwaya ngabantu abaziziyatha;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 22, 'Ngokuba kuphenjwe umlilo emsindweni wam;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 23, 'Ndiya kubahlanganisela ububi; Ke utolo lwam ndoluphelela kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 24, 'Odliwa yindlala, odliwe kukurhala, nekuphanza elikrakra; ndiya kubathumela amazinyo amarhamncwa, nobuhlungu beenyoka zothuli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 25, 'Uya kuphanzisa umkhonto ongaphandle, zinkwantye ngaphakathi kumlisela nomthinjana, nomntwana nengwevu.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 26, 'Ndathi, Ndiya kubaphangalalisa ezimbombeni, ndisiphelise isikhumbuzo sabo ezintlangeni.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 27, 'Yayingekuko na ngenxa yokoyika umsindo weentshaba, naxa iintshaba zazo zingenzi ngendlela engaqhelekanga zaza zathi: “Izandla zethu ziphakamile, yaye uYehova akazange na akwenze konke oku?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 28, 'Ngokuba ngabantu abangenanjongo, tu ingqondo kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 29, 'Ukuba babelumkile, ngebekuqonde oko, Waliqonda ikamva labo!', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 30, 'Bebeya kubaleka njani na iwaka, yaye bekuya kuthini na ukusaba ishumi lamawaka amabini, ukuba iLiwa labo belingathengisanga ngabo, waza uYehova wabazala?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 31, 'Ngokuba alinjengeLiwa lethu iliwa lazo, lintshaba zethu zingabagwebi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 32, 'Ngokuba iidiliya zabo zizidiliya zaseSodom, namasimi aseGomora; Iidiliya zabo ziidiliya ezinencasa, iidiliya zabo zinobukrakra;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 33, 'Bubuhlungu beempungutye iwayini yabo, Bubuhlungu obubulalayo bezizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 34, 'Ayihlanganiselwanga na kum, yatywinwa koovimba bam?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 35, 'Yeyam impindezelo nesohlwayo; Unyawo lwabo luya kukhubeka ngexesha elifanelekileyo, ngenxa yokuba isondele imini yentlekele yabo, yaye izinto ezehlelayo ziyakhawuleza.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 36, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova uya kubagweba abantu bakhe yaye uya kuba buhlungu ngenxa yabakhonzi bakhe xa ebona amandla abo ephelile, yaye akukho bani uvalelweyo okanye ushiywe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 37, 'Uya kuthi, Baphi na oothixo babo, iLiwa labo ababekholose ngalo?', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 38, 'Abadla amanqatha emibingelelo yabo, Abasela iwayini yeminikelo yabo ethululwayo? makavuke, akuncede, abe lukhuselo lwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 39, 'Bonani ngoku, ukuba ndikho nje, ngokuba kungekho thixo unam. Ndiyabulala, ndidlise ubomi; Ndihlabile, ndiphilisa, akukho unokuhlangula esandleni sam.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 40, 'Ngokuba ndisiphakamisela ezulwini isandla sam, Ndithi, Ndihleli ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 41, 'Ukuba ndililolile ikrele lam elibengezelayo, Sabamba isigwebo ngesandla sam; Ndiya kuphindezela kwiintshaba zam, ndiphindezele kwabandithiyayo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 42, 'Ndiza kuzinxilisa iintolo zam egazini, nekrele lam liya kudla inyama; kwaye oku ngegazi labo babuleweyo nabathinjwe, ukususela ekuqaleni kwempindezelo kutshaba.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 43, 'Memelelani, zintlanga, bantu bakhe, ngenxa yokuba eliphindezelela igazi labakhonzi bakhe, eliphindezelela impindezelo kubachasi bakhe, abe nemfesane ezweni lakhe nakubantu bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 44, 'Weza ke uMoses, wawathetha onke amazwi ale ngoma, bephulaphule abantu, yena noHoseya unyana kaNun.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 45, 'Wagqiba uMoses ukuwathetha onke la mazwi koonyana bakaSirayeli bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 46, 'Wathi kuwo, Wabekeleni iintliziyo zenu onke amazwi endiwangqinayo phakathi kwenu namhla, nibawisele umthetho oonyana benu, ukuba bagcine ukuwenza onke amazwi alo myalelo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 47, 'Kuba akulambatha kuni; ngokuba bubomi bakho; yaye ngenxa yoko niya kuyandisa imihla yenu kwilizwe eniwela iYordan nisiya kulidla ilifa.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 48, 'Wathetha uYehova kuMoses kwangaloo mini, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 49, 'Nyuka uye kule ntaba yeAbharim, uye entabeni yeNebho, esezweni lakwaMowabhi, malungana neYeriko; ukhangele ilizwe lakwaKanan, endilinika oonyana bakaSirayeli ukuba libe lilifa labo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 50, 'Wena ufele entabeni, oyinyukayo, uphumle phakathi kwabantu bakowenu; njengoko wafelayo umkhuluwa wakho uAron entabeni yeHore, wathatyathwa phakathi kwabantu bakowabo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 51, 'Kungenxa yokuba nalahlwayo phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli emanzini aseMeribha yaseKadeshe entlango yaseSine; ngenxa yokuba ningandingcwalisanga phakathi koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 32, 52, 'Wolibona ilizwe liphambi kwakho; ke aniyi kungena ezweni endilinika oonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 1, 'Yiyo le intsikelelo, awabasikelela ngayo uMoses, umfo wakwaThixo, oonyana bakaSirayeli, engekafi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 2, 'Wathi, uYehova wavela eSinayi, wabakhupha kwaSehire; Wabengezela esezintabeni zaseParan, weza neshumi lamawaka abantu bengcwele; ekunene kwakhe ngumthetho womlilo kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 3, 'Ewe, wayebathanda abantu; Bonke abangcwele bakhe basezandleni zenu, yaye bahleli ezinyaweni zenu; bonke baya kuwamkela amazwi akho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 4, 'uMoses wasiwisela umyalelo, Ilifa ke elo lebandla lakwaYakobi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 5, 'Waba ngukumkani kwaYeshurun, Ekuzihlanganiseni iintloko zabantu, nezizwe zakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 6, 'uRubhen makadle ubomi, angafi; kwaye amadoda akhe makangabi buthathaka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 7, 'Yiyo le intsikelelo kaYuda: yaye wathi: “Yehova, liphulaphule ilizwi likaYuda, uze umzise kubantu bakowabo; iingalo zakhe zimnele; Umncede ezintshabeni zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 8, 'Wathi uLevi, IiTumim zakho neeUrim zakho mazibe koyiNgcwele wakho, Owamlingayo eMasa, Owamnyulayo emanzini aseMeribha;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 9, 'Lowo wathi kuyise nakunina, Andimbonanga; yaye akabazi abantakwabo, akabazi nabantwana bakhe, ngenxa yokuba baligcina ilizwi lakho nomnqophiso wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 10, 'Baya kumyala uYakobi ngamasiko akho, bamfundise uSirayeli umyalelo wakho; baqhumisele phambi kwakho, baqhumisele ngamadini anyukayo esibingelelweni sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 11, 'Dumisani, Yehova, ukulunga kwakhe, Yamkelani imisebenzi yezandla zakhe; wababetha esinqeni abo basukela phezulu kuye, nabamthiyayo, bangabi savuka.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 12, 'NgoBhenjamin wathi, Intanda kaYehova iya kuhlala kuye ikholosile; yaye uYehova uya kumgubungela yonke imihla, yaye uya kuhlala phakathi kwamagxa akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 13, 'Wathi uYosefu, uYehova makalisikelele ilizwe lakhe ngezinto ezinqabileyo zezulu, nangombethe, naphezu komlambo wamanzi asezantsi;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 14, 'nakwiziqhamo ezilungileyo eziveliswa lilanga, nakwiziqhamo ezilungileyo eziveliswa yinyanga.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 15, 'Ngezinto ezinqwenelekayo zeentaba zamandulo, Nezinto ezinqabileyo ezisezintabeni ezihlala zihleli;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 16, 'Ngokuphathelele izinto ezinqwenelekayo zehlabathi nenzaliseko yalo nokukholisa lowo uhlala emahlathini: Intsikelelo mayibe entlokweni kaYosefu nasentlokweni yalowo wahlukanisiweyo naye abazalwana.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 17, 'Eyamazibulo inkunzi yakhe, ubungangamsha bayo, neempondo zayo zinjengeempondo zenqu; ngoko ke uya kubatyhala abantu kude kuse eziphelweni zehlabathi; yaye bangamawaka alishumi akwaEfrayim, yaye bangamawaka akwaManase.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 18, 'Ngokusingisele kuZebhulon wathi, Yiba nemihlali, Zebhulon, ngenxa yokumka kwakho; noIsakare ezintenteni zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 19, 'Baya kubizela entabeni iintlanga; baya kubingelela khona imibingelelo yobulungisa; ngokuba besanya ubutyebi baselwandle nobuncwane obufihliweyo entlabathini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 20, 'NgoGadi wathi, Makabongwe owandisa uGadi; uhleli njengengonyama, esolula isandla sakhe elukakayini lwentloko yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 21, 'Wazinyulela isahlulo esiyingqalo; ngokuba besihleli khona isabelo sommisi-mthetho; Wabazisa iintloko zabantu, wenza ubulungisa bukaYehova, namasiko akhe kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 22, 'Wathi yena uDan, uDan yingonyama; uya kubonakala eBhashan.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 23, 'Wathi yena uNafetali, Nafetali, yaneliseke yintsikelelo kaYehova; owasentshona nomzantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 24, 'Wathi uAshere, Usikelelwe ngoonyana uAshere; Makamkeleke kubazalwana bakhe, athi nkxu unyawo lwakhe eolini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 25, 'Iimbadada zakho mazibe yintsimbi nobhedu; kube njengemihla yakho ukuqina kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 26, 'Akukho unjengoThixo, Yeshurun, unyuka emazulwini ukuba ancede, Nokuphakama kwakhe emazulwini.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 27, 'Likhaya uThixo wamandulo, Ngaphantsi ziingalo ezingunaphakade; wolugxotha utshaba phambi kwenu; bathi, Batshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 28, 'uSirayeli uya kuhlala yedwa ekonwabayo; Iqula likaYakobi liya kuba sezweni lengqolowa nelewayini; nesibhakabhaka sakhe siya kuwisa umbethe.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 33, 29, 'Unoyolo, Sirayeli, onjengawe, luhlanga oluhlawulelweyo nguYehova, Ikhaka loncedo lwakho, Ikrele lobukhulu bakho zofunyanwa zixoka kuni iintshaba zenu; yaye uya kuzinyathela iindawo zabo eziphakamileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 1, 'uMoses wazishiya iintlango zakwaMowabhi, wenyuka waya entabeni yeNebho, esangweni lePisga, malungana neYeriko. uYehova wambonisa lonke ilizwe laseGiliyadi, kwesa kwaDan;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 2, 'nelakwaNafetali lonke, nelizwe lakwaEfrayim, nelakwaManase, nelizwe lonke lakwaYuda, kwesa elwandle nganeno kwayo;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 3, 'nelizwe lasezantsi, nentlango yaseYeriko, umzi wamasundu, lesa eTsohare.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 4, 'Wathi uYehova kuye, Lilo eli ilizwe endafunga ngalo kooAbraham noIsake noYakobi, ndathi, Ndiya kulinika imbewu yakho; Ndikubonise ngamehlo akho, kodwa ungahambi. Pha.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 5, 'Wafela khona uMoses, umkhonzi kaYehova, ezweni lakwaMowabhi, ngokwelizwi likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 6, 'Wamngcwabela emfuleni wakwaMowabhi, ngaseBhete-pehore, engaziwa bani ingcwaba lakhe unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 7, 'uMoses ubeminyaka ilikhulu elinamanci mabini ezelwe, ukufa kwakhe; Laye lingasenalurhatyazo iliso lakhe, engekabi nawo amandla emvelo.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 8, 'Oonyana bakaSirayeli bamlilela uMoses ezinkqantosini zakwaMowabhi iintsuku ezimashumi mathathu; zaphela ke iintsuku zokulila nokumzilela uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 9, 'Waza uYoshuwa, unyana kaNun, wazala ngumoya wobulumko; ngokuba uMoses wabeka izandla phezu kwakhe; Bamthobela oonyana bakaSirayeli, benza njengoko uYehova wamwiselayo umthetho uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 10, 'Ukususela ngelo xesha akuzange kubonakale mprofeti unjengoMoses kwaSirayeli, ubemazi uYehova bekhangelene ebusweni;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 11, 'nemiqondiso yonke, nezimanga, awamthumayo uYehova ukuba azenze ezweni laseYiputa kuFaro, nakubakhonzi bakhe bonke, nakwilizwe lakhe lonke;', 'XHO22'),
(5, 34, 12, 'nangaso sonke eso sandla sithe nkqi, nako konke ukoyika okukhulu awakwenzayo uMoses emehlweni oonyana bakaSirayeli bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 1, 'Kwathi, akufa uMoses umkhonzi kaYehova, wathetha uYehova kuYoshuwa unyana kaNun, umkhonzi kaMoses, esithi,', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 2, 'uMoses umkhonzi wam ufile; Suka kaloku, uyiwele iYordan le, wena naba bantu bonke, ningene ezweni endilinika oonyana bakaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 3, 'Iindawo zonke eziya kunyathela kuyo intende yonyawo lwenu, ndininikile, njengoko ndathethayo kuMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 4, 'Ukususela entlango le Lebhanon kuse kumlambo omkhulu, uMlambo umEfrate, lonke ilizwe lamaHeti, ukuya kufikelela kuLwandle Olukhulu ekutshoneni kwelanga, iya kuba ngumda wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 5, 'Akukho mntu uya kuma phambi kwakho yonke imihla yokudla kwakho ubomi; ndiya kuba nawe, njengokuba bendinoMoses; Andisoze ndikushiye okanye ndikufulathele.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 6, 'Yomelela ukhaliphe, ngenxa yokuba olu hlanga uya kulunika ilizwe endathembisa ookhokho balo ngesifungo sokuba ndiya kubanika lona njengelifa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 7, 'Kodwa ke zomelela, ukhaliphe kunene, ukuze wenze ngokomyalelo wonke, awawisa umthetho ngawo uMoses umkhonzi wam, ungatyeki kuwo, uye ekunene nasekhohlo, ukuze ube ngengqiqo apho sukuba usiya khona.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 8, 'Ize ingesuki incwadi yomyalelo emlonyeni wakho; uze ucinge ngayo imini nobusuku, ukuze wenze ngenyameko, njengoko kubhaliweyo kuyo;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 9, 'Andikuyalelanga na? Yomelela ukhaliphe; musa ukoyika, musa ukoyika, ngokuba uYehova uThixo wakho unawe, naphi na apho sukuba usiya khona.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 10, 'uYoshuwa wabayalela abalindi abantu, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 11, 'Khandlula amatyala, nibawisele umthetho abantu, nithi, Zilungiseni ukudla; kuba emva kweentsuku ezintathu niya kuyiwela le Yordan nisiya kulidla ilifa ilizwe elo uYehova uThixo wenu aya kuninika lona ukuba libe lelenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 12, 'Wathetha uYoshuwa kumaRubhen, amaGadi, nakwisiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 13, 'Likhumbuleni ilizwi awaniwisela umthetho ngalo uMoses, umkhonzi kaYehova, esithi, uYehova uThixo wenu uniphumzile, uninikile eli lizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 14, 'Abafazi benu, nabantwana benu, nemfuyo yenu, bohlala ezweni aninika lona uMoses nganeno kweYordan; sukani ke nikhawuleze nixhobe, niye kubazalwana benu, onke amagorha anobukroti, nibancede;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 15, 'ade uYehova abaphumze abazalwana benu, njengoko aninikileyo nina, balihluthe nabo ilizwe elo abanika lona uYehova uThixo wenu; nandule ke nibuyele ezweni lelifa lenu, nidle oko waninika kona uMoses umkhonzi kaYehova nganeno kweYordan ekuphumeni kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 16, 'Bamphendula uYoshuwa, bathi, Yonke into osiyalele yona soyenza; naphi na apho usithumele khona, siya kuya.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 17, 'Ngako konke esamphulaphulayo uMoses, siya kukuphulaphula nawe kwanjengoko; uYehova uThixo wakho yedwa makabe nawe, njengokuba wayenoMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 1, 18, 'Bonke abasukuba begwilika kumyalelo wakho, bangawaphulaphuli amazwi akho, kuyo yonke into omwisele umthetho ngayo, bobulawa; yiba nje womelele uze ukhaliphe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 1, 'uYoshuwa unyana kaNun wesusa amadoda amabini aziintlola, wathi ngasese, Hambani niye kulikhangela ilizwe laseYeriko. Ahamba ke afika endlwini yehenyukazi eligama linguRahabhi, ahlala khona.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 2, 'Waxelelwa ukumkani waseYeriko, kwathiwa, Yabonani, kufike apha amadoda akoonyana bakaSirayeli ngobu busuku, eza kulihlola ilizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 3, 'Wathumela ukumkani waseYeriko kuRahabhi, esithi, Wakhuphe amadoda afikileyo kuwe, angenileyo endlwini yakho; ngokuba eze kuhlola ihlabathi lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 4, 'Yawathabatha inkazana loo madoda omabini, yawafihla, isithi, Bekukho amadoda abesiza kum, phofu bendingawazi apho abevela khona.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 5, 'Lakuba livaliwe isango, kwakuba mnyama, aphuma amadoda; Bendingazi ukuba aye phi na loo madoda; ngokuba uya kufikelela kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 6, 'Wawazisa eluphahleni lwendlu, wawafihla phezu kweendiza zeflakisi, abezilungelelanisile eluphahleni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 7, 'Awasukela loo madoda ngendlela yaseYordan, esa emdeni; baphuma ke abo basukelayo, balivala isango.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 8, 'Ngaphambi kokuba baye kulala, wenyuka waya kubabona phezu kwendlu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 9, 'Wathi kuloo madoda, Ndiyazi ukuba uYehova uninikile eli lizwe, nokuba ukulinda kwenu kube phezu kwethu, nokuba bafa bonke abemi belizwe ngenxa yenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 10, 'Kuba sivile ukuba iNkosi yanitshisela amanzi olwandle lwaseGalili ekuphumeni kwenu eYiputa; noko nakwenzayo kookumkani ababini bama-Amori, ababephesheya kweYordan, uSihon no-Ogi, enabaqalekisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 11, 'Sithe ke sakuziva ezi zinto, zanyibilika iintliziyo zethu, akwabakho kuqina kwamxhelo mntwini ngenxa yenu; ngokuba uYehova uThixo wenu nguye uThixo emazulwini phezulu, nasehlabathini phantsi apha.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 12, 'Ndifungeleni ke uYehova, ekubeni ndinenzele inceba, ukuba nani niya kuyenzela inceba indlu kabawo nindinike umqondiso wenyaniso;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 13, 'nokuba usindise ubawo noma, nabantakwethu, neento zonke abanazo, usisindise ekufeni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 14, 'Athi kuye loo madoda, Siphila ngawe, ukuba anithanga nisixele. Yaye ukuba uYehova usinike eli lizwe, siya kunikhonza ngobubele nangokunyaniseka.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 15, 'Wabahlisa ke ngefestile ngentsontelo, ngokuba indlu yakhe yayingaseludongeni lomzi, ibe yena ehleli eludongeni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 16, 'Wathi kubo, Hambani niye entabeni, banganihlanganisi abanitshutshisayo; zimele apho iintsuku ezintathu, bade babuye abo banisukelayo; kwaye emva koko ungahamba.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 17, 'Athi loo madoda kuye, Asinatyala thina ngesi sifungo sakho osifungise kuthi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 18, 'Uyabona, sakungena kweli lizwe, ubophe le ntsontelo ibomvu efestileni obusihlise ngayo; ngenisa uyihlo nonyoko nabantakwenu nosapho lwakho lonke ekhaya eya kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 19, 'Osukuba ephuma emnyango wendlu yakho, esiya phandle, igazi lakhe loba phezu kwentloko yakhe, sibe msulwa thina; osukuba ekuwe endlwini, igazi lakhe malibe phezu kwentloko yethu, ukuba kuthe kwasiwa sandla kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 20, 'Ukuba uthe wasixelela ngale nto, sokhululeka esifungweni sakho owasifungayo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 21, 'Wathi yena, Kungokwamazwi enu. Wabandulula ke bemka; waza wabophelela umtya obomvu efestileni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 22, 'Ahamba ke aya entabeni, ahlala khona iintsuku zantathu, bada babuya abo bawasukelayo; baza abatshutshisi babafuna endleleni yonke, ababafumana.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 23, 'Abuya amadoda lawo omabini, ehla entabeni, awela, afika kuYoshuwa unyana kaNun, amxelela yonke into eyenzeka kuwo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 2, 24, 'Athi kuYoshuwa: “Okunene, uYehova ulinikele esandleni sethu lonke ilizwe elo; ngokuba bathe ngenxa yethu bonke abemi behlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 1, 'Wavuka kusasa uYoshuwa; Banduluka eShitim, bafika eYordan, yena noonyana bonke bakaSirayeli, balalisa khona ubusuku ngaphambi kokuba banduluke.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 2, 'Emva kweentsuku ezintathu abathetheli behamba phakathi komkhosi;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 3, 'babawisela abantu umthetho, besithi, Xa nithe nayibona ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova uThixo wenu, nababingeleli abangabaLevi beyithwele, nophumani endaweni yenu, niyilandele.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 4, 'Kodwa makubekho ithuba phakathi kwakho naye, elingathi ngamawaka amabini eekubhite ngokomlinganiso; musani ukusondela kuyo, ukuze uyazi indlela oya kuhamba ngayo;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 5, 'Wathi uYoshuwa ebantwini, Zihlambululeni, ngokuba ngengomso uYehova uya kwenza imisebenzi ebalulekileyo phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 6, 'Wathi uYoshuwa kubabingeleli, Thwalani ityeya yomnqophiso, nihambe phambi kwabantu; Bayithabatha ityeya yomnqophiso, baphuma, bekhokela abantu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 7, 'Wathi uYehova kuYoshuwa, Namhlanje ndiya kuqala ukukwenza mkhulu emehlweni oonyana bakaSirayeli bonke, bazi ukuba ndiya kuba nawe, njengokuba ndibe ndinoMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 8, 'Bawisele umthetho ababingeleli abathwele ityeya yomnqophiso, uthi, Xa nithe nafika emdeni wamanzi aseYordan, nime eYordan;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 9, 'Wathi uYoshuwa koonyana bakaSirayeli, Sondelani apha, nive amazwi kaYehova uThixo wenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 10, 'Wathi uYoshuwa, Niya kwazi ke ukuba uThixo ophilileyo uphakathi kwenu, uya kuwagqogqa phambi kwenu amaKanan, namaHeti, namaHeti, namaPerizi, namaGirgashi, nama-Amori, phambi kwenu, namaYebhusi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 11, 'Yabonani, ityeya yomnqophiso weNkosi yehlabathi lonke inisa eYordan;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 12, 'Zithabatheleni ke amadoda abe lishumi elinamabini kuzo izizwe zakwaSirayeli, indoda ibe nye esizweni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 13, 'Kuthe ke, xeshikweni iintende zeenyawo zababingeleli abathwele ityeya kaYehova, iNkosi yehlabathi, zithe zafika emanzini aseYordan, avingca amanzi eYordan ngamanzi aphuma phezulu; baya kuma phezu kwemfumba.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 14, 'Baphuma ke abantu ezintenteni zabo, ukuba bawele iYordan, nababingeleli abathwele ityeya yomnqophiso babakhokela abantu;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 15, 'Kwathi, ekufikeni kwabathwali betyeya eYordan, zantywiliselwa iinyawo zababingeleli abathwele ityeya elunxwemeni lwamanzi; ngokuba iYordan ibiwela zonke iindonga zayo, ngexesha lokuvuna.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 16, 'Ema amanzi avela phezulu, aba yimfumba, kude nomzi ka-Adam, okufuphi neSaretan, ehla elwandle lwentlango, uLwandle lweTyuwa, aphela, atshabalala bawela abantu eYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 3, 17, 'Ababingeleli abathwele ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova bema ngokuqinileyo emhlabeni owomileyo phakathi kweYordan, yaye onke amaSirayeli awela kumhlaba owomileyo de lonke uhlanga luwele iYordan lucocekile.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 1, 'Bahlambuluka ke bonke abantu eYordan, wathetha uYehova kuYoshuwa, wathi,', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 2, 'Zithabatheleni ebantwini amadoda abe lishumi elinamabini, indoda ibe nye esizweni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 3, 'Wabawisela umthetho, wathi, Thabathani apha phakathi kweYordan, apho zazimi khona iinyawo zababingeleli, amatye alishumi elinamabini, niwathuthuzele, niwashiye apho nilala khona iyakuhlala ngokuhlwanje.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 4, 'Wawabiza uYoshuwa amadoda alishumi elinamabini, abewamisile koonyana bakaSirayeli, indoda yanye esizweni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 5, 'Wathi uYoshuwa kubo, Hambani ngokukhawuleza niye etyeya kaYehova uThixo wenu, ningene eYordan phakathi, nithabathe elowo ilitye egxalabeni lakhe, ngokwenani lezizukulwana zoonyana bakaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 6, 'kube ngumqondiso phakathi kwenu, xa bathe oonyana benu babuza kooyise ngexesha elizayo, bathi, Ayintoni na la matye?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 7, 'Baphenduleni, nithi, Amanzi eYordan avingcelwa phambi kwetyeya yomnqophiso kaYehova; ekuweleni kwayo iYordan, anqamka amanzi aseYordan, abe sisikhumbuzo saloo matye koonyana bakaSirayeli ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 8, 'Oonyana bakaSirayeli benza njengoko uYoshuwa wabawisela umthetho ngako, bathabatha amatye alishumi elinamabini eYordan phakathi, njengoko uYehova wathethayo kuYoshuwa, ngenani lezizwe zoonyana bakaSirayeli, bawasa ezweni lakwaSirayeli balala khona, balala khona.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 9, 'uYoshuwa wawamisa amatye alishumi elinamabini eYordan phakathi, apho zazimi khona iinyawo zababingeleli abathwele ityeya yomnqophiso; aselapho unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 10, 'Ababingeleli ababethwele ityeya bema phakathi eYordan de yagqitywa yonke into uYehova awayiyalela uYoshuwa ukuba ayithethe ebantwini, kanye njengoko uMoses wamyalelayo uYoshuwa; badlula ngokukhawuleza abantu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 11, 'Bahlambuluka bonke abantu, yadlula ityeya kaYehova nababingeleli phambi kwabantu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 12, 'Bawela oonyana bakaRubhen, noonyana bakaGadi, nesiqingatha sesizwe sakwaManase, bexhobile, phambi koonyana bakaSirayeli, njengoko wathethayo kubo uMoses.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 13, 'Ngathi babengamashumi amane amawaka axhobele imfazwe, abawelayo phambi koYehova, baye kulwa ezinkqantosini zaseYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 14, 'Ngaloo mini uYehova wamvelisa uYoshuwa emehlweni amaSirayeli onke; yaye bamoyika kanye njengoko babemoyika uMoses yonke imihla yobomi bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 15, 'Wathetha uYehova kuYoshuwa, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 16, 'Bawisele umthetho ababingeleli abathwele ityeya yesingqino, ukuba baphume eYordan;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 17, 'uYoshuwa wabawisela umthetho ababingeleli, wathi, Nyukani niphume eYordan.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 18, 'Ekunyukeni kwawo eYordan ababingeleli ababethwele ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova, nokunyuka kweenyawo zababingeleli baya emhlabeni owomileyo, abuyela endaweni yawo amanzi aseYordan, ahamba phezu kwelizwe lonke iindonga zayo, njengoko benza ngako.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 19, 'Banduluka abantu eYordan ngomhla weshumi wenyanga yokuqala, bamisa iintente eGiligali, engasempumalanga yeYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 20, 'Amatye alishumi elinamabini abawathabatha eYordan, uYoshuwa wawamisa eGiligali.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 21, 'Wathetha koonyana bakaSirayeli, wathi, Xa bathe oonyana benu babuza kooyise ngexesha elizayo, bathi, Ayintoni na la matye?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 22, 'Nize nibaxelele oonyana benu, nithi, Oonyana bakaSirayeli bayiwela le Yordan, behamba emhlabeni owomileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 23, 'Kuba uYehova uThixo wenu wawafudumeza amanzi aseYordan phambi kwenu nada nawela, kanye njengoko wenzayo uYehova uThixo wenu ngoLwandle lweSikhephe awalufudumeza phambi kwethu sada sawela;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 4, 24, 'ukuze zonke izizwe zehlabathi zisazi isandla sikaYehova ukuba somelele, ukuze zimoyike uYehova uThixo wazo ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 1, 'Kwathi, beva bonke ookumkani bama-Amori, ababephesheya kweYordan ngasentshonalanga, nookumkani bonke bamaKanan, ababengaselwandle, ukuba uYehova wawapheka kuqala amanzi aseYordan sada sacanda oonyana bakaSirayeli, zanyibilika iintliziyo zabo, akaba sabakho kubo umoya wabo ngenxa yoonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 2, 'Ngelo xesha wathi uYehova kuYoshuwa, Zenzele iintshengece, uphinde ubaluse oonyana bakaSirayeli okwesibini.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 3, 'Wazenzela uYoshuwa iintshengece, wabalusa oonyana bakaSirayeli endulini yezintsu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 4, 'Nasi isizathu sokuba uYoshuwa abaluse: Bonke abantu abaphuma eYiputa, amadoda, ewe, onke amadoda okulwa, afela entlango endleleni, ekuphumeni kwawo eYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 5, 'Baqalekiswa bonke abantu abaphumayo; Ke bonke abantu abazalelwe entlango endleleni ephuma eYiputa babengalukanga.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 6, 'Bahamba oonyana bakaSirayeli entlango iminyaka emashumi mane, ada atshabalala onke amadoda okulwa aphuma eYiputa, ngokuba engaliphulaphulanga ilizwi likaYehova; awabafungelayo uYehova ukuba akayi kubakho babonise ilizwe elo uYehova walithembisa ooyise ngesifungo, ukuba wosinika lona, ilizwe elibaleka amasi neenyosi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 7, 'Kwaabantwana wabavusileyo endaweni yabo, ngabo abamalusayo uYoshuwa, ngokuba bemathile, ngokuba bengabalusanga endleleni.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 8, 'Bakuba belugqibile ukulwalusa uhlanga lonke, bahlala ezintenteni zabo, bada baphola.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 9, 'Wathi uYehova kuYoshuwa, Namhla ndilisusile ihlazo leYiputa kuwe; ngenxa yoko kwathiwa igama laloo ndawo yiGiligali, unanamhla.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 10, 'Bamisa iintente oonyana bakaSirayeli eGiligali, benza ipasika ngomhla weshumi elinesine wenyanga, lakutshona ilanga, ezinkqantosini zaseYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 11, 'Ngengomso emva kwepasika yengqolowa yelizwe, badla izonka ezingenagwele nengqolowa egcadiweyo, kwangaloo mini.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 12, 'Yaphela imana ngengomso, xa badla ingqolowa yelizwe; bangabi saba nemana oonyana bakaSirayeli; badla iziqhamo zelizwe lakwaKanan ngaloo mnyaka.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 13, 'Xa uYoshuwa wayeseYeriko wawaphakamisa amehlo akhe, wakhangela, wabona indoda imi malunga naye, ithe rhuthu ikrele layo ngesandla; Waya kuyo uYoshuwa, wathi kuyo, Ungakuthi, ungakuthi, kusini na?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 14, 'Wathi, Hayi; kodwa ngoku ingumthetheli wenkundla kaYehova. Wawa uYoshuwa ngobuso bakhe, waqubuda, wathi kuyo, Ithetha ntoni na inkosi yam kumkhonzi wayo?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 5, 15, 'Wathi umthetheli womkhosi kaYehova kuYoshuwa, Khulula iimbadada zakho; ngokuba indawo leyo umi kuyo ingcwele. Wenjenjalo uYoshuwa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 1, 'Wavalwa ke umzi waseYeriko ngenxa yoonyana bakaSirayeli; akwaphuma mntu, kungangeni mntu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 2, 'Wathi uYehova kuYoshuwa, Yabona, ndiyinikela esandleni sakho iYeriko, nokumkani wayo, namagorha anobukroti.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 3, 'Wujikelezeni umzi, nonke nina madoda okulwa, niwujikeleze umzi kube kanye; Uya kwenjenjalo ngeentsuku ezintandathu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 4, 'Ke isixhenxe sababingeleli sothabatha iimpondo ezisixhenxe zenkunzi yegusha, phambi kwetyeya; ngomhla wesixhenxe nijikeleze isixeko izihlandlo ezisixhenxe, yaye ababingeleli bamele bavuthele izigodlo zeenkunzi zeegusha.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 5, 'Ekuvuthelweni kwesigodlo ixesha elide, nasekuveni isandi sesigodlo, baduma bonke abantu, baduma; kwaye udonga lwesixeko luya kuwa, kwaye abantu baya kunyuka, ngamnye amkhokela.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 6, 'uYoshuwa, unyana kaNun, wababiza ababingeleli, wathi kubo, Thwalani ityeya yomnqophiso, ababingeleli abasixhenxe bathabathe iimpondo ezisixhenxe zenkunzi yegusha, baqhube ityeya kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 7, 'Wathi ebantwini, Yiyani, niwungenele umzi, abaxhobileyo bagqithe ngokukhawuleza etyeyeni kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 8, 'Xa uYoshuwa wayethetha nabantu, ababingeleli abasixhenxe abaphethe izigodlo ezisixhenxe zenkunzi yegusha bahamba phambi koYehova, bevuthela izigodlo, yaye ityeya yomnqophiso kaYehova yabalandela.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 9, 'Abaxhobileyo babakhokela ababingeleli abaquphayo ukuvuthela ngezigodlo, umvuzo ulandela ityeya, ababingeleli baqupha ukuvuthela ngezigodlo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 10, 'uYoshuwa wabawisela umthetho abantu, wathi, Musani ukuduma, ningawaphithi amazwi enu, ningaphumi lizwi emlonyeni wenu, ide ibe yimini endiniwisela umthetho ngayo ukuba nimbulale ukumkani; ngoko kufuneka ukhwaze.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 11, 'Yawujikeleza ke ityeya kaYehova umzi, yafika kwaba kanye kuwo; bangena eminqubeni, balala phakathi kweminquba;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 12, 'uYoshuwa wavuka kusasa ngengomso, bayithwala ababingeleli ityeya kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 13, 'Ababingeleli abasixhenxe ababethwele iimpondo ezisixhenxe zeenkunzi zeegusha phambi kwetyeya kaYehova badlula baza bavuthela izigodlo; zikhokelwa ngamagorha; kodwa umvuzo waba ngasemva kwetyeya kaYehova, ekuqhubekeni kwababingeleli ukuvuthela ngezigodlo zokuvuthela.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 14, 'Ngomhla wesibini bawujikeleza umzi kanye, babuyela eminqubeni; benjenjalo iintsuku zantandathu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 15, 'Bavuka kusasa ngengomso, bawujikeleza umzi kwangolo hlobo izihlandlo zasixhenxe; kodwa ngaloo mini basijikeleza isixeko izihlandlo ezisixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 16, 'Kwathi ngesihlandlo sesixhenxe ababingeleli bavuthela izigodlo, waza uYoshuwa wathi ebantwini: “Khwazani! ngokuba uYehova uninikile umzi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 17, 'Isixeko siya kuba sisiqalekiso kuYehova, sona nento yonke ekuso; kuphela nguRahabhi ihenyukazi yedwa owodla ubomi, yena nento yonke ekuye endlwini yakhe; ngokuba wabazimezayo abathunywa esabathumayo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 18, 'Noko ke, zigcineni kwizinto ezalelweyo, ukuze ningaqalekiswa ngokwenu ukuba nithe nazamkela ezinye zezinto ezalelweyo, nenza inkampu kaSirayeli yaba yinto esingelwe phantsi, ibe isuka yabaqalekisa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 19, 'Ke yona isilivere, negolide, neempahla zobhedu, nezesinyithi, zinyulelwe uYehova; iya kungena ebuncwaneni bukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 20, 'Baduma ke abantu, ababingeleli ukuvuthela ngezigodlo baqupha; bakuva abantu isandi sesigodlo, baduma abantu ngodumo olukhulu, lwawa udonga, benyuka abantu bangena esixekweni, elowo ecaleni lakhe, wasithimba isixeko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 21, 'Ababulala ngobushushu bekrele bonke ababekuloo mzi, amadoda nabafazi, abaselula nabadala, neenkomo, neegusha, namaesile.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 22, 'Wathi uYoshuwa kumadoda amabini abelihlolile ilizwe, Ngenani endlwini yehenyukazi, niyikhuphe loo nkazana nayo yonke impahla yayo, njengoko nayifungelayo;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 23, 'Abengenile ke amadodana aziintlola, amthabatha uRahabhi, noyise, nonina, nabanakwabo, nabo bonke abenabo; yaye bazikhupha zonke izizwe zakhe baza bazishiya ngaphandle kwenkampu yakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 24, 'Bawutshisa umzi ngomlilo, neento zonke eziluwo; ngaphandle kwesilivere, negolide, nezinto zobhedu, nezesinyithi, zazibeka ebuncwaneni bendlu kaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 25, 'uYoshuwa wamsindisa uRahabhi, ihenyukazi, nendlu kayise, nabo bonke abenabo; wahlala kwaSirayeli unanamhla; ngokuba ubebazime abathunywa, abebathumile uYoshuwa ukuba baye kuhlola iYeriko.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 26, 'Wawaqalekisa uYoshuwa ngelo xesha, esithi, Uqalekisiwe phambi koYehova umntu oya kusuka awakhe lo mzi, iYeriko le; wowuseka ngowamazibulo akhe, unyana wakhe omncinane awamise amasango ayo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 6, 27, 'uYehova waba noYoshuwa; udumo lwakhe lwaphuma ehlabathini lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 1, 'Baxhuma oonyana bakaSirayeli ebuncwaneni; ngokuba uAkan, unyana kaKarmi, unyana kaSabhedi, unyana kaSeraki, wesizwe sakwaYuda, wathimba elinye ixhoba, wavutha ke umsindo kaYehova koonyana bakaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 2, 'uYoshuwa wasusa amadoda eYeriko ukuba aye eAyi, malungana neBhete-aven, ngasempumalanga eBheteli, wathi kuwo, Nyukani nilihlole ilizwe. Enyuka amadoda lawo, ayikhangela eAyi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 3, 'Abuyela kuYoshuwa, athi kuye, Musa ukuluvumela lunyuke lonke uhlanga; kodwa amadoda angamawaka amabini, okanye amathathu, ahlasela ayoyise iAyi; akuyi kusebenza bonke abantu khona; ngokuba bambalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 4, 'Kwenyuka ke kwaya khona amadoda amalunga namawaka amathathu, asaba phambi kwamadoda aseAyi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 5, 'Amadoda aseAyi abulala kuwo, amalunga namashumi amathathu anantandathu, ngokuba awasukelayo, esuka phambi kwesango, esa eSebharim, awabulala esisekweni; zanyibilika iintliziyo zabantu, zaba njengamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 6, 'uYoshuwa wazikrazula iingubo zakhe, wawa ngobuso bakhe phambi kwetyeya kaYehova kwada kwahlwa, yena namadoda amakhulu akwaSirayeli, bazigqubuthela ngothuli iintloko zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 7, 'Wathi uYoshuwa, Camagu, Nkosi yam, Yehova, yini na ukuba ubathuthuzele aba bantu eYordan, usinikele esandleni sama-Amori, asitshabalalise? Ukuba nje uThixo ebekholisiwe sithi, ngesa sahlala phesheya kweYordan!', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 8, 'Owu, Yehova, ndothini na xa amaSirayeli ezinikele ikhosi iintshaba zawo!', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 9, 'Ngokuba aya kuva amaKanan, nabemi bonke behlabathi, asinyelise, alicime igama lethu ehlabathini; Wenze ntoni na ngegama lakho elikhulu?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 10, 'Wathi uYehova kuYoshuwa, Suk’ ume; yini na ukuba ulale okobuso nje?', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 11, 'Ona oonyana bakaSirayeli, bawaphula umnqophiso wam endawawisela umthetho ngawo; kuba bade bathabatha enye yempahla yebhanki kananjalo beba baza bagrogrisa kwakhona, baza bayibeka phakathi kwempahla yabo.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 12, 'Ngoko oonyana bakaSirayeli ababanga nakuma phambi kweentshaba zabo, kodwa bazinikela umva iintshaba zabo, ngenxa yokuba babeqalekisiwe; andisayi kuba nawe, ukuba anithanga nitshabalalise isiqalekiso phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 13, 'Vuka, ubangcwalise abantu, uthi, Zihlambululeni ngomso; ngokuba utsho uYehova uThixo kaSirayeli, ukuthi, Kukho nto isiqalekiso phakathi kwakho, Sirayeli; Aniyi kuma phambi kweentshaba zenu nide nizisuse abaqalekisiweyo phakathi kwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 14, 'Ke ngoko, niya kuziswa ngomso ngokwezizukulwana zenu; yaye isizukulwana uYehova akholiswayo ngaso siya kuza kwizizukulwana zakhe; yaye isizukulwana esamkelekileyo kuYehova siya kuza ngokweentsapho; nendlu aya kuyithabatha uYehova, yophuma ngomntu.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 15, 'Lowo uthinjiweyo nempahla yakhe uya kutshiswa ngomlilo, yena nayo yonke into anayo, ngenxa yokuba uwaphule umnqophiso kaYehova nangenxa yokuba wenze ngobudenge kwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 16, 'Wavuka kusasa uYoshuwa, wabasondeza oonyana bakaSirayeli ngokwezizwe zabo; ekunyulweni kwesizwe sakwaYuda.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 17, 'Wasisondeza isizwe sakwaYuda; wathabatha umzi kaSarge; wasisondeza isizwe sikaBhasargi ngokwaso; noSabdi wabanjwa.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 18, 'Wasondela elowo endlwini yakhe; kwakhethwa uAkan, unyana kaKarmi, unyana kaSabhedi, unyana kaSeraki, wesizwe sakwaYuda;', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 19, 'Wathi uYoshuwa kuAkan, Nyana wam, mzukise uYehova uThixo kaSirayeli, umdumise; khawundixelele into oyenzileyo; musa ukundifihlela.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 20, 'uAkan wamphendula uYoshuwa, wathi, Okunene ndonile kuYehova uThixo kaSirayeli, ndenze le nto naleya:', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 21, 'ndabona exhobeni ingubo enkulu entle yaseBhabheli, namakhulu amabini eeshekele zesilivere, nejikazi lekhonkco legolide, liziishekele ezimashumi mahlanu ubunzima balo; nanzo zifunyenwe emhlabeni, phakathi emqolombeni wam, isilivere ingaphantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 22, 'Wathuma uYoshuwa abathunywa, wagidima waya ententeni; nanzo zimbelwe ententeni yakhe, isilivere ingaphantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(10, 7, 23, 'Bayithabatha ententeni, bayisa kuYoshuwa, nakoonyana bakaSirayeli bonke, bayibeka phambi koYehova.', 'XHO22');
